#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kalarm; lets you schedule the display of personal alarm messages, the "
"playing of sound files, the execution of commands and the sending of emails."
msgstr ""
"&kalarm; omogoča načrtovanje prikaza osebnih alarmnih sporočil, predvajanja "
"zvočnih datotek, izvajanja ukazov in pošiljanja e-pošte."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kalarm; displays the list of pending alarms, showing their times and "
"details. You can create new alarms, or you can select existing alarms for "
"modification or deletion. You can also optionally view expired alarms."
msgstr ""
"&kalarm; prikaže seznam čakajočih alarmov, čas in podrobnosti. Ustvarite "
"lahko nove alarme ali izberete obstoječe alarme, ki jih želite spremeniti "
"ali izbrisati. Po želji si lahko ogledate tudi pretečene alarme."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When configuring an alarm, you can choose whether it should repeat, and "
"whether the alarm should be canceled if it cannot be triggered at its "
"scheduled time. For display alarms, you can type in a message text, specify "
"a text or image file to display, or specify a command whose output should be "
"displayed. You can also choose the color of the alarm message, and whether "
"to play a sound or speak the message."
msgstr ""
"Pri konfiguriranju alarma lahko izberete, ali naj se ponavlja in ali naj se "
"alarm prekliče, če ga ni mogoče sprožiti ob načrtovanem času. Za prikaz "
"alarmov lahko vnesete besedilo sporočila, določite besedilno ali slikovno "
"datoteko, ki naj se prikaže, ali pa določite ukaz, katerega izpis naj se "
"prikaže. Izberete lahko tudi barvo alarmnega sporočila in izberete, ali naj "
"se predvaja zvok ali naj se sporočilo govori."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Alarms may also be scheduled from the command line, or via &DBus; calls from "
"programs."
msgstr ""
"Alarme lahko načrtujete tudi iz ukazne vrstice ali prek klicev &DBus; iz "
"programov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When an alarm message is due, if the windowing system permits, it is "
"displayed on each desktop to ensure that you don't miss it. The message "
"window shows the time for which the alarm was scheduled. It usually has a "
"defer option to ask for the alarm to be displayed again later. An example of "
"an alarm message:"
msgstr ""
"Ko pride do alarmnega sporočila, se prikaže na vsakem namizju, če okenski "
"sistem dopušča, da se zagotovi, da ga ne zamudite. Okno s sporočilom "
"prikazuje čas, za katerega je bil načrtovan alarm. Običajno ima možnost "
"odloga, da zahteva, da se alarm znova prikaže pozneje. Primer alarmnega "
"sporočila:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the &kalarm; message window"
msgstr "Zaslonska slika okna s &kalarm; sporočilom"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid "Alarm message"
msgstr "Alarmno sporočilo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Optionally, an alarm message may be displayed as a notification instead of "
"in a window."
msgstr ""
"Po želji se lahko alarmno sporočilo namesto v oknu prikaže kot obvestilo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When the alarm specifies a command to execute or an email to send, &kalarm; "
"displays nothing."
msgstr ""
"Ko alarm določi ukaz, ki ga je treba izvesti, ali elektronsko sporočilo, ki "
"ga je treba poslati, simbol &kalarm; ne prikaže ničesar."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kalarm; usually shows an icon in the system tray, although this can be "
"hidden if desired."
msgstr ""
"&kalarm; običajno prikaže ikono v sistemski vrstici, a jo lahko po želji "
"skrijete."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &kalarm;"
msgstr "Uporaba &kalarm;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When it is run with no command line parameters, &kalarm; starts in graphical "
"mode, and displays the current list of outstanding alarms."
msgstr ""
"Ko je program &kalarm; zagnan brez parametrov ukazne vrstice, se zažene v "
"grafičnem načinu in prikaže trenutni seznam nerešenih alarmov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All spin boxes in &kalarm; have an acceleration facility. To make the value "
"change by larger steps, hold down the &Shift; key while you click on the "
"spin arrow buttons."
msgstr ""
"Vsa polja za vrtenje v sistemu &kalarm; imajo možnost pospeševanja. Če "
"želite, da se vrednost spreminja po večjih korakih, med klikanjem na gumbe s "
"puščicami držite pritisnjeno tipko &Shift;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid "Alarm Types"
msgstr "Tipi alarmov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The basic functions available from the different alarm types which &kalarm; "
"provides are:"
msgstr ""
"Osnovne funkcije, ki so na voljo v različnih vrstah alarmov, ki jih "
"zagotavlja &kalarm;, so:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:141
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Display alarms display either a text message which you type in, or the "
"contents of a text or image file, or the textual output from a command which "
"is run when the alarm triggers. In addition to displaying one of these "
"items, they can also play audio files, have their text spoken, or emit a "
"simple beep. You can also specify commands to be executed before and after "
"the alarm message is displayed."
msgstr ""
"Prikazni alarmi prikažejo besedilno sporočilo, ki ga vnesete, vsebino "
"besedilne ali slikovne datoteke ali besedilni izpis ukaza, ki se zažene ob "
"sprožitvi alarma. Poleg prikaza enega od teh elementov lahko predvajajo tudi "
"zvočne datoteke, govorijo besedilo ali oddajajo preprost zvočni signal. "
"Določite lahko tudi ukaze, ki se izvedejo pred prikazom alarmnega sporočila "
"in po njem."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Command alarms execute either a command or a shell script which you can type "
"in. Nothing is displayed unless an error occurs."
msgstr ""
"Ukazni alarmni naprave izvedejo ukaz ali skriptno programsko opremo, ki jo "
"lahko vnesete. Nič se ne prikaže, razen če pride do napake."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:156
#, no-c-format
msgid "Email alarms send a email. Nothing is displayed unless an error occurs."
msgstr ""
"E-poštni alarmi pošljejo e-poštno sporočilo. Nič se ne prikaže, razen če "
"pride do napake."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:161
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Audio alarms play an audio file. Nothing is displayed unless an error occurs."
msgstr ""
"Zvočni alarmi predvajajo zvočno datoteko. Nič se ne prikaže, razen če pride "
"do napake."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:167
#, no-c-format
msgid "Error Handling"
msgstr "Ravnanje z napakami"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:169
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If an error occurs when an alarm triggers, an error message will be "
"displayed (unless you have previously specified not to show that type of "
"message again)."
msgstr ""
"Če se ob sprožitvi alarma pojavi napaka, se prikaže sporočilo o napaki "
"(razen če ste predhodno določili, da se ta vrsta sporočila ne sme več "
"prikazati)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If an execution error occurred the last time a command alarm triggered, a "
"white on red exclamation mark is shown in the message color column. Details "
"of the error are displayed in a tooltip if you position the cursor over that "
"line in the alarm list. The same error indications are shown for display "
"alarms if an execution error occurred for a pre- or post-alarm command "
"specified in the Special Actions dialog, except that the color column is not "
"changed to a red background."
msgstr ""
"Če se je ob zadnjem sprožitvi ukaza za alarm zgodila napaka pri izvajanju, "
"se v sporočilnem barvnem stolpcu prikaže belo rdeči klicaj. Podrobnosti o "
"napaki se prikažejo v opombi, če postavite kazalec na to vrstico v seznamu "
"alarmov. Enake navedbe napak so prikazane za prikaz alarmov, če je prišlo do "
"napake pri izvajanju ukaza pred ali po alarmu, določenega v pogovornem oknu "
"Posebna dejanja, le da se barvni stolpec ne spremeni v rdeče ozadje."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:186
#, no-c-format
msgid "Alarm List"
msgstr "Seznam alarmov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:188
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The main &kalarm; window displays the current list of pending alarms, "
"showing their times, repetition intervals, colors, names, and message texts, "
"names of files to play or display, commands to execute or email subjects. "
"(For a recurring alarm, the time shown is its next scheduled trigger time. "
"For an alarm with a reminder, the time shown is the time of the alarm "
"proper, not the reminder time.) An icon at the left of each alarm text/file/"
"command/email subject indicates the type of alarm."
msgstr ""
"V glavnem oknu &kalarm; je prikazan trenutni seznam čakajočih alarmov, ki "
"prikazuje njihove čase, intervale ponavljanja, barve, namena in besedila "
"sporočil, namena datotek za predvajanje ali prikazovanje, ukaze za izvajanje "
"ali predmete e-pošte. (Pri ponavljajočem se alarmu je prikazani čas "
"naslednji načrtovani čas sprožitve. Za alarm z opomnikom je prikazan čas "
"pravega alarma in ne čas opomnika.) Ikona na levi strani vsakega predmeta "
"besedila/datoteke/priporočila/elektronske pošte označuje vrsto alarma."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:197
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that the <guilabel>Name</guilabel> column only exists if the use of "
"alarm names is enabled in the <link linkend=\"preferences-general\">General</"
"link> tab of the Configuration dialog."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da stolpec <guilabel>Ime</guilabel> obstaja samo, če je uporaba "
"namen alarmov omogočena v zavihku <link linkend=\"preferences-general"
"\">Splošno</link> pogovornega okna Konfiguracija."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:203
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the &kalarm; main window"
msgstr "Zaslonska slika &kalarm; glavnega okna"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:209
#, no-c-format
msgid "Main window"
msgstr "Glavno okno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:214
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For a repeated alarm, the list shows its next scheduled trigger time and its "
"basic repetition interval (&eg; <quote>1 Day</quote> for a daily recurrence, "
"<quote>3 Weeks</quote> for a recurrence which triggers on Monday and "
"Wednesday every third week, <quote>Login</quote> for a repeat-at-login "
"alarm)."
msgstr ""
"Za ponavljajoči alarm sta na seznamu prikazana naslednji načrtovani čas "
"sprožitve in osnovni interval ponavljanja (&eg; <quote>1 dan</quote> za "
"dnevno ponavljanje, <quote>3 tedne</quote> za ponavljanje, ki se sproži v "
"ponedeljek in sredo vsak tretji teden, <quote>Prijava</quote> za alarm s "
"ponovitvijo ob prijavi)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If an execution error occurred the last time a command alarm triggered, or "
"the last time a display alarm's pre- or post-alarm command was executed, an "
"error indication is shown in the color column, as described in <link linkend="
"\"errors\">Error Handling</link> above."
msgstr ""
"Če je prišlo do napake pri izvajanju ob zadnjem sprožitvi ukaznega alarma "
"ali ob zadnjem izvajanju ukaza pred alarmom ali po njem, se v barvnem "
"stolpcu prikaže oznaka napake, kot je opisano v <link linkend=\"errors"
"\">Obravnava napak</link> zgoraj."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:227
#, no-c-format
msgid "Changing the Alarm List Appearance"
msgstr "Spreminjanje videza seznama alarmov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:229
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The alarms may be ordered by date/time, repeat interval, color, type, name "
"or text by clicking on the titlebar for the appropriate column. To reverse "
"the sort order, click the column titlebar again."
msgstr ""
"Alarme lahko razvrstite po datumu/času, intervalu ponavljanja, barvi, vrsti, "
"namenu ali besedilu s klikom na naslovno vrstico ustreznega stolpca. Če "
"želite obrniti vrstni red, ponovno kliknite naslovno vrstico stolpca."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:234
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can optionally show the remaining time until each alarm is due, together "
"with, or instead of, the alarm's scheduled time."
msgstr ""
"Po želji lahko skupaj z načrtovanim časom alarma ali namesto njega prikažete "
"preostali čas, ki bo ostal do začetka vsakega alarma."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:237
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can select which columns to display or hide by <mousebutton>Right</"
"mousebutton> clicking on the column headings and using the context menu to "
"set the columns to show. But note that at least one of the <guilabel>Name</"
"guilabel> or <guilabel>Message, File or Command</guilabel> columns, and at "
"least one of the <guilabel>Time</guilabel> or <guilabel>Time To</guilabel> "
"columns, are always shown."
msgstr ""
"Stolpce, ki jih želite prikazati ali skriti, lahko izberete tako, da "
"<mousebutton>Desno</mousebutton> kliknete na naslove stolpcev in s pomočjo "
"kontekstnega menija določite stolpce, ki jih želite prikazati. Upoštevajte, "
"da je vedno prikazan vsaj eden od stolpcev <guilabel>Ime</guilabel> ali "
"<guilabel>Sporočilo, datoteka ali ukaz</guilabel> in vsaj eden od stolpcev "
"<guilabel>Čas</guilabel> ali <guilabel>Čas do</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:245
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you use multiple alarm calendars, you can color code alarms according to "
"which calendar they belong to, by selecting a different background color for "
"each calendar (see <link linkend=\"using-calendars\">Using Calendars</link>)."
msgstr ""
"Če uporabljate več koledarjev, lahko alarme barvno označite glede na to, "
"kateremu koledarju pripadajo, tako da za vsak koledar izberete drugo barvo "
"ozadja (glejte <link linkend=\"using-calendars\">Uporaba koledarjev</link>)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:253
#, no-c-format
msgid "Archived Alarms"
msgstr "Arhivirani alarmi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:255
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default, &kalarm; archives alarms for a limited period once they have "
"expired or been deleted. (But note that alarms which you delete are stored "
"only if they have already triggered at least once.) You can control whether "
"&kalarm; archives expired alarms, and for how long, in the <link linkend="
"\"preferences-storage\">Configuration dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto &kalarm; za omejeno obdobje arhivira alarme, ko potečejo ali so "
"izbrisani. (Upoštevajte pa, da se alarmi, ki jih izbrišete, shranijo le, če "
"so se že vsaj enkrat sprožili.) V pogovornem oknu <link linkend="
"\"preferences-storage\">Konfiguracija</link> lahko določite, ali &kalarm; "
"arhivira pretečene alarme in koliko časa."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:262
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Archived alarms may be shown in the alarm list by selecting "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem>Show Archived Alarms</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. To hide them again, deselect "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem>Show Archived Alarms</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Arhivirane alarme lahko prikažete na seznamu alarmov z izbiro "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guimenuitem>Pokaži arhivirane alarme</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Če jih želite znova skriti, odstranite izbiro "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guimenuitem>Pokaži arhivirane alarme</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:271
#, no-c-format
msgid "Filtering the Alarm List by Date"
msgstr "Filtriranje seznama alarmov po datumu"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:273
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can restrict the alarm list to show only alarms which are scheduled to "
"occur on a selected date. This is achieved by means of the alarm date "
"selector, which can be displayed or hidden by <menuchoice><guimenu>View</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Date Selector</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. Select "
"a date by clicking on it in the date selector, or deselect it by clicking on "
"it again. The date selector displays a single month. To display a different "
"month, use the arrow controls in the date selector, or the mouse wheel."
msgstr ""
"Seznam alarmov lahko omejite tako, da so prikazani samo alarmi, ki se bodo "
"predvidoma pojavili na izbrani datum. To dosežemo z izbirnikom datuma "
"alarma, ki ga lahko prikažemo ali skrijemo z <menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pokaži izbirnik datumov</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. "
"Izberite datum s klikom nanj v izbirniku datumov ali ga odstranite s "
"ponovnim klikom nanj. V izbirniku datuma je prikazan en mesec. Če želite "
"prikazati drug mesec, uporabite puščice v izbirniku datuma ali kolesce miške."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:286
#, no-c-format
msgid "Searching the Alarm List"
msgstr "Iskanje po seznamu alarmov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:288
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can search through the alarm list to find alarms containing a search "
"text. To invoke this, select <menuchoice> <guimenu>Edit</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Find...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. In the search "
"dialog, select the alarm types which you wish to search. To continue "
"searching for more alarms which match, use <menuchoice> <guimenu>Edit</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Find Next</guimenuitem></menuchoice> or <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Find Previous</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Po seznamu alarmov lahko iščete alarme, ki vsebujejo iskano besedilo. Če ga "
"želite priklicati, izberite <menuchoice> <guimenu>Uredi</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Najdi...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. V pogovornem oknu "
"za iskanje izberite vrste alarmov, ki jih želite iskati. Če želite "
"nadaljevati iskanje več alarmov, ki se ujemajo, uporabite <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Najdi naslednje</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> ali <menuchoice> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Najdi "
"predhodno</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:298
#, no-c-format
msgid "Searching is performed as follows:"
msgstr "Iskanje poteka na naslednji način:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:302
#, no-c-format
msgid "Text message alarms: the message text is searched."
msgstr "Besedilo: Poišče se besedilo sporočila."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:306
#, no-c-format
msgid "File display alarms: the file path/&URL; is searched."
msgstr "Datoteka: išče se pot do datoteke/&URL;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:310
#, no-c-format
msgid "Command alarms: the command line or command script is searched."
msgstr "Ukaz: išče se ukazna vrstica ali ukazna skripta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:315
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Email alarms: in addition to the subject and body of the email, the "
"recipients and the URLs of attachments are searched."
msgstr ""
"E-pošta: poleg predmeta in vsebine e-pošte se iščejo tudi prejemniki in URL-"
"ji priponk."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:320
#, no-c-format
msgid "Audio alarms: the file path/&URL; is searched."
msgstr "Zvok: išče se pot do datoteke/&URL;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:324
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Only alarms currently shown in the alarm list can be selected for searching. "
"So if you want to search archived alarms, you must first display them as "
"described in the section above."
msgstr ""
"Za iskanje lahko izberete samo alarme, ki so trenutno prikazani na seznamu "
"alarmov. Če torej želite iskati arhivirane alarme, jih morate najprej "
"prikazati, kot je opisano v zgornjem razdelku."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:331
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating and Manipulating Alarms"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje in upravljanje alarmov"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:334
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating a New Alarm"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje novega alarma"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:336
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To create a new alarm, do one of the following, and then select the type of "
"alarm from the list which appears. This displays the <link linkend=\"alarm-"
"edit-dlg\">Alarm Edit dialog</link> through which you configure the alarm."
msgstr ""
"Če želite ustvariti nov alarm, naredite eno od naslednjih dejanj, nato pa s "
"seznama, ki se prikaže, izberite vrsto alarma. Prikaže se <link linkend="
"\"alarm-edit-dlg\">Pogovorno okno za urejanje alarma</link>, prek katerega "
"konfigurirate alarm."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:343
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nova</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:348
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<mousebutton>Right</mousebutton> click on the system tray icon and choose "
"<menuchoice><guimenuitem>New Alarm</guimenuitem></menuchoice> from the "
"context menu."
msgstr ""
"<mousebutton>Desno</mousebutton> kliknite ikono v sistemski vrstici in v "
"kontekstnem meniju izberite <menuchoice><guimenuitem>Nov alarm</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:355
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<mousebutton>Right</mousebutton> click in the alarm list and choose "
"<menuchoice><guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem></menuchoice> from the context "
"menu."
msgstr ""
"<mousebutton>Desno</mousebutton> kliknite v seznamu alarmov in v kontekstnem "
"meniju izberite <menuchoice><guimenuitem>Nova</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:361
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Alternatively, you can create new alarms preconfigured from various sources:"
msgstr ""
"Ustvarite lahko tudi nove alarme, ki so vnaprej konfigurirani iz različnih "
"virov:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:366
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To preset the alarm's date in the <link linkend=\"alarm-edit-dlg-time"
"\">Alarm Edit dialog</link>, <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> click on the "
"desired date in the alarm date selector (see <link linkend=\"datepicker"
"\">Filtering the Alarm List by Date</link>) and select the appropriate alarm "
"type from the context menu."
msgstr ""
"Če želite v <link linkend=\"alarm-edit-dlg-time\">pogovornem oknu za "
"urejanje alarmov</link> vnaprej nastaviti datum alarma, <mousebutton>z "
"desno</mousebutton> kliknite želeni datum v izbirniku datuma alarma (glejte "
"<link linkend=\"datepicker\">Filtriranje seznama alarmov po datumu</link>) "
"in v kontekstnem meniju izberite ustrezno vrsto alarma."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:375
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To base your new alarm on an alarm template, follow the instructions in the "
"<link linkend=\"templates\">Alarm Templates</link> section."
msgstr ""
"Če želite, da nov alarm temelji na predlogi za alarm, upoštevajte navodila v "
"razdelku <link linkend=\"templates\">Predloge alarmov</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:381
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To base your new alarm on an existing one, highlight the existing alarm in "
"the list and select <menuchoice> <guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Copy</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. This opens the <link linkend=\"alarm-edit-dlg"
"\">Alarm Edit dialog</link> already filled in with a copy of the selected "
"alarm's details."
msgstr ""
"Če želite, da vaš novi alarm temelji na obstoječem, označite obstoječi alarm "
"na seznamu in izberite <menuchoice> <guimenu>Datoteka</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Kopiraj</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. To odpre <link "
"linkend=\"alarm-edit-dlg\">Pogovorno okno za urejanje alarma</link>, ki je "
"že izpolnjeno s kopijo podrobnosti izbranega alarma."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:389
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To create a new alarm which displays an existing email message, drag the "
"email from &kmail; onto &kalarm;'s main window. Then select the "
"<guilabel>Display Alarm</guilabel> option. This opens the <link linkend="
"\"alarm-edit-dlg\">Alarm Edit dialog</link> with the entire email message "
"(including sender, recipient, &etc;) as the alarm text."
msgstr ""
"Če želite ustvariti nov alarm, ki prikazuje obstoječe e-poštno sporočilo, "
"povlecite e-poštno sporočilo iz &kmail; v glavno okno &kalarm;. Nato "
"izberite možnost <guilabel>Prikazni alarm</guilabel>. To odpre <link linkend="
"\"alarm-edit-dlg\">Pogovorno okno Uredi alarm</link> s celotnim e-poštnim "
"sporočilom (vključno s pošiljateljem, prejemnikom in drugimi podatki) kot "
"besedilom alarma."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:398
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To create a new email alarm to send a copy of an existing email message, "
"drag the email from &kmail; onto &kalarm;'s main window. Then select the "
"<guilabel>Email Alarm</guilabel> option. The <link linkend=\"alarm-edit-dlg"
"\">Alarm Edit dialog</link> is preset with the entire email message except "
"sender."
msgstr ""
"Če želite ustvariti nov e-poštni alarm za pošiljanje kopije obstoječega e-"
"poštnega sporočila, povlecite e-poštno sporočilo iz programa &kmail; v "
"glavno okno programa &kalarm;. Nato izberite možnost <guilabel>E-poštni "
"alarm</guilabel>. <link linkend=\"alarm-edit-dlg\">Pogovorno okno za "
"urejanje alarma</link> je prednastavljeno s celotnim e-poštnim sporočilom "
"razen pošiljatelja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:406
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To create a new alarm which displays a summary of an existing to-do, drag "
"the to-do from &korganizer; or other application onto &kalarm;'s main "
"window. This opens the <link linkend=\"alarm-edit-dlg\">Alarm Edit dialog</"
"link> with the to-do contents as the alarm text."
msgstr ""
"Če želite ustvariti nov alarm, ki prikazuje povzetek obstoječega opravila, "
"povlecite opravilo iz programa &korganizer; ali druge aplikacije v glavno "
"okno programa &kalarm;. To odpre <link linkend=\"alarm-edit-dlg\">Pogovorno "
"okno Uredi alarm</link> z vsebino opravila kot besedilom alarma."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:414
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To create a new command alarm, drag the text of a script starting with "
"<quote>#!</quote> onto &kalarm;'s main window. Then select the "
"<guilabel>Command Alarm</guilabel> option. This opens the <link linkend="
"\"alarm-edit-dlg\">Alarm Edit dialog</link> preset with the script text."
msgstr ""
"Če želite ustvariti nov ukazni alarm, povlecite besedilo skripte, ki se "
"začne z <quote>#!</quote>, v glavno okno programa &kalarm;. Nato izberite "
"možnost <guilabel>Ukazni Alarm</guilabel>. To odpre prednastavitev <link "
"linkend=\"alarm-edit-dlg\">Pogovorno okno za urejanje alarmov</link> z "
"besedilom scenarija."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:422
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To create a file display alarm, drag a text or image file &URL; onto "
"&kalarm;'s main window. This opens the <link linkend=\"alarm-edit-dlg"
"\">Alarm Edit dialog</link> and sets the file name."
msgstr ""
"Če želite ustvariti prikazni alarm, povlecite besedilno ali slikovno "
"datoteko &URL; v glavno okno programa &kalarm;. To odpre <link linkend="
"\"alarm-edit-dlg\">Pogovorno okno Uredi alarm</link> in nastavi ime datoteke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:429
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To create an audio alarm, drag an audio file &URL; onto &kalarm;'s main "
"window. This opens the <link linkend=\"alarm-edit-dlg\">Alarm Edit dialog</"
"link> and sets the file name."
msgstr ""
"Če želite ustvariti zvočni alarm, povlecite zvočno datoteko &URL; v glavno "
"okno programa &kalarm;. To odpre <link linkend=\"alarm-edit-dlg\">Pogovorno "
"okno za urejanje alarmov</link> in nastavi ime datoteke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:436
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To create a text message alarm, drag any piece of text onto &kalarm;'s main "
"window. If prompted, select the <guilabel>Display Alarm</guilabel> option. "
"This opens the <link linkend=\"alarm-edit-dlg\">Alarm Edit dialog</link> "
"preset with the alarm text."
msgstr ""
"Če želite ustvariti Besedilni alarm, povlecite poljuben del besedila v "
"glavno okno programa &kalarm;. Če ste pozvani, izberite možnost "
"<guilabel>Prikazni alarm</guilabel>. To odpre prednastavitev <link linkend="
"\"alarm-edit-dlg\">Pogovorno okno Uredi alarm</link> z besedilom alarma."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:444
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can automatically create birthday alarms for people in &kaddressbook; as "
"described in <link linkend=\"birthdays\">Importing Birthdays from "
"&kaddressbook;</link>."
msgstr ""
"Za osebe v &kaddressbook; lahko samodejno ustvarite rojstnodnevne alarme, "
"kot je opisano v <link linkend=\"birthdays\">Uvoz rojstnih dni iz "
"&kaddressbook;</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:454
#, no-c-format
msgid "Modifying an Existing Alarm"
msgstr "Spreminjanje obstoječega alarma"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:456
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To modify an existing pending alarm (expired alarms cannot be amended), do "
"one of the following:"
msgstr ""
"Če želite spremeniti obstoječi čakajoči alarm (pretečenih alarmov ni mogoče "
"spremeniti), naredite eno od naslednjih dejanj:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:461
#, no-c-format
msgid "Double click on its entry in the alarm list."
msgstr "Dvakrat kliknite na njegov vnos na seznamu alarmov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:465
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select it by clicking on its entry in the alarm list. Then choose "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Edit</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Izberite ga s klikom na njegov vnos na seznamu alarmov. Nato izberite "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Uredi</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:471
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<mousebutton>Right</mousebutton> click on its entry in the alarm list and "
"choose <menuchoice><guimenuitem>Edit</guimenuitem></menuchoice> from the "
"context menu."
msgstr ""
"<mousebutton>Desno</mousebutton> kliknite njegov vnos na seznamu alarmov in "
"v kontekstnem meniju izberite <menuchoice><guimenuitem>Uredi</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:478
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This displays the <link linkend=\"alarm-edit-dlg\">Alarm Edit dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže se <link linkend=\"alarm-edit-dlg\">Pogovorno okno za urejanje "
"alarmov</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:484
#, no-c-format
msgid "Deleting/Reactivating an Alarm"
msgstr "Brisanje/ponovno aktiviranje alarma"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:486
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To delete existing alarms, select one or more by clicking on their entries "
"in the alarm list. Then do one of the following:"
msgstr ""
"Če želite izbrisati obstoječe alarme, izberite enega ali več s klikom na "
"njihov vnos na seznamu alarmov. Nato naredite eno od naslednjih dejanj:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:491
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose <menuchoice> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Delete</guimenuitem> "
"</menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Izberite <menuchoice> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Izbriši</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:496
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<mousebutton>Right</mousebutton> click on the selected entries and choose "
"<menuchoice><guimenuitem>Delete</guimenuitem></menuchoice> from the context "
"menu."
msgstr ""
"<mousebutton>Desno</mousebutton> kliknite na izbrane vnose in izberite "
"<menuchoice><guimenuitem>Izbriši</guimenuitem></menuchoice> iz kontekstnega "
"menija."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:502
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To delete them without a confirmation prompt, type &Shift;-<keycap>Delete</"
"keycap>."
msgstr ""
"Če jih želite izbrisati brez poziva za potrditev, vnesite &Shift;-"
"<keycap>Delete</keycap>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:507
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you delete an active alarm, it is archived, provided that it has "
"triggered at least once before being deleted, and provided that expired "
"alarms are archived at all. (Use the <link linkend=\"preferences-storage"
"\">Configuration dialog</link> to control whether and for how long archived "
"alarms are stored.) When you delete an archived alarm, or an active alarm "
"which has not yet triggered, it is removed permanently."
msgstr ""
"Ko izbrišete aktivni alarm, se ta arhivira, če se je pred izbrisom vsaj "
"enkrat sprožil in če se alarmi, ki jim je potekla veljavnost, sploh "
"arhivirajo. (Uporabite <link linkend=\"preferences-storage\">Pogovorno okno "
"Konfiguracija</link> za nadzor, ali in koliko časa se arhivirani alarmi "
"shranjujejo.) Ko izbrišete arhiviran alarm ali aktivni alarm, ki se še ni "
"sprožil, se ta trajno odstrani."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:515
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can reactivate a deleted alarm from the archived alarms list, provided "
"that it has not yet expired. To do this, first display archived alarms, as "
"described in <link linkend=\"expired\">Archived Alarms</link>. Then:"
msgstr ""
"Izbrisan alarm s seznama arhiviranih alarmov lahko ponovno aktivirate, če še "
"ni potekel. To storite tako, da najprej prikažete arhivirane alarme, kot je "
"opisano v <link linkend=\"expired\">Arhivirani Alarmi</link>. Nato:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:522
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select one or more appropriate archived alarms by clicking on their entries "
"in the alarm list. Then choose <menuchoice> <guimenu>Actions</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Reactivate</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Izberite enega ali več ustreznih arhiviranih alarmov s klikom na njihove "
"vnose na seznamu alarmov. Nato izberite <menuchoice> <guimenu>Dejanja</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Znova omogoči</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:528
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<mousebutton>Right</mousebutton> click on the desired entries in the "
"archived alarm list and choose <menuchoice><guimenuitem>Reactivate</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> from the context menu."
msgstr ""
"<mousebutton>Desno</mousebutton> kliknite želene vnose na seznamu "
"arhiviranih alarmov in izberite <menuchoice><guimenuitem>Znova omogoči</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> iz kontekstnega menija."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:538
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enabling/Disabling an Alarm"
msgstr "Omogočanje/izklop alarma"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:540
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"See <link linkend=\"enable-disable\">Enabling and Disabling Alarms</link> "
"for how to enable and disable alarms, either individually or as a whole, or "
"temporarily skip individual alarms."
msgstr ""
"Glejte <link linkend=\"enable-disable\">Omogočanje in Izklop alarmov</link>, "
"kako vključiti in izključiti alarme, posamezno ali kot celoto, ali začasno "
"preskočiti posamezne alarme."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:547
#, no-c-format
msgid "Setting an Alarm to Wake from Suspend"
msgstr "Nastavitev budilke za prebujanje iz stanja mirovanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:549
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"See <link linkend=\"wake-suspend\">Wake From Suspend</link> for how to "
"configure an alarm to wake up your system from suspension or hibernation."
msgstr ""
"Glejte <link linkend=\"wake-suspend\">Prebujanje iz stanja mirovanja</link>, "
"kjer je opisano, kako konfigurirati alarm za prebujanje sistema iz stanja "
"mirovanja ali hibernacije."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:556
#, no-c-format
msgid "Acknowledging an Alarm"
msgstr "Potrditev alarma"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:558
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"See <link linkend=\"message-display\">Alarm Message Display</link> for how "
"to acknowledge alarms."
msgstr ""
"Glejte <link linkend=\"message-display\">Prikaz alarmnega sporočila</link> "
"za potrditev alarmov."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:564
#, no-c-format
msgid "Alarm Templates"
msgstr "Predloge alarmov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:566
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you frequently want to set up similar alarms, you can create an alarm "
"template to avoid having to enter all the details from scratch each time. A "
"template can contain all the details which an alarm can contain, apart from "
"the start date."
msgstr ""
"Če želite pogosto nastavljati podobne alarme, lahko ustvarite predlogo "
"alarma, da vam ne bo treba vsakič znova vnašati vseh podrobnosti. Predloga "
"lahko vsebuje vse podrobnosti, ki jih lahko vsebuje alarm, razen datuma "
"začetka."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:571
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As an example, you may regularly want to set an alarm to remind you about a "
"television program whose time varies from week to week. The template would "
"contain all the alarm details (message text, whether to play a sound, &etc;) "
"except for the time and date. Now, to create the alarm, all you need to do "
"is open the <link linkend=\"alarm-edit-dlg\">Alarm Edit dialog</link> with "
"that template and then enter the time and date."
msgstr ""
"Na primer, morda želite redno nastaviti alarm, ki vas bo opomnil na "
"televizijski program, katerega čas se iz tedna v teden spreminja. Predloga "
"bi vsebovala vse podrobnosti alarma (besedilo sporočila, ali naj se predvaja "
"zvok &etc;), razen ure in datuma. Če želite ustvariti alarm, morate odpreti "
"<link linkend=\"alarm-edit-dlg\">Pogovorno okno Uredi alarm</link> s to "
"predlogo in nato vnesti čas in datum."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:579
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To create an alarm based on a template, open the <link linkend=\"alarm-edit-"
"dlg\">Alarm Edit dialog</link> preset with the template details:"
msgstr ""
"Če želite ustvariti alarm na podlagi predloge, odprite <link linkend=\"alarm-"
"edit-dlg\">Pogovorno okno Uredi alarm</link> s podrobnostmi predloge:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:585
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the <menuchoice> <guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>New</"
"guimenuitem> <guimenuitem>New Alarm From Template</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> menu item, and then select the desired template."
msgstr ""
"Izberite element menija <menuchoice> <guimenu>Datoteka</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Nova</guimenuitem> <guimenuitem>Nov alarm iz predloge</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice> in nato izberite želeno predlogo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:592
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<mousebutton>Right</mousebutton> click on the system tray icon and choose "
"<menuchoice><guimenuitem>New Alarm</guimenuitem> <guimenuitem>New Alarm From "
"Template</guimenuitem></menuchoice> from the context menu. Then select the "
"desired template."
msgstr ""
"<mousebutton>Desno</mousebutton> kliknite ikono v sistemski vrstici in "
"izberite <menuchoice><guimenuitem>Nov alarm</guimenuitem> <guimenuitem>Nov "
"alarm iz predloge</guimenuitem></menuchoice> iz kontekstnega menija. Nato "
"izberite želeno predlogo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:600
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Open the <link linkend=\"alarm-edit-dlg\">Alarm Edit dialog</link> in the "
"usual way, and click the <guibutton>Load Template...</guibutton> button to "
"select a template to preset the dialog with."
msgstr ""
"Odprite <link linkend=\"alarm-edit-dlg\">Pogovorno okno za urejanje alarmov</"
"link> na običajen način in kliknite gumb <guibutton>Naloži predlogo...</"
"guibutton>, da izberete predlogo, s katero boste prednastavili pogovorno "
"okno."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:608
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring Templates"
msgstr "Konfiguriranje predlog"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:610
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can create, modify or delete templates using the Alarm Templates dialog, "
"or you can create a new alarm template based on an existing alarm."
msgstr ""
"Predloge lahko ustvarite, spremenite ali izbrišete v pogovornem oknu "
"Predloge alarmov ali pa ustvarite novo predlogo alarma na podlagi "
"obstoječega alarma."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:614
#, no-c-format
msgid "To create a new alarm template, do one of the following:"
msgstr ""
"Če želite ustvariti novo predlogo za alarm, naredite eno od naslednjih "
"dejanj:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:618
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Display the Alarm Templates dialog by selecting the <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Templates...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> "
"menu item, clicking <guibutton>New</guibutton>, and choosing the alarm type "
"from the list which appears. This displays a blank Template Edit dialog."
msgstr ""
"Prikažite pogovorno okno Predloge alarmov tako, da izberete element menija "
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Predloge...</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice>, kliknete <guibutton>Nova</guibutton> in na "
"prikazanem seznamu izberete vrsto alarma. Prikaže se prazno pogovorno okno "
"za urejanje predloge."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:626
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Display the Alarm Templates dialog by selecting the <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Templates...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> "
"menu item, select an existing template from the list and click "
"<guibutton>Copy</guibutton>. This opens the Template Edit dialog already "
"filled in with a copy of the existing template's details."
msgstr ""
"Prikažite pogovorno okno Predloge alarmov tako, da izberete element menija "
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Nova</guimenu><guimenuitem>Predloge...</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice>, s seznama izberete obstoječo predlogo in kliknete "
"<guibutton>Kopiraj</guibutton>. To odpre pogovorno okno Urejanje predloge, "
"ki je že izpolnjeno s kopijo podrobnosti obstoječe predloge."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:635
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Highlight an alarm in the alarm list and select <menuchoice> <guimenu>File</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Create Template...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. This "
"opens the Template Edit dialog already filled in with a copy of the selected "
"alarm's details."
msgstr ""
"Označite alarm na seznamu alarmov in izberite <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Ustvari predlogo...</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice>. To odpre pogovorno okno Urejanje predloge, ki je že izpolnjeno "
"s kopijo podrobnosti izbranega alarma."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:642
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To modify an existing template, display the Alarm Templates dialog by "
"selecting the <menuchoice> <guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Templates...</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice> menu item and click <guibutton>Edit</guibutton>. "
"This displays the Template Edit dialog which is described below."
msgstr ""
"Če želite spremeniti obstoječo predlogo, prikažite pogovorno okno Predloge "
"alarmov tako, da izberete element menija <menuchoice> <guimenu>Datoteka</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Predloge...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> in kliknete "
"<guibutton>Uredi</guibutton>. Prikaže se pogovorno okno Urejanje predloge, "
"ki je opisano v nadaljevanju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:648
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To delete existing templates, display the Alarm Templates dialog by "
"selecting the <menuchoice> <guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Templates...</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice> menu item, select one or more templates and click "
"<guibutton>Delete</guibutton>. A confirmation prompt is issued to prevent "
"accidental deletions."
msgstr ""
"Če želite izbrisati obstoječe predloge, prikažite pogovorno okno Predloge "
"alarmov tako, da izberete meni <menuchoice> <guimenu>Datoteka</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Predloge...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>, izberete eno "
"ali več predlog in kliknete <guibutton>Izbriši</guibutton>. Da bi preprečili "
"nenamerno brisanje, se prikaže poziv za potrditev."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:658
#, no-c-format
msgid "Template Edit Dialog"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno za Urejanje predloge"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:660
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Template Edit dialog is similar to the <link linkend=\"alarm-edit-dlg"
"\">Alarm Edit dialog</link>. The following controls are different:"
msgstr ""
"Pogovorno okno za urejanje predloge je podobno pogovornemu oknu <link "
"linkend=\"alarm-edit-dlg\">Pogovorno okno za urejanje alarmov</link>. "
"Naslednje kontrole se razlikujejo:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:666
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter the template's name in <guilabel>Template name</guilabel>. It is the "
"template's name which is displayed in template selection lists, so it is "
"best to choose a name which will remind you of its function. Each template's "
"name must be unique."
msgstr ""
"Ime predloge vnesite v polje <guilabel>Ime predloge</guilabel>. Ime predloge "
"je tisto, ki se prikaže v seznamih za izbiro predlog, zato je najbolje "
"izbrati ime, ki vas bo spominjalo na njeno funkcijo. Ime vsake predloge mora "
"biti edinstveno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:673
#, no-c-format
msgid "In the <guilabel>Time</guilabel> group box, select one of:"
msgstr ""
"V polju skupine <guilabel>Čas</guilabel> izberite eno od naslednjih možnosti:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:677
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Default time</guilabel> if you do not wish to specify any trigger "
"time. Alarms based on this template will initially use the normal default "
"trigger time for new alarms."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Privzet čas</guilabel>, če ne želite določiti nobenega časa "
"sprožitve. Alarmi, ki temeljijo na tej predlogi, bodo na začetku uporabljali "
"običajni privzeti čas sprožitve za nove alarme."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:683
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check <guilabel>Time</guilabel> to enter a time when the alarm is to be "
"triggered."
msgstr ""
"Označite <guilabel>Čas</guilabel>, da vnesete čas, ko naj bi se alarm "
"sprožil."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:688
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check <guilabel>Date only</guilabel> to specify that the alarm should only "
"have a date, not a time."
msgstr ""
"Označite <guilabel>Samo datum</guilabel>, če želite določiti, da naj alarm "
"vsebuje samo datum in ne časa."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:693
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check <guilabel>Time from now</guilabel> to enter how long (in hours and "
"minutes) after the alarm is created, that it should be triggered."
msgstr ""
"Označite možnost <guilabel>Čas od zdaj</guilabel>, da vnesete, koliko časa "
"(v urah in minutah) po ustvarjenem alarmu naj bi se ta sprožil."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:701
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <guilabel>Recurrence Rule</guilabel> group box in the "
"<guilabel>Recurrence</guilabel> tab, no day or month need be selected for "
"weekly or yearly recurrences, respectively."
msgstr ""
"V skupinskem polju <guilabel>Pravilo za ponovitev</guilabel> v zavihku "
"<guilabel>Ponovitev</guilabel> za tedenske oziroma letne ponovitve ni treba "
"izbrati dneva ali meseca."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:712
#, no-c-format
msgid "Alarm Calendars"
msgstr "Alarmi v koledarju"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:714
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you only use one computer and work independently, it may not matter to "
"you where &kalarm; stores its alarms. But if you need to access alarms on "
"more than one computer, or in more than one location on your local computer, "
"you can define <quote>alarm calendars</quote> to tell &kalarm; to use other "
"alarm calendars additional to, or in place of, its default ones."
msgstr ""
"Če uporabljate samo en računalnik in delate samostojno, vam morda ni "
"pomembno, kje &kalarm; shranjuje alarme. Če pa potrebujete dostop do alarmov "
"v več kot enem računalniku ali na več kot enem mestu v lokalnem računalniku, "
"lahko določite <quote>Alarme v koledarju</quote>, s čimer sporočite programu "
"&kalarm;, naj poleg privzetih koledarjev alarmov ali namesto njih uporablja "
"druge koledarje alarmov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:721
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can view and manipulate calendars via the calendar list, which can be "
"displayed alongside the alarm list in &kalarm;'s main window. Alarms from "
"all alarm calendars are shown merged together in the alarm list. When you "
"save a new alarm, you can set a configuration option to determine whether it "
"is automatically saved into the default calendar, or whether you will be "
"prompted to choose a calendar. When you edit an existing alarm, it is "
"automatically saved back into its original alarm calendar."
msgstr ""
"Koledarje si lahko ogledate in z njimi upravljate prek koledarskega seznama, "
"ki je lahko prikazan poleg seznama alarmov v glavnem oknu programa &kalarm;. "
"Alarmi iz vseh koledarjev so na seznamu alarmov prikazani združeni. Ko "
"shranite nov alarm, lahko nastavite možnost konfiguracije, s katero "
"določite, ali se alarm samodejno shrani v privzeti koledar ali pa boste "
"pozvani k izbiri koledarja. Ko uredite obstoječi alarm, se samodejno shrani "
"nazaj v prvotni koledar alarmov."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:731
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the &kalarm; main window, showing the calendar list"
msgstr ""
"Zaslonska slika glavnega okna programa &kalarm; prikazuje seznam koledarjev"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:738
#, no-c-format
msgid "Main window showing the calendar list"
msgstr "Glavno okno s seznamom koledarjev"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:744
#, no-c-format
msgid "Calendar Types and Options"
msgstr "Vrste in možnosti koledarja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:746
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Alarm calendars are categorized by alarm type and storage type. They can be "
"disabled, set read-only, or made the default calendar for their alarm type."
msgstr ""
"Koledarji alarmov so razvrščeni glede na vrsto alarma in vrsto shranjevanja. "
"Lahko jih onemogočite, nastavite samo za branje ali določite kot privzeti "
"koledar za svojo vrsto alarma."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:752
#, no-c-format
msgid "Alarm type"
msgstr "Vrsta alarma"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:754
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The three alarm entity types &ndash; active alarms, archived alarms and "
"alarm templates &ndash; are stored in separate alarm calendars. &kalarm; "
"therefore has three standard default calendars, one for each type (see <link "
"linkend=\"faq\">Questions and Answers</link> for details), which you can "
"change if you wish."
msgstr ""
"Trije tipi alarmnih entitet &ndash; aktivni alarmi, arhivirani alarmi in "
"predloge alarmov &ndash; so shranjeni v ločenih koledarjih alarmov. &kalarm; "
"ima zato tri standardne privzete koledarje, enega za vsako vrsto (za "
"podrobnosti glejte <link linkend=\"faq\">Vprašanja in odgovori</link>), ki "
"jih lahko po želji spremenite."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:764
#, no-c-format
msgid "Storage type"
msgstr "Vrsta shranjevanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:766
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kalarm; handles two alarm calendar storage types:"
msgstr "&kalarm; obdeluje dve vrsti shranjevanja koledarja alarma:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:769
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Local file: Alarms are stored in a single local file in iCalendar format. "
"&kalarm; uses local file calendars by default (see <link linkend=\"faq"
"\">Questions and Answers</link> for details). <quote>Local files</quote>, in "
"addition to files on the local computer, can include alarm calendars on the "
"local network as long as their location can be represented by a path name "
"starting with <literal>/</literal>."
msgstr ""
"Lokalna datoteka: Alarmi so shranjeni v eni lokalni datoteki v formatu "
"iCalendar. &kalarm; privzeto uporablja koledarje lokalnih datotek (za "
"podrobnosti glejte <link linkend=\"faq\">Vprašanja in odgovori</link>). "
"<quote>Lokalne datoteke</quote> lahko poleg datotek v lokalnem računalniku "
"vključujejo tudi koledarje alarmov v lokalnem omrežju, če je njihovo "
"lokacijo mogoče predstaviti z namenom poti, ki se začne z <literal>/</"
"literal>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:778
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Remote file: Alarms are stored in a single remote file in iCalendar format. "
"This storage method allows you to access your alarm data remotely no matter "
"where you are, or enables alarm calendars to be viewed by other people. When "
"using remote files, &kalarm; works with a local copy of the data."
msgstr ""
"Oddaljena datoteka: Alarmi so shranjeni v eni oddaljeni datoteki v formatu "
"iCalendar. Ta način shranjevanja vam omogoča dostop do podatkov o alarmih na "
"daljavo, ne glede na to, kje ste, ali omogoča drugim osebam ogled koledarjev "
"alarmov. Ko uporabljate oddaljene datoteke, &kalarm; deluje z lokalno kopijo "
"podatkov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:784
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kalarm; does not monitor remote alarm calendars for changes, so that if "
"changes are made by someone else, &kalarm; might overwrite them. To avoid "
"this, you are recommended to adopt either of the following policies:"
msgstr ""
"&kalarm; ne nadzoruje oddaljenih alarmnih koledarjev za spremembe, tako da, "
"če spremembe izvede nekdo drug, &kalarm; jih lahko prepiše. Da bi se temu "
"izognili, vam priporočamo, da sprejmete enega od naslednjih pravilnikov:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:789
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Ensure that only one person or application accesses the calendar at any one "
"time."
msgstr ""
"Zagotovite, da do koledarja hkrati dostopa samo ena oseba ali aplikacija."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:791
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All users other than the calendar owner should configure the calendar as "
"read-only."
msgstr ""
"Vsi uporabniki razen lastnika koledarja morajo koledar konfigurirati kot "
"samo za branje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:794
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Otherwise, as a minimum you should reload the calendar before changing it or "
"relying on its contents, using the method described in <link linkend=\"using-"
"calendars\">Using Calendars</link>. Note also that if the calendar is "
"configured as read-write, &kalarm; will overwrite it whenever an alarm "
"triggers."
msgstr ""
"V nasprotnem primeru morate vsaj znova naložiti koledar, preden ga "
"spremenite ali se zanašate na njegovo vsebino, z uporabo metode, opisane v "
"<link linkend=\"using-calendars\">Uporaba koledarjev</link>. Upoštevajte "
"tudi, da če je koledar konfiguriran za branje in pisanje, &kalarm; ga bo "
"prepisal vsakič, ko se sproži alarm."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:806
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enabled/disabled status"
msgstr "Vključeno/izključeno stanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:808
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Disabling a calendar has the same effect as removing it, except that it "
"still appears in the calendar list for easy re-enabling. When disabled, its "
"alarms are ignored and do not appear in the alarm list or list of templates. "
"When it is re-enabled, its alarms are once again shown and, if it is an "
"active alarm calendar, made active."
msgstr ""
"Onemogočanje koledarja ima enak učinek kot njegovo odstranjevanje, le da je "
"koledar še vedno prikazan na seznamu koledarjev, da ga lahko znova "
"omogočite. Če je onemogočen, se njegovi alarmi ne upoštevajo in niso "
"prikazani na seznamu alarmov ali seznamu predlog. Ko ga ponovno omogočite, "
"se njegovi alarmi ponovno prikažejo in, če gre za aktiven koledar alarmov, "
"postanejo aktivni."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:818
#, no-c-format
msgid "Read-only status"
msgstr "Stanje samo za branje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:820
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A read-only calendar's alarms cannot be changed or added to. So you cannot "
"edit its alarms, or save new alarms to it. Also, it is not possible to defer "
"its alarms, since to do so would need the deferral time to be saved into the "
"alarm. After its alarms trigger, they are not removed from the calendar and "
"archived until you or another user accesses the calendar in read-write mode."
msgstr ""
"Alarmov koledarja, ki je namenjen samo branju, ni mogoče spreminjati ali "
"dodajati. Zato ne morete urejati njegovih alarmov ali vanj shranjevati novih "
"alarmov. Prav tako ni mogoče odložiti njegovih alarmov, saj bi bilo treba "
"čas odložitve shraniti v alarm. Ko se sprožijo njegovi alarmi, se ne "
"odstranijo iz koledarja in ne arhivirajo, dokler vi ali drug uporabnik ne "
"dostopate do koledarja v bralno-pisalnem načinu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:828
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can set the read-only status of a calendar in the calendar configuration "
"dialog. However, some calendars cannot be made writeable, for various "
"reasons:"
msgstr ""
"V pogovornem oknu za konfiguracijo koledarja lahko nastavite stanje "
"koledarja samo za branje. Vendar nekaterih koledarjev zaradi različnih "
"razlogov ni mogoče napisati:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:833
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If a calendar was created by another application, it would be unsafe to "
"allow &kalarm; to update it, since differences in data format might make it "
"unusable by the creating application."
msgstr ""
"Če je koledar ustvarila druga aplikacija, bi bilo nevarno dovoliti, da ga "
"&kalarm; posodobi, saj bi zaradi razlik v obliki podatkov aplikacija, ki ga "
"je ustvarila, tega koledarja morda ne mogla uporabljati."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:838
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the calendar was created by a later version of &kalarm;, data might be "
"lost if your version of &kalarm; updated it."
msgstr ""
"Če je bil koledar ustvarjen s poznejšo različico programa &kalarm;, se lahko "
"podatki izgubijo, če ga vaša različica programa &kalarm; posodobi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:843
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the calendar was created by a previous version of &kalarm;, data could be "
"lost or it could be made unusable for the previous &kalarm; version if your "
"version of &kalarm; updated it. You will be prompted whether to convert its "
"format so as to make it writeable, bearing in mind the potential "
"compatibility problems if the previous &kalarm; version needs to access it "
"again."
msgstr ""
"Če je bil koledar ustvarjen s prejšnjo različico programa &kalarm;, se lahko "
"podatki izgubijo ali pa so neuporabni za prejšnjo različico programa "
"&kalarm;, če ga vaša različica programa &kalarm; posodobi. Pozvali vas bomo, "
"ali naj pretvorite njegovo obliko tako, da ga bo mogoče zapisovati, pri "
"čemer je treba upoštevati morebitne težave z združljivostjo, če bo prejšnja "
"različica programa &kalarm; ponovno potrebovala dostop do njega."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:851
#, no-c-format
msgid "If you do not have permission to write to the calendar file or folder."
msgstr "Če nimate dovoljenja za pisanje v datoteko ali mapo koledarja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:856
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you need write access to alarms in a calendar which cannot be made "
"writeable, you can copy its alarms by importing them into a writeable "
"calendar using the latter calendar's <menuchoice><guimenuitem>Import...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> context menu option (see <link linkend=\"import"
"\">Importing Alarms from External Calendars</link>)."
msgstr ""
"Če potrebujete dostop za pisanje alarmov v koledarju, ki ga ni mogoče "
"narediti pisalnega, lahko njegove alarme kopirate tako, da jih uvozite v "
"pisalni koledar z uporabo možnosti <menuchoice><guimenuitem>Uvoz...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> kontekstnega menija slednjega (glejte <link "
"linkend=\"import\">Uvoz alarmov iz zunanjih koledarjev</link>)."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:866
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default calendar status"
msgstr "Privzeto stanje koledarja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:868
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"One calendar of each alarm type can optionally be made the default calendar "
"for that alarm type. New alarms are automatically saved to the default "
"calendar for the appropriate alarm type, unless you have selected the prompt "
"option for new alarms and templates in the <link linkend=\"preferences-"
"storage\">Configuration dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"En koledar vsake vrste alarma lahko po želji postane privzeti koledar za to "
"vrsto alarma. Novi alarmi se samodejno shranijo v privzeti koledar za "
"ustrezno vrsto alarma, razen če ste v <link linkend=\"preferences-storage"
"\">Pogovornem oknu za konfiguracijo</link> izbrali možnost poziv za nove "
"alarme in predloge."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:880
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using Calendars"
msgstr "Uporaba koledarjev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:882
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can view and manipulate calendars via the calendar list, which can be "
"displayed or hidden by <menuchoice> <guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem>Show "
"Calendars</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. When using the calendar list, first "
"select the alarm type using the combo box above the list. Then either click "
"on one of the buttons below the list, or <mousebutton>Right</mousebutton> "
"click on the appropriate calendar in the list and choose an item from the "
"context menu. The actions available are:"
msgstr ""
"Koledarje si lahko ogledate in z njimi upravljate prek seznama koledarjev, "
"ki ga lahko prikažete ali skrijete z <menuchoice> <guimenu>Pogled</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Pokaži koledarje</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. Če "
"uporabljate seznam koledarja, najprej izberite vrsto alarma v izbirnem polju "
"nad seznamom. Nato kliknite enega od gumbov pod seznamom ali "
"<mousebutton>Desno</mousebutton> kliknite ustrezen koledar na seznamu in "
"izberite element v kontekstnem meniju. Na voljo so naslednji ukrepi:"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:893
#, no-c-format
msgid "Add..."
msgstr "Dodaj..."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:895
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Add a calendar of the selected type to the list. You are asked to choose a "
"storage type, following which the calendar configuration dialog is "
"displayed, where you can enter the location of the calendar and its "
"characteristics. If there is no existing alarm calendar in the specified "
"location, a new one will be created."
msgstr ""
"Na seznam dodajte koledar izbrane vrste. Izbrati morate vrsto shranjevanja, "
"nato se prikaže pogovorno okno za konfiguracijo koledarja, v katerem lahko "
"vnesete lokacijo koledarja in njegove značilnosti. Če na določenem mestu ni "
"obstoječega koledarja z alarmi, se ustvari nov koledar."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:904
#, no-c-format
msgid "Remove"
msgstr "Odstrani"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:906
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Remove the selected calendar from the list. The calendar itself is left "
"intact; it is simply removed from the list, and may subsequently be "
"reinstated in the list if desired."
msgstr ""
"Odstranite izbrani koledar s seznama. Sam koledar ostane nedotaknjen; "
"preprosto se odstrani s seznama in se lahko po želji ponovno vključi na "
"seznam."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:913
#, no-c-format
msgid "Edit..."
msgstr "Uredi..."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:915
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Edit the selected calendar. This displays the configuration dialog for the "
"selected calendar."
msgstr ""
"Urejanje izbranega koledarja. Prikaže se pogovorno okno za konfiguracijo "
"izbranega koledarja."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:921
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reload"
msgstr "Znova naloži"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:923
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Reload the selected calendar. The calendar is re-read from its storage "
"location, ensuring that there is no discrepancy between what &kalarm; "
"displays and the current state of the calendar. If the calendar is shared "
"with other users, any changes which they have made will now be seen by "
"&kalarm;."
msgstr ""
"Ponovno naložite izbrani koledar. Koledar se ponovno prebere iz "
"shranjevalnega mesta, s čimer se zagotovi, da ni neskladja med tem, kar "
"prikazuje &kalarm;, in trenutnim stanjem koledarja. Če je koledar v skupni "
"rabi z drugimi uporabniki, bo vse njihove spremembe zdaj videl tudi &kalarm;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:929
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you reload a remote calendar, any changes to alarms which you have made "
"since the calendar was last saved will be lost. Also, any alarms which have "
"expired since the last save may be retriggered."
msgstr ""
"Če ponovno naložite oddaljeni koledar, se izgubijo vse spremembe alarmov, ki "
"ste jih naredili od zadnjega shranjevanja koledarja. Prav tako se lahko "
"ponovno sprožijo vsi alarmi, ki so potekli od zadnjega shranjevanja."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:937
#, no-c-format
msgid "Import..."
msgstr "Uvozi..."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:939
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Import alarms from external calendar files into the selected calendar. This "
"is described in <link linkend=\"import\">Importing Alarms from External "
"Calendars</link>. This option is not available for disabled or read-only "
"calendars."
msgstr ""
"Uvoz alarmov iz zunanjih koledarskih datotek v izbrani koledar. To je "
"opisano v <link linkend=\"import\">Uvoz alarmov iz zunanjih koledarjev</"
"link>. Ta možnost ni na voljo za onemogočene koledarje ali koledarje samo za "
"branje."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:948
#, no-c-format
msgid "Export..."
msgstr "Izvoz..."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:950
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Export all the alarms in the selected calendar to an external calendar file. "
"This is described in <link linkend=\"export\">Exporting Alarms to External "
"Calendars</link>. This option is not available for disabled calendars."
msgstr ""
"Izvozite vse alarme v izbranem koledarju v zunanjo datoteko koledarja. To je "
"opisano v <link linkend=\"export\">Izvoz alarmov v zunanje koledarje</link>. "
"Ta možnost ni na voljo za onemogočene koledarje."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:958
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show Details"
msgstr "Prikaži podrobnosti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:960
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Display details about the selected calendar. This shows the calendar's "
"location, storage type and status information."
msgstr ""
"Prikaz podrobnosti o izbranem koledarju. To prikazuje lokacijo koledarja, "
"vrsto shranjevanja in informacije o stanju."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:967
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use as Default"
msgstr "Uporabi kot privzeto"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:969
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Make the selected calendar the default calendar for the selected calendar "
"type. This option is not available for disabled or read-only calendars."
msgstr ""
"Izbrani koledar postane privzeti koledar za izbrano vrsto koledarja. Ta "
"možnost ni na voljo za onemogočene koledarje ali koledarje samo za branje."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:976
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set Color..."
msgstr "Nastavi barvo..."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:978
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select a background color for highlighting this calendar's alarms in the "
"alarm list. This enables you to see at a glance which alarms belong to a "
"particular calendar."
msgstr ""
"Izberi barvo ozadja za poudarjanje alarmov tega koledarja na seznamu "
"alarmov. Tako lahko na prvi pogled vidite, kateri alarmi pripadajo "
"določenemu koledarju."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:985
#, no-c-format
msgid "Clear Color"
msgstr "Počisti barvo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:987
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clear color highlighting for this calendar's alarms in the alarm list. The "
"option only appears after <guimenuitem>Set Color</guimenuitem> has been used "
"on this calendar."
msgstr ""
"Izbrišite barvno osvetlitev za alarme tega koledarja na seznamu alarmov. Ta "
"možnost se prikaže šele po tem, ko je bila za ta koledar uporabljena možnost "
"<guimenuitem>Nastavi barvo</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1000
#, no-c-format
msgid "Importing Alarms from External Calendars"
msgstr "Uvoz alarmov iz zunanjih koledarjev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1002
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can import alarms from other calendar files into &kalarm;. The import "
"function scans the selected calendar files for events containing alarms, and "
"copies them (with new unique IDs) into &kalarm;'s calendar. Events without "
"alarms, and calendar entries other than events, are ignored. There are two "
"ways to import alarms:"
msgstr ""
"V program &kalarm; lahko uvozite alarme iz drugih koledarskih datotek. "
"Funkcija za uvoz pregleda izbrane koledarske datoteke za dogodke, ki "
"vsebujejo alarme, in jih kopira (z novimi edinstvenimi ID-ji) v koledar "
"&kalarm;. Dogodki brez alarmov in koledarski vnosi, ki niso dogodki, se ne "
"upoštevajo. Alarme lahko uvozite na dva načina:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1011
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Import Alarms...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> to import alarms of all types (active alarms, "
"archived alarms and alarm templates) from the calendar files."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Uvozi "
"Alarme...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> za uvoz alarmov vseh vrst (aktivni "
"alarmi, arhivirani alarmi in predloge alarmov) iz koledarskih datotek."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1016
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have configured <link linkend=\"calendars\">alarm calendars</link>, "
"alarms of each type will be added to the appropriate default calendar, or if "
"you have selected the prompt option for new alarms and templates in the "
"<link linkend=\"preferences-storage\">Configuration dialog</link>, you will "
"be prompted for the calendar to use."
msgstr ""
"Če ste konfigurirali <link linkend=\"calendars\">Koledarje alarmov</link>, "
"bodo alarmi vsake vrste dodani v ustrezen privzeti koledar, če pa ste v "
"<link linkend=\"preferences-storage\">Pogovornem oknu za konfiguracijo</"
"link> izbrali možnost poziva za nove alarme in predloge, boste pozvani k "
"uporabi koledarja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1025
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<mousebutton>Right</mousebutton> click on a calendar in the calendar list, "
"and choose <menuchoice><guimenuitem>Import...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"from the context menu. This imports alarms of the currently selected type "
"into that calendar. For example, if the selected calendar type is alarm "
"templates, alarm templates (and not active alarms or archived alarms) will "
"be imported."
msgstr ""
"<mousebutton>Desno</mousebutton> kliknite koledar na seznamu koledarjev in "
"izberite <menuchoice><guimenuitem>Uvozi...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> iz "
"kontekstnega menija. S tem v koledar uvozite alarme trenutno izbrane vrste. "
"Če je na primer izbrana vrsta koledarja predloga za alarm, bodo uvožene "
"predloge za alarm (in ne aktivni alarmi ali arhivirani alarmi)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1035
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you import alarms from calendar files which were created by applications "
"other than &kalarm;, the alarms may be changed by the import process &ndash; "
"even alarm times may change. This depends on the data storage conventions "
"used by the other application, and is unavoidable if those conventions "
"differ from what &kalarm; expects. Always check imported alarms for "
"unexpected changes, and adjust them as necessary."
msgstr ""
"Če uvozite alarme iz koledarskih datotek, ki so bile ustvarjene s programi, "
"ki niso &kalarm;, se lahko alarmi pri uvozu spremenijo &ndash; celo časi "
"alarmov se lahko spremenijo. To je odvisno od načinov za shranjevanje "
"podatkov, ki jih uporablja druga aplikacija, in je neizogibno, če se ti "
"načini razlikujejo od tistih, ki jih pričakuje &kalarm;. Uvožene alarme "
"vedno preverite za nepričakovane spremembe in jih po potrebi prilagodite."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1046
#, no-c-format
msgid "Exporting Alarms to External Calendars"
msgstr "Izvoz alarmov v zunanje koledarje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1048
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can export alarms from &kalarm; to other calendar files, either the "
"alarms currently selected in the alarm list, or all the alarms from an alarm "
"calendar. The methods to do this are given below. Whichever method is used, "
"you can either create a new calendar file or append the exported alarms to "
"an existing calendar file. To append the alarms, check <guilabel>Append to "
"existing file</guilabel> in the file selection dialog; otherwise, any "
"existing file is overwritten."
msgstr ""
"Alarme lahko izvozite iz programa &kalarm; v druge koledarske datoteke, "
"bodisi alarme, ki so trenutno izbrani na seznamu alarmov, bodisi vse alarme "
"iz koledarja alarmov. Načini za to so navedeni v nadaljevanju. Ne glede na "
"uporabljeno metodo lahko ustvarite novo datoteko koledarja ali pa izvožene "
"alarme dodate obstoječi datoteki koledarja. Če želite dodati alarme, v "
"pogovornem oknu za izbiro datoteke označite <guilabel>Dodaj v obstoječo "
"datoteko</guilabel>; v nasprotnem primeru se prepiše vsaka obstoječa "
"datoteka."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1059
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To export the alarms currently selected in the alarm list, "
"<mousebutton>Right</mousebutton> click on the selection and choose "
"<menuchoice><guimenuitem>Export...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> from the "
"context menu, or use <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Export "
"Selected Alarms...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> in the main menu."
msgstr ""
"Če želite izvoziti alarme, ki so trenutno izbrani na seznamu alarmov, "
"<mousebutton>Desno</mousebutton> kliknite na izbor in izberite "
"<menuchoice><guimenuitem>Izvozi...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> iz "
"kontekstnega menija ali uporabite <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Izvozi izbrane alarme...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> v glavnem "
"meniju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1068
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To export all the alarms from a calendar, <mousebutton>Right</mousebutton> "
"click on a calendar in the calendar list, and choose "
"<menuchoice><guimenuitem>Export...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> from the "
"context menu."
msgstr ""
"Če želite izvoziti vse alarme iz koledarja, <mousebutton>Desno</mousebutton> "
"kliknite koledar na seznamu koledarjev in v kontekstnem meniju izberite "
"<menuchoice><guimenuitem>Izvoz...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1079
#, no-c-format
msgid "Importing Birthdays from &kaddressbook;"
msgstr "Uvoz rojstnih dni iz &kaddressbook;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1081
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This function is only available if &kalarm;'s <link linkend=\"akonadi-plugin"
"\">Akonadi plugin</link> is installed and enabled."
msgstr ""
"Ta funkcija je na voljo le, če je nameščen in omogočen vtičnik <link linkend="
"\"akonadi-plugin\">Akonadi</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1086
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can set up display alarms for birthdays stored in &kaddressbook;, by "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Import Birthdays...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. This displays a dialog which allows you to select "
"which birthdays to create alarms for."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite lahko prikaz alarmov za rojstne dneve, shranjene v &kaddressbook;, "
"z <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Uvozi Rojstne dneve..."
"</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Prikaže se pogovorno okno, v katerem lahko "
"izberete rojstne dneve, za katere želite ustvariti alarme."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1094
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <guilabel>Alarm Text</guilabel> group box, you can set up the text to "
"be displayed in the birthday alarm messages. The message text is created by "
"combining the <guilabel>Prefix</guilabel> text followed by the person's name "
"followed by the <guilabel>Suffix</guilabel> text. No spaces are added, so "
"remember to include any necessary trailing space in <guilabel>Prefix</"
"guilabel> and leading space in <guilabel>Suffix</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"V polju skupine <guilabel>Besedilo alarma</guilabel> lahko nastavite "
"besedilo, ki bo prikazano v rojstnodnevnih alarmnih sporočilih. Besedilo "
"sporočila je ustvarjeno z združitvijo besedila <guilabel>Predpona</"
"guilabel>, ki mu sledi ime osebe in besedilo <guilabel>Pripona</guilabel>. "
"Presledki se ne dodajajo, zato ne pozabite vključiti potrebnega zadnjega "
"presledka v <guilabel>Predpona</guilabel> in začetnega presledka v "
"<guilabel>Pripona</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1102
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you change the alarm text, the birthday selection list will be re-"
"evaluated."
msgstr ""
"Če spremenite besedilo alarma, se seznam za izbiro rojstnih dni ponovno "
"oceni."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <guilabel>Select Birthdays</guilabel> list, select the birthdays "
"which you want to create alarms for. Note that the list shows only those "
"entries in &kaddressbook; which contain a birthday and which do not already "
"have a birthday alarm in the format currently defined in the <guilabel>Alarm "
"Text</guilabel> group box."
msgstr ""
"Na seznamu <guilabel>Izberi rojstne dneve</guilabel> izberite rojstne dneve, "
"za katere želite ustvariti alarme. Upoštevajte, da so na seznamu prikazani "
"samo tisti vnosi v &kaddressbook;, ki vsebujejo rojstni dan in ki še nimajo "
"alarma za rojstni dan v obliki, ki je trenutno določena v polju skupine "
"<guilabel>Besedilo alarma</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1115
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The remaining controls are the same as for <guilabel>Text</guilabel> alarms "
"in the <link linkend=\"alarm-edit-dlg\">Alarm Edit dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"Preostali kontrolniki so enaki kot za <guilabel>Besedilne</guilabel> alarme "
"v <link linkend=\"alarm-edit-dlg\">Pogovorno okno Uredi alarm</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1121
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have configured <link linkend=\"calendars\">alarm calendars</link>, "
"the alarms will be added to the default active alarm calendar, or if you "
"have selected the prompt option for new alarms and templates in the <link "
"linkend=\"preferences-storage\">Configuration dialog</link>, you will be "
"prompted for the calendar to use."
msgstr ""
"Če ste konfigurirali <link linkend=\"calendars\">koledarje alarmov</link>, "
"bodo alarmi dodani v privzeti aktivni alarmni koledar, če pa ste v "
"pogovornem oknu <link linkend=\"preferences-storage\">Pogovorno okno "
"Konfiguracija</link> izbrali možnost poziv za nove alarme in predloge, boste "
"morali izbrati koledar, ki ga želite uporabiti."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1130
#, no-c-format
msgid "Undo / Redo"
msgstr "Razveljavi / Ponovno uveljavi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1132
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can undo and redo the most recent changes which you have made during the "
"current session of &kalarm;. Most actions can be undone, including creation, "
"edit and deletion of alarms and alarm templates, and reactivation of alarms. "
"To prevent excessive resources being used by the undo history, the number of "
"changes stored is limited to the last 12."
msgstr ""
"Zadnje spremembe, ki ste jih naredili med trenutno sejo programa &kalarm;, "
"lahko razveljavite in ponovite. Večino dejanj je mogoče preklicati, vključno "
"z ustvarjanjem, urejanjem in brisanjem alarmov in alarmnih predlog ter "
"ponovnim aktiviranjem alarmov. Da zgodovina razveljavitev ne bi porabila "
"preveč virov, je število shranjenih sprememb omejeno na zadnjih 12."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1139
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To undo the last change, select <menuchoice> <guimenu>Edit</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Undo</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. To redo the last "
"change which was undone, select <menuchoice> <guimenu>Edit</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Redo</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite preklicati zadnjo spremembo, izberite <menuchoice> <guimenu>Uredi</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Razveljavi</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Če želite "
"ponoviti zadnjo razveljavljeno spremembo, izberite <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Urejanje</guimenu><guimenuitem>Ponovno uveljavi</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1145
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To undo a change other than the last one, click on the <guibutton>Undo</"
"guibutton> button in the toolbar and hold the mouse button down. A list of "
"actions will be displayed from which you can choose the one to undo. If you "
"don't see the action which you are looking for, remember that you may need "
"to undo more recent changes first, which the desired change depends on. For "
"example, if you edited an alarm and then deleted it, you cannot undo the "
"edit until you have first undone the deletion."
msgstr ""
"Če želite preklicati spremembo, ki ni zadnja, kliknite gumb "
"<guibutton>Razveljavi</guibutton> v orodni vrstici in držite pritisnjen gumb "
"miške. Prikaže se seznam akcij, s katerega lahko izberete tisto, ki jo "
"želite preklicati. Če ne vidite želenega ukrepa, ne pozabite, da boste morda "
"morali najprej razveljaviti novejše spremembe, od katerih je odvisna želena "
"sprememba. Če ste na primer uredili alarm in ga nato izbrisali, ne morete "
"razveljaviti urejanja, dokler ne razveljavite izbrisa."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1154
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Redoing a change other than the last one can be done in a similar manner, "
"using the <guibutton>Redo</guibutton> toolbar button."
msgstr ""
"Ponovno izvedbo spremembe, ki ni bila zadnja, lahko izvedete na podoben "
"način, in sicer z gumbom <guibutton>Ponovno uveljavi</guibutton> v orodni "
"vrstici."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1162
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Alarm Edit Dialog"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno Uredi alarm"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1164
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Alarm Edit dialog enables you to view and edit an alarm. When you first "
"use &kalarm;, a simplified form of the dialog is displayed, with only a "
"small number of options visible. To see all options, click the "
"<guibutton>More Options</guibutton> button; to revert to the simplified "
"dialog, click the <guibutton>Less Options</guibutton> button. &kalarm; "
"always remembers your last display choice whenever the Alarm Edit dialog is "
"redisplayed."
msgstr ""
"V pogovornem oknu Uredi alarm si lahko ogledate in uredite alarm. Ob prvi "
"uporabi funkcije &kalarm; se prikaže poenostavljena oblika pogovornega okna, "
"v kateri je vidnih le nekaj možnosti. Če želite prikazati vse možnosti, "
"kliknite gumb <guibutton>Več Možnosti</guibutton>; če se želite vrniti na "
"poenostavljeno pogovorno okno, kliknite gumb <guibutton>Manj možnosti</"
"guibutton>. &kalarm; si vedno zapomni vašo zadnjo izbiro prikaza, kadar koli "
"se ponovno prikaže pogovorno okno urejanja alarmov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1173
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can configure the default values of many of the settings in the Alarm "
"Edit dialog using the <link linkend=\"preferences-edit\">Configuration "
"dialog's Edit tab</link>."
msgstr ""
"Privzete vrednosti številnih nastavitev v pogovornem oknu Urejanje alarmov "
"lahko nastavite z uporabo zavihka <link linkend=\"preferences-edit"
"\">Konfiguracija pogovornega okna Uredi</link>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1178
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the simplified Alarm Edit dialog"
msgstr "Zaslonska slika poenostavljenega pogovornega okna za urejanje alarmov"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1184
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Simplified Alarm Edit dialog for a display alarm</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Poenostavljeno pogovorno okno za urejanje alarma za alarm na "
"zaslonu</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1186
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Simplified Alarm Edit dialog for a display alarm</para>"
msgstr ""
"<para>Poenostavljeno pogovorno okno za urejanje alarma za alarm na zaslonu</"
"para>"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1191
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the Alarm Edit dialog showing all options"
msgstr ""
"Zaslonska slika pogovornega okna za urejanje alarma, ki prikazuje vse "
"možnosti"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1197
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>Alarm Edit dialog for a display alarm, showing all options</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Pogovorno okno za urejanje alarma zaslona, ki prikazuje vse "
"možnosti</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1199
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Alarm Edit dialog for a display alarm, showing all options</para>"
msgstr ""
"<para>Pogovorno okno za urejanje alarma za prikaz, ki prikazuje vse "
"možnosti</para>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1204
#, no-c-format
msgid "Alarm Name"
msgstr "Ime alarma"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1206
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can give a name to the alarm in the <guilabel>Alarm name</guilabel> "
"field. This is a convenience to help you identify the alarm more easily. You "
"do not have to enter a name, and it need not be unique."
msgstr ""
"V polju <guilabel>Ime alarma</guilabel> lahko alarma poimenujete. To je "
"pripomoček za lažjo prepoznavo alarma. Imena vam ni treba vnesti in ni "
"nujno, da je edinstveno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1211
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that this field is only displayed if the use of alarm names is enabled "
"in the <link linkend=\"preferences-general\">General</link> tab of the "
"Configuration dialog."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da je to polje prikazano le, če je uporaba imen alarmov "
"omogočena v zavihku <link linkend=\"preferences-general\">Splošno</link> "
"pogovornega okna Konfiguracija."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1219
#, no-c-format
msgid "Alarm Action"
msgstr "Dejanja alarma"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1221
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The controls in the <guilabel>Action</guilabel> group box vary depending on "
"the type of alarm being edited."
msgstr ""
"Nadzorni elementi v skupinskem polju <guilabel>Dejanja</guilabel> se "
"razlikujejo glede na vrsto alarma, ki ga urejate."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1225
#, no-c-format
msgid "Display Alarms"
msgstr "Prikazni alarmi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1227
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Display alarms display a window when the alarm triggers. Select the method "
"used to generate the alarm window contents, using the combo box at the top:"
msgstr ""
"Prikaz alarmov prikaže okno, ko se alarm sproži. V izbirnem oknu na vrhu "
"izberite metodo, ki se uporablja za ustvarjanje vsebine alarmnega okna:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1233
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Text message</guilabel> in order to enter an alarm message text "
"(which may include newlines) in the edit box."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Besedilo</guilabel>, če želite v urejevalno polje vnesti besedilo "
"alarmnega sporočila (ki lahko vključuje nove vrstice)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1238
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>File contents</guilabel> to enter the path or &URL; of a text or "
"image file whose contents are to be displayed in the alarm message. Use the "
"button beside the edit box to display a file selection dialog. The "
"<guilabel>Speak</guilabel> option is not available for this type of alarm."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Vsebina datoteke</guilabel> za vnos poti ali &URL; besedilne ali "
"slikovne datoteke, katere vsebina bo prikazana v alarmnem sporočilu. Za "
"prikaz pogovornega okna za izbiro datoteke uporabite gumb poleg polja za "
"urejanje. Možnost <guilabel>Govora</guilabel> za to vrsto alarma ni na voljo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1246
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Command output</guilabel> to specify that the alarm message text "
"will be generated by a command which is executed when the alarm triggers. "
"See <link linkend=\"command-alarm\">Command Alarms</link> below for details "
"of how to enter the command or command script to execute."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Izhod ukaza</guilabel> za določitev, da bo besedilo sporočila o "
"alarmu ustvarjeno z ukazom, ki se izvede ob sprožitvi alarma. Za podrobnosti "
"o vnosu ukaza ali skripte ukaza za izvedbo glejte <link linkend=\"command-"
"alarm\">Ukazni alarmi</link> spodaj."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1254
#, no-c-format
msgid "The controls available for display alarms are:"
msgstr "Za prikaz alarmov so na voljo naslednji upravljalni elementi:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1258
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Sound</guilabel> option allows you to select whether an "
"audible alarm should sound when the alarm message is displayed. Choose:"
msgstr ""
"Z možnostjo <guilabel>Zvok</guilabel> lahko izberete, ali naj se ob prikazu "
"alarmnega sporočila sproži zvočni alarm. Izberite:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1264
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>None</guilabel> to display the alarm silently."
msgstr "<guilabel>Brez</guilabel>, da se alarm prikaže tiho."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1268
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Beep</guilabel> to sound a beep."
msgstr "<guilabel>Pisk</guilabel> za zvočni signal."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1272
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Speak</guilabel> to have the alarm message spoken as well as being "
"displayed. This option is only available if &kalarm; was built with speech "
"enabled and you have the &Qt; Speech module installed and working."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Govor</guilabel>, če želite, da se alarmno sporočilo poleg prikaza "
"tudi govori. Ta možnost je na voljo le, če je bil program &kalarm; zgrajen z "
"omogočenim govorom in če imate nameščen in deluje modul &Qt; Speech."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1279
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Sound file</guilabel> to play an audio file. Use the button on the "
"right to display the Sound File dialog which lets you select a file to play "
"and set volume and repetition options. If you hover the mouse over the "
"selector, a tooltip will display the audio file currently selected."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Zvočna datoteka</guilabel> za predvajanje zvočne datoteke. Z "
"gumbom na desni strani prikažite pogovorno okno Zvočna datoteka, v katerem "
"lahko izberete datoteko za predvajanje ter nastavite glasnost in možnosti "
"ponavljanja. Če se z miško pomaknete nad izbirnik, se v opombi prikaže "
"trenutno izbrana zvočna datoteka."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1285
#, no-c-format
msgid "In the Sound File dialog:"
msgstr "V pogovornem oknu Zvočna datoteka:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1289
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter the sound file path, or use the button beside the edit box to display "
"a file selection dialog. You can listen to the selected file by clicking the "
"play button to the left of the edit field. That button then changes function "
"to allow you to stop playing when you have heard enough."
msgstr ""
"Vnesite pot do zvočne datoteke ali uporabite gumb poleg urejevalnega polja, "
"da prikažete pogovorno okno za izbiro datoteke. Izbrano datoteko lahko "
"poslušate tako, da kliknete gumb za predvajanje levo od polja za urejanje. "
"Ta gumb nato spremeni svojo funkcijo in omogoča, da preneha igrati, ko "
"slišite dovolj."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1297
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check <guilabel>Repeat</guilabel> to continually repeat the audio file for "
"as long as the alarm is displayed. (The alarm message window contains a "
"button to stop playing the sound should you need silence but still want to "
"display the alarm.)"
msgstr ""
"Označite možnost <guilabel>Ponovi</guilabel>, če želite zvočno datoteko "
"neprekinjeno ponavljati toliko časa, dokler je prikazan alarm. (Okno s "
"sporočilom alarma vsebuje gumb za zaustavitev predvajanja zvoka, če ga "
"želite utišati, vendar želite še vedno prikazati alarm.)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1304 index.docbook:1585
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check <guilabel>Volume</guilabel> and adjust the slider control if you want "
"to adjust the volume at which the audio file is played."
msgstr ""
"Če želite prilagoditi glasnost predvajanja zvočne datoteke, označite možnost "
"<guilabel>Nastavi glasnost</guilabel> in nastavite drsnik."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1310 index.docbook:1591
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the audio backend currently in use supports it, you can fade the volume. "
"Fading means to start playing the audio file at one volume and gradually "
"change to the final volume, over a specified time interval. The final volume "
"is that entered in <guilabel>Volume</guilabel> above. To enable fade, check "
"<guilabel>Fade</guilabel>, and then enter the fade period in seconds in the "
"<guilabel>Fade time</guilabel> field, and adjust the <guilabel>Initial "
"volume</guilabel> slider."
msgstr ""
"Če zvočno zaledje, ki je trenutno v uporabi, to podpira, lahko zmanjšate "
"glasnost. Pojemanje pomeni začetek predvajanja zvočne datoteke pri eni "
"glasnosti in postopno spreminjanje do končne glasnosti v določenem časovnem "
"intervalu. Končna glasnost je tista, ki je vnesena v <guilabel>Glasnost</"
"guilabel> zgoraj. Če želite omogočiti pojemanje, označite <guilabel>Pojemaj</"
"guilabel> in nato vnesite obdobje pojemanja v sekundah v polje <guilabel>Čas "
"pojemanja</guilabel> ter prilagodite drsnik <guilabel>Začetna glasnost</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1321
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can use the <guibutton>Try</guibutton> button to test out the selected "
"sound levels."
msgstr ""
"Z gumbom <guibutton>Poskusi</guibutton> lahko preizkusite izbrane ravni "
"zvoka."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1328
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the <guibutton>Font &amp; Color...</guibutton> button to select a font, "
"and foreground and background colors, for the alarm message. In the "
"<guilabel>Choose Alarm Font &amp; Color</guilabel> dialog, check "
"<guilabel>Use default font</guilabel> to display the message in whatever "
"font is configured as the default at the time the message is displayed. To "
"choose a specific font for the message, uncheck <guilabel>Use default font</"
"guilabel>. (The default font and colors can be set in the <link linkend="
"\"preferences-edit\">Configuration dialog</link>.)"
msgstr ""
"Z gumbom <guibutton>Pisava &amp; Barva...</guibutton> lahko izberete pisavo "
"ter barvo v ospredju in ozadju za alarmno sporočilo. V pogovornem oknu "
"<guilabel>Izberi pisavo &amp; barvo alarma</guilabel> potrdite možnost "
"<guilabel>Uporabi privzeto pisavo</guilabel>, da se sporočilo prikaže v "
"pisavi, ki je v času prikaza sporočila konfigurirana kot privzeta. Če želite "
"izbrati določeno pisavo za sporočilo, odstranite potrditev <guilabel>Uporabi "
"privzeto pisavo</guilabel>. (Privzeto pisavo in barve lahko nastavite v "
"<link linkend=\"preferences-edit\">Pogovorno okno konfiguracije</link>.)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1338
#, no-c-format
msgid "The selected colors are shown in the alarm message text entry field."
msgstr "Izbrane barve so prikazane v polju za vnos besedila alarma."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1343
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Display method</guilabel> option lets you select how to "
"display the alarm. Choose:"
msgstr ""
"Z možnostjo <guilabel>Metoda prikaza</guilabel> lahko izberete način prikaza "
"alarma. Izberite:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1348
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Window</guilabel> to display the alarm in a window. This option "
"allows the full range of options to be used when configuring the alarm."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Okno</guilabel> za prikaz alarma v oknu. Ta možnost omogoča "
"uporabo celotnega nabora možnosti pri konfiguriranju alarma."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1354
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Notification</guilabel> to use the standard notification system to "
"display the alarm message. Due to the limitations of the notification "
"system, the following alarm configuration options cannot be used with "
"notifications: setting font and color; setting an audio file to play when "
"the alarm is displayed; confirmation of alarm acknowledgement; automatic "
"closing of the display on expiry of the late-cancellation time."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Obvestilo</guilabel> za uporabo standardnega sistema obveščanja za "
"prikaz alarmnega sporočila. Zaradi omejitev sistema obveščanja z obvestili "
"ni mogoče uporabljati naslednjih možnosti konfiguracije alarma: nastavitev "
"pisave in barve; nastavitev zvočne datoteke, ki se predvaja ob prikazu "
"alarma; potrditev potrditve alarma; samodejno zaprtje zaslona ob izteku časa "
"pozne odpovedi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1364
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"See the <link linkend=\"message-display\">Alarm Message Display</link> "
"section for further details about how alarm messages are displayed."
msgstr ""
"Za več podrobnosti o prikazu alarmnih sporočil glejte razdelek <link linkend="
"\"message-display\">Prikaz alarmnega sporočila</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1370
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the <guibutton>Special Actions...</guibutton> button to specify shell "
"commands to execute before or after displaying the alarm. In the "
"<guilabel>Special Alarm Actions</guilabel> dialog:"
msgstr ""
"Z gumbom <guibutton>Posebna dejanja...</guibutton> določite ukaze lupine, ki "
"se izvedejo pred ali po prikazu alarma. V pogovornem oknu <guilabel>Posebna "
"dejanja alarmov</guilabel>:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1377
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <guilabel>Pre-alarm action</guilabel> field, enter a shell command to "
"execute before the alarm is displayed. Note that &kalarm; will wait for the "
"command to complete before displaying the alarm."
msgstr ""
"V polje <guilabel>Dejanje pred alarmom</guilabel> vnesite ukaz lupine, ki se "
"izvede pred prikazom alarma. Upoštevajte, da bo ukaz &kalarm; počakal, da se "
"ukaz zaključi, preden bo prikazal alarm."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1382
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A pre-alarm action is only executed once when the alarm message is initially "
"displayed, including when a reminder message is replaced by the actual alarm "
"message. It is <emphasis>not</emphasis> executed in any of the following "
"circumstances:"
msgstr ""
"Predalarmno dejanje se izvede samo enkrat, ko se alarmno sporočilo prikaže "
"na začetku, vključno s tem, ko opomnik nadomesti dejansko alarmno sporočilo. "
"<emphasis>Ne</emphasis> izvede se v kateri koli od naslednjih okoliščin:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1388
#, no-c-format
msgid "When a reminder message is displayed."
msgstr "Ko se prikaže sporočilo z opomnikom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1389
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When the message is redisplayed after deferring the alarm, unless "
"<guilabel>Execute for deferred alarms</guilabel> is checked."
msgstr ""
"Ko se sporočilo ponovno prikaže po odložitvi alarma, razen če je označena "
"možnost <guilabel>Izvedi za odložene alarme</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1392
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When the message was displaying at the time you logged off and is then "
"restored when you log back in."
msgstr ""
"Ko je bilo sporočilo prikazano v času odjave in se obnovi, ko se ponovno "
"prijavite."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1394
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When a recurring alarm triggers but the alarm message (or a deferred alarm "
"message) from a previous occurrence of the alarm is still visible; in other "
"words, when the previous occurrence of the alarm has not yet been "
"acknowledged."
msgstr ""
"Ko se sproži ponavljajoči se alarm, vendar je alarmno sporočilo (ali "
"odloženo alarmno sporočilo) iz prejšnjega pojava alarma še vedno vidno; z "
"drugimi besedami, ko prejšnji pojav alarma še ni bil potrjen."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1400
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The pre-alarm action can be used to control whether to display the alarm "
"message:"
msgstr ""
"S predalarmnim dejanjem lahko določite, ali naj se prikaže alarmno sporočilo:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1404
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check <guilabel>Cancel alarm on error</guilabel> to cancel the alarm if the "
"pre-alarm command returns an error status. This will prevent the alarm "
"message from being displayed, and any post-alarm action from being executed."
msgstr ""
"Označite <guilabel>Ob napaki prekliči alarm</guilabel>, da prekličete alarm, "
"če ukaz za predalarm vrne status napake. S tem preprečite prikaz alarmnega "
"sporočila in izvedbo vseh ukrepov po alarmu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1409
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Normally, if the pre-alarm command returns an error, an error message is "
"displayed and an error indication is shown in the alarm list. These error "
"notifications can be prevented by checking <guilabel>Do not notify errors</"
"guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Če ukaz za predalarm vrne napako, se običajno prikaže sporočilo o napaki, na "
"seznamu alarmov pa se prikaže oznaka napake. Ta obvestila o napakah lahko "
"preprečite tako, da preverite možnost <guilabel>Ne obveščaj o napakah</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1417
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <guilabel>Post-alarm action</guilabel> field, enter a shell command "
"to execute when the alarm is acknowledged (whether by clicking "
"<guibutton>Close</guibutton> or by using the close button in the window's "
"titlebar). It is <emphasis>not</emphasis> executed in any of the following "
"circumstances:"
msgstr ""
"V polje <guilabel>Dejanje po alarmu</guilabel> vnesite ukaz lupine, ki se "
"izvede, ko je alarm potrjen (s klikom na <guibutton>Prekliči</guibutton> ali "
"z uporabo gumba za zapiranje v naslovni vrstici okna). <emphasis>Ne</"
"emphasis> izvede se v kateri koli od naslednjih okoliščin:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1424
#, no-c-format
msgid "When a reminder message is closed."
msgstr "Ko je sporočilo opomnika zaprto."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1425
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you defer the alarm, except when the deferred alarm is finally "
"acknowledged."
msgstr "Ko odložite alarm, razen ko je odloženi alarm dokončno potrjen."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1427
#, no-c-format
msgid "When the alarm message is closed due to logging out."
msgstr "Ko se alarmno sporočilo zapre zaradi odjave."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1433
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"See <link linkend=\"command-alarm\">Command Alarms</link> below for details "
"of how shell commands are executed."
msgstr ""
"Za podrobnosti o izvajanju ukazov lupine glejte <link linkend=\"command-alarm"
"\">Odredbe za ukaze</link> spodaj."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1441
#, no-c-format
msgid "Command Alarms"
msgstr "Ukazni alarmi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1443
#, no-c-format
msgid "Command alarms execute a command without displaying any alarm message."
msgstr ""
"Alarmi ukazov izvedejo ukaz brez prikaza kakršnega koli alarmnega sporočila."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1446
#, no-c-format
msgid "This alarm type is not available if &kde; is running in kiosk mode."
msgstr ""
"Ta vrsta alarma ni na voljo, če se program &kde; izvaja v načinu kiosk."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1449
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When the command is executed, the environment variable <envar>KALARM_UID</"
"envar> contains the event UID for the alarm. Note that when the command is "
"executed from the Alarm Edit dialog's <guibutton>Try</guibutton> button, "
"<envar>KALARM_UID</envar> will be blank if it is a new alarm, or if the "
"alarm has been modified in the dialog, because the alarm only acquires a UID "
"when it is saved in the alarm calendar."
msgstr ""
"Ko se ukaz izvrši, okoljska spremenljivka <envar>KALARM_UID</envar> vsebuje "
"UID dogodka za alarm. Upoštevajte, da bo pri izvajanju ukaza iz gumba "
"<guibutton>Poskusi</guibutton> pogovornega okna Urejanje alarma "
"<envar>KALARM_UID</envar> prazen, če gre za nov alarm ali če je bil alarm "
"spremenjen v pogovornem oknu, saj alarm dobi UID šele, ko je shranjen v "
"koledar alarmov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1457
#, no-c-format
msgid "The controls available for command alarms are:"
msgstr "Za alarmne ukaze so na voljo naslednji upravljalni elementi:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1461
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Enter a script</guilabel> check box lets you choose whether to "
"enter a shell command line or a script."
msgstr ""
"S potrditvenim poljem <guilabel>Vnesite skript</guilabel> lahko izberete, "
"ali želite vnesti ukazno vrstico lupine ali skripto."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1464
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is unchecked, you can enter a shell command line to execute. "
"The command is passed straight to the default shell (defined by the "
"<envar>SHELL</envar> environment variable), and may include whatever "
"options, parameters, piped commands, &etc; are permitted by the shell in a "
"single line command."
msgstr ""
"Če ta možnost ni označena, lahko vnesete ukazno vrstico lupine, ki se "
"izvede. Ukaz se posreduje neposredno privzeti lupini (opredeljeni z okoljsko "
"spremenljivko <envar>SHELL</envar>) in lahko vključuje vse možnosti, "
"parametre, cevovodne ukaze in drugo, kar lupina dovoljuje v enovrstičnem "
"ukazu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1470
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is checked, you can enter the text of a script to execute. "
"Remember to include a first line such as <literal>#!/bin/bash</literal> to "
"ensure that the correct command interpreter is invoked."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost označena, lahko vnesete besedilo skripte, ki se izvede. Ne "
"pozabite vključiti prve vrstice, kot je <literal>#!/bin/bash</literal>, da "
"zagotovite, da se sproži pravilen prevajalnik ukazov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1476
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the command returns an error, an error message is normally displayed, and "
"an error indication is shown in the alarm list. The error notification "
"message can be prevented by checking <guilabel>Do not notify errors</"
"guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Če ukaz vrne napako, se običajno prikaže sporočilo o napaki, na seznamu "
"alarmov pa je prikazana oznaka napake. Sporočilo o napaki lahko preprečite "
"tako, da preverite možnost <guilabel>Ne obveščaj o napakah</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1482
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the <guilabel>Command Output</guilabel> group box to specify what you "
"want to be done with any terminal output which the command produces when it "
"executes."
msgstr ""
"V skupinskem polju <guilabel>Izhod ukaza</guilabel> lahko določite, kaj "
"želite narediti z izhodnimi podatki terminala, ki jih ukaz ustvari med "
"izvajanjem."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1488
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check <guilabel>Execute in terminal window</guilabel> to cause the command "
"to be executed in a terminal window. You can choose which type of terminal "
"window should be used in the <link linkend=\"preferences-general"
"\">Configuration dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"Označite možnost <guilabel>Izvedi v terminalskem oknu</guilabel>, da se ukaz "
"izvede v terminalskem oknu. V pogovornem oknu <link linkend=\"preferences-"
"general\">Pogovorno okno za konfiguracijo</link> lahko izberete, katera "
"vrsta terminalskega okna naj se uporabi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1495
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check <guilabel>Log to file</guilabel> to save the command's output in a "
"file. The output, prefixed by a heading showing the time at which the "
"command was scheduled to run, will be appended to any existing contents of "
"the file. Enter the file name in the edit box, or use the button beside the "
"edit box to display a file selection dialog."
msgstr ""
"Označite možnost <guilabel>Beleži v datoteko</guilabel>, če želite izpis "
"ukaza shraniti v datoteko. Izpis, pred katerim je naslov, ki prikazuje čas, "
"ko je bil ukaz načrtovan za izvedbo, bo dodan obstoječi vsebini datoteke. V "
"urejevalno polje vnesite ime datoteke ali uporabite gumb poleg urejevalnega "
"polja, da prikažete pogovorno okno za izbiro datoteke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1504
#, no-c-format
msgid "Check <guilabel>Discard</guilabel> to throw away the command's output."
msgstr "Označite <guilabel>Zavrzi</guilabel>, če želite izpis ukaza zavreči."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1513
#, no-c-format
msgid "Email Alarms"
msgstr "E-poštni alarmi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1515
#, no-c-format
msgid "Email alarms send an email without displaying any alarm message."
msgstr "E-poštni alarmi pošljejo e-pošto, ne da bi prikazali sporočilo alarma."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1518
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Fill in the recipients' addresses, the email subject line and the message "
"body in the three edit fields. Use the button beside the addressee edit box "
"to display your &kde; address book from which you can select email "
"recipients. (Note that the button is only shown if &kalarm;'s <link linkend="
"\"akonadi-plugin\">Akonadi plugin</link> is installed and enabled.) "
"Attachments may be added using the <guibutton>Add...</guibutton> button. "
"Note that attached files must still exist when the alarm is triggered; no "
"copy is stored at the time the alarm is configured. To remove an attachment, "
"highlight it in the drop-down list and click the <guibutton>Remove</"
"guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"V tri polja za urejanje vnesite naslove prejemnikov, predmet e-pošte in "
"vsebino sporočila. Z gumbom poleg polja za urejanje naslovnika prikažite "
"svoj imenik, iz katerega lahko izberete prejemnike e-pošte. (Upoštevajte, da "
"je gumb prikazan le, če je nameščen in omogočen <link linkend=\"akonadi-"
"plugin\">Vtičnik Akonadi</link>.) Priloge lahko dodate z gumbom "
"<guibutton>Dodaj...</guibutton>. Upoštevajte, da morajo priložene datoteke "
"ob sprožitvi alarma še vedno obstajati; ob konfiguriranju alarma se kopija "
"ne shrani. Če želite odstraniti priponko, jo označite na spustnem seznamu in "
"kliknite gumb <guibutton>Odstrani</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1531 index.docbook:1563
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set the following options:"
msgstr "Nastavite naslednje možnosti:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1535
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>From</guilabel> combo box allows you to select which &kmail; "
"identity to use as your email address for sending the email. This option "
"only appears if your <guilabel>From</guilabel> email address in the <link "
"linkend=\"preferences-email\">Configuration dialog</link> is set to "
"<guilabel>Use &kmail; identities</guilabel>. Otherwise your email address is "
"preset in the <link linkend=\"preferences-email\">Configuration dialog</"
"link>, rendering this option inapplicable."
msgstr ""
"V izbirnem polju <guilabel>Od</guilabel> lahko izberete identiteto &kmail;, "
"ki jo želite uporabiti kot e-poštni naslov za pošiljanje e-pošte. Ta možnost "
"se prikaže le, če je vaš <guilabel>Od</guilabel> e-poštni naslov v <link "
"linkend=\"preferences-email\">Pogovorno okno konfiguracije</link> nastavljen "
"na <guilabel>Uporabi &kmail; identitete</guilabel>. V nasprotnem primeru je "
"vaš e-poštni naslov vnaprej nastavljen v <link linkend=\"preferences-email"
"\">Pogovorno okno za konfiguracijo</link>, zato ta možnost ni uporabna."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1547
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check <guilabel>Copy email to self</guilabel> to send a blind copy of the "
"email to yourself when the alarm is triggered. The email address to which "
"the copy will be sent may be set in the <link linkend=\"preferences-email"
"\">Configuration dialog</link>, the default being your email address set in "
"&kmail;."
msgstr ""
"Označite možnost <guilabel>Pošlji kopijo e-pošte sebi</guilabel>, da si ob "
"sprožitvi alarma pošljete slepo kopijo e-pošte. E-poštni naslov, na katerega "
"bo poslana kopija, lahko nastavite v <link linkend=\"preferences-email"
"\">Pogovoru za konfiguracijo</link>, pri čemer je privzeto vaš e-poštni "
"naslov, nastavljen v &kmail;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1558
#, no-c-format
msgid "Audio Alarms"
msgstr "Zvočni alarmi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1560
#, no-c-format
msgid "Audio alarms play an audio file without displaying any alarm message."
msgstr ""
"Zvočni alarmi predvajajo zvočno datoteko brez prikaza alarmnega sporočila."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1567
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter the sound file path, or use the button beside the edit box to display "
"a file selection dialog."
msgstr ""
"Vnesite pot do zvočne datoteke ali uporabite gumb poleg urejevalnega polja, "
"da prikažete pogovorno okno za izbiro datoteke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1572
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check <guilabel>Repeat</guilabel> to continually repeat the audio file until "
"the <guilabel>Stop Play</guilabel> option is selected. To stop playing the "
"file, select the <menuchoice><guimenu>Actions</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Stop "
"Play</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu option, or <mousebutton>Right</"
"mousebutton> click on the system tray icon and choose "
"<menuchoice><guimenuitem>Stop Play</guimenuitem></menuchoice> from the "
"context menu. If you wish, you can set up a global shortcut key for this "
"action."
msgstr ""
"Označite možnost <guilabel>Ponovi</guilabel>, če želite zvočno datoteko "
"nenehno ponavljati, dokler ne izberete možnosti <guilabel>Ustavi "
"predvajanje</guilabel>. Če želite ustaviti predvajanje datoteke, izberite "
"možnost menija <menuchoice><guimenu>Dejanja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Ustavi "
"Predvajanje</guimenuitem></menuchoice> ali <mousebutton>Desno</mousebutton> "
"kliknite ikono v sistemski vrstici in v kontekstnem meniu izberite "
"<menuchoice><guimenuitem>Ustavi Predvajanje</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Če "
"želite, lahko za to dejanje nastavite globalno bližnjico."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1605
#, no-c-format
msgid "Deferral and Skipping"
msgstr "Odlog in preskakovanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1607
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the alarm is a recurring alarm and it was deferred after it was last "
"displayed, the <guilabel>Deferred / Skipped Alarm</guilabel> group box shows "
"the time the alarm was deferred to. <guibutton>Change...</guibutton> "
"displays a dialog which allows you to change the deferred time or to cancel "
"the deferral."
msgstr ""
"Če je alarm ponavljajoči se alarm in je bil odložen po zadnjem prikazu, "
"skupinsko polje <guilabel>Odloženi / Preskočeni alarm</guilabel> prikazuje "
"čas, na katerega je bil alarm odložen. <guibutton>Spremeni...</guibutton> "
"prikaže pogovorno okno, ki vam omogoča, da spremenite čas odloga ali "
"prekličete odlog."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1613
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the alarm is a recurring alarm and it is currently being skipped (see "
"<link linkend=\"skipping\">Skipping Individual Alarms</link>), the "
"<guilabel>Deferred / Skipped Alarm</guilabel> group box shows the next time "
"the alarm will trigger after being skipped, &ie; the time at which it will "
"resume normal operation. <guibutton>Cancel skip</guibutton> will cancel "
"skipping the alarm."
msgstr ""
"Če je alarm ponavljajoč se alarm in se trenutno preskakuje (glejte <link "
"linkend=\"skipping\">Preskakovanje posameznih alarmov</link>), skupinsko "
"polje <guilabel>Odloženi / Preskočeni alarm</guilabel> prikazuje naslednjič, "
"ko se bo alarm sprožil po preskoku, &ie; čas, ko bo nadaljeval z normalnim "
"delovanjem. <guibutton>Prekliči preskok</guibutton> prekličete preskakovanje "
"alarma."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1620
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you make any changes to the alarm's start time or recurrence details, "
"skipping is automatically canceled and the skip time is no longer displayed."
msgstr ""
"Če spremenite čas začetka ali podrobnosti ponavljanja alarma, se "
"preskakovanje samodejno prekliče in se čas preskakovanja ne prikazuje več."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1624
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that changes to deferral and skipping take effect when <guibutton>OK</"
"guibutton> is clicked."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da spremembe odloga in preskakovanja začnejo veljati, ko "
"kliknete <guibutton>V redu</guibutton>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1630
#, no-c-format
msgid "Time"
msgstr "Čas"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1632
#, no-c-format
msgid "In the <guilabel>Time</guilabel> group box, select either"
msgstr "V polju skupine <guilabel>Čas</guilabel> izberite"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1636
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>At date/time</guilabel> to enter the date and time when the alarm "
"is to be triggered. Check <guilabel>Any time</guilabel> if you want to "
"specify only a date for the alarm: in this case the alarm will be displayed "
"at the first opportunity on or after the configured start-of-day time, on "
"the specified date. (<link linkend=\"preferences-time\">Configuring &kalarm;"
"</link> describes how to set the start-of-day time.)"
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Na datum/čas</guilabel> za vnos datuma in ure, ko naj se sproži "
"alarm. Označite <guilabel>Poljuben čas</guilabel>, če želite za alarm "
"določiti samo datum: v tem primeru se bo alarm prikazal ob prvi priložnosti "
"ob ali po nastavljenem času začetka dneva na določen datum. (<link linkend="
"\"preferences-time\">Konfiguriranje &kalarm;</link> opisuje, kako nastaviti "
"čas začetka dneva.)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1644
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For a non-recurring alarm, the date/time which you enter must be in the "
"future, or if you enter only a date it must be today or later. For a "
"recurring alarm, there are no such restrictions since the start date/time "
"will be automatically adjusted to the first recurrence due after the current "
"time."
msgstr ""
"Za enkratni alarm mora biti vneseni datum/čas v prihodnosti, če vnesete samo "
"datum, pa mora biti danes ali pozneje. Za ponavljajoči se alarm ni takšnih "
"omejitev, saj se začetni datum/čas samodejno prilagodi prvemu ponovnemu "
"dogodku po trenutnem času."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1652
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Time from now</guilabel> to enter how long after now (in hours and "
"minutes) the alarm should be triggered."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Čas od zdaj</guilabel> za vnos časa, po katerem naj se sproži "
"alarm (v urah in minutah)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1657
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If desired, choose a time zone to apply to the alarm. This time zone is used "
"for all dates and times relating to this alarm, including recurrence and "
"exception dates and times. Normally, you should leave the time zone controls "
"unchanged unless you have a good reason to change them."
msgstr ""
"Po želji izberite časovni pas, ki ga želite uporabiti za alarm. Ta časovni "
"pas se uporablja za vse datume in ure, povezane s tem alarmom, vključno z "
"datumi in urami ponovitve in izjeme. Običajno morate pustiti kontrole "
"časovnega pasu nespremenjene, razen če imate dober razlog, da jih spremenite."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1663
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The time zone controls are displayed only when the selected time zone is "
"different from the default time zone set in the <link linkend=\"preferences-"
"time\">Configuration dialog</link>, or if you click the <guibutton>Time "
"Zone...</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Krmilniki časovnega pasu se prikažejo le, če se izbrani časovni pas "
"razlikuje od privzetega časovnega pasu, nastavljenega v <link linkend="
"\"preferences-time\">Pogovorno okno Konfiguracija</link>, ali če kliknete "
"gumb <guibutton>Časovni pas...</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1670
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the combo box, choose the time zone which this alarm is to use. When "
"creating a new alarm, this is initially set to the time zone selected in the "
"<link linkend=\"preferences-time\">Configuration dialog</link>, which will "
"be your computer's time zone unless you have changed it."
msgstr ""
"V izbirnem polju izberite časovni pas, ki ga bo uporabljal ta alarm. Pri "
"ustvarjanju novega alarma je ta sprva nastavljen na časovni pas, izbran v "
"<link linkend=\"preferences-time\">Pogovorno okno za konfiguracijo</link>, "
"ki bo časovni pas vašega računalnika, razen če ste ga spremenili."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1678
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select <guilabel>System time zone</guilabel> if you want to use the local "
"computer time zone (on whichever computer &kalarm; happens to be running on "
"at the time)."
msgstr ""
"Izberite <guilabel>Sistemski časovni pas</guilabel>, če želite uporabiti "
"lokalni časovni pas računalnika (na katerem koli računalniku, na katerem je "
"v tistem trenutku nameščen program &kalarm;)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1687
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reminder"
msgstr "Opomnik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1689
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For a display alarm, check <guilabel>Reminder</guilabel> if you want to "
"display a reminder either before or after the main alarm and each of its "
"recurrences (if any). Enter how long in advance or afterwards, using the "
"edit controls beside the check box. Note that if the alarm recurs, the "
"reminder period is normally limited to being less than the recurrence or sub-"
"repetition interval."
msgstr ""
"Za Prikazni alarm potrdite možnost <guilabel>Opomnik</guilabel>, če želite "
"prikazati opomnik pred ali po glavnem alarmu in vseh njegovih ponovitvah (če "
"obstajajo). Z gumbi za urejanje poleg potrditvenega polja vnesite, koliko "
"časa vnaprej ali pozneje. Če se alarm ponovi, je obdobje opomnika običajno "
"krajše od intervala ponovitve ali pod-ponovitve."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1696
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Reminders are not displayed for sub-repetitions within a recurrence. "
"Reminders are only shown for each main recurrence of the alarm."
msgstr ""
"Opomniki niso prikazani za pod-ponovitve znotraj ponovitve. Opomniki se "
"prikažejo samo za vsako glavno ponovitev alarma."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1700
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the alarm recurs, check <guilabel>Reminder for first recurrence only</"
"guilabel> if you only want a reminder for the alarm's first recurrence. If "
"this is checked, and it is an advance reminder, the reminder period is not "
"subject to the normal limit of being less than the recurrence or sub-"
"repetition interval."
msgstr ""
"Če se alarm ponavlja, označite možnost <guilabel>Opomnik samo za prvo "
"ponovitev</guilabel>, če želite opomnik samo za prvo ponovitev alarma. Če je "
"to označeno in gre za vnaprejšnji opomnik, za obdobje opomnika ne velja "
"običajna omejitev, da je krajše od intervala ponovitve ali ponovitve."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1710
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cancelation"
msgstr "Preklic"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1712
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The late-cancelation options determine how an alarm is treated after its "
"scheduled time:"
msgstr ""
"Možnosti pozne preklica določajo, kako se obravnava alarm po izteku "
"načrtovanega časa:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1717
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Cancel if late</guilabel> check box determines what happens if "
"the alarm cannot be triggered at its scheduled time."
msgstr ""
"Označevalno polje <guilabel>Prekliči, če je prepozno</guilabel> določa, kaj "
"se zgodi, če alarma ni mogoče sprožiti ob načrtovanem času."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1720
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check this box to cancel the alarm if it cannot be triggered within a "
"specified time period after the right time. The time period is selected "
"using controls which appear when you check the box. For example, if you "
"enter a time period of 1 hour, the alarm will be triggered at the first "
"opportunity up to an hour after it is due, but if it cannot be triggered "
"within an hour its activation will be canceled."
msgstr ""
"Označite to polje, če želite preklicati alarm, če ga ni mogoče sprožiti v "
"določenem časovnem obdobju po pravem času. Časovno obdobje izberete s "
"kontrolnimi elementi, ki se prikažejo, ko potrdite polje. Če na primer "
"vnesete časovno obdobje 1 ure, se bo alarm sprožil ob prvi priložnosti do "
"ene ure po roku, če pa ga ne bo mogoče sprožiti v eni uri, bo njegova "
"aktivacija preklicana."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1728
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The lateness of date-only alarms, &ie; ones for which the <guilabel>Any "
"time</guilabel> option is selected, is calculated from the start-of-day time "
"on the alarm's scheduled date."
msgstr ""
"Poznost alarmov, &ie; ki so vezani samo na datum, in alarmov, za katere je "
"izbrana možnost <guilabel>Katerikoli čas</guilabel>, se izračuna od časa "
"začetka dneva na načrtovani datum alarma."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1732
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Leave the box unchecked to trigger the alarm at the first opportunity "
"starting at the scheduled time, regardless of how late it is."
msgstr ""
"Polje pustite neodkljukano, če želite sprožiti alarm ob prvi priložnosti, ki "
"se začne ob načrtovani uri, ne glede na to, koliko je že pozno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1736
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An alarm can only be triggered while you are logged in, and while both X and "
"&kalarm; are running."
msgstr ""
"Alarm lahko sprožite le, če ste prijavljeni in če sta vklopljena programa X "
"in &kalarm;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1741
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check <guilabel>Auto-close window after this time</guilabel> if you want the "
"alarm window to be automatically closed if it is still showing at the expiry "
"of the late-cancelation time."
msgstr ""
"Označite možnost <guilabel>Samodejno zapri okno po tem času</guilabel>, če "
"želite, da se okno alarma samodejno zapre, če je ob izteku časa pozne "
"preklica še vedno prikazano."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1750
#, no-c-format
msgid "Recurrence"
msgstr "Ponovitev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1752
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specify whether or how the alarm should be repeated using the "
"<guilabel>Recurrence</guilabel> tab."
msgstr ""
"V zavihku <guilabel>Ponovitev</guilabel> določite, ali naj se alarm ponovi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1755
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The alarm's basic repetition characteristics are displayed for convenience "
"in the title of the <guilabel>Recurrence</guilabel> tab. The recurrence "
"interval is shown first, followed by any sub-repetition interval set up "
"using the <guibutton>Sub-Repetition</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Osnovne značilnosti ponavljanja alarma so zaradi priročnosti prikazane v "
"naslovu zavihka <guilabel>Ponovitev</guilabel>. Najprej je prikazan interval "
"ponavljanja, nato pa morebitni interval pod-ponavljanja, nastavljen z gumbom "
"<guibutton>Pod-Ponavljanje</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1761
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <guilabel>Recurrence Rule</guilabel> group box, set the recurrence "
"type or time period as follows:"
msgstr ""
"V polju skupine <guilabel>Pravilo ponavljanja</guilabel> nastavite vrsto "
"ponavljanja ali časovno obdobje, kot sledi:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1765
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To trigger the alarm once only, select <guilabel>No recurrence</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite alarm sprožiti samo enkrat, izberite <guilabel>Brez ponovitev</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1768
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select <guilabel>At login</guilabel> to trigger the alarm whenever you log "
"in, until its scheduled end time. Then, at its scheduled end time it will "
"finally be triggered one last time. (Note that an alarm repeated at login "
"will also be triggered any time you restart &kalarm;.)"
msgstr ""
"Izberite <guilabel>Pri prijavi</guilabel>, če želite sprožiti alarm, kadar "
"koli se prijavite, do načrtovanega časa zaključka. Nato se ob načrtovanem "
"času zaključka še zadnjič sproži. (Upoštevajte, da se alarm, ki se ponovi ob "
"prijavi, sproži tudi vsakič, ko znova zaženete &kalarm;.)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1775
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To make the alarm recur at regular intervals, select one of the time period "
"types and then enter in the <guilabel>Recur every</guilabel> box how many "
"time periods should elapse between recurrences. For example, to repeat every "
"fortnight, you could select <guilabel>Daily</guilabel> and enter a value of "
"14, or select <guilabel>Weekly</guilabel> and enter a value of 2. Depending "
"on the time period type selected, you may have further options:"
msgstr ""
"Če želite, da se alarm ponavlja v rednih časovnih presledkih, izberite eno "
"od vrst časovnih obdobij in nato v polje <guilabel>Ponovi vsakih</guilabel> "
"vnesite, koliko časovnih obdobij naj preteče med ponovitvami. Če želite na "
"primer ponoviti vsakih štirinajst dni, lahko izberete <guilabel>Dnevno</"
"guilabel> in vnesete vrednost 14 ali izberete <guilabel>Tedensko</guilabel> "
"in vnesete vrednost 2. Glede na izbrano vrsto časovnega obdobja so na voljo "
"dodatne možnosti:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1786
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For a daily recurrence, check each day in the week on which the alarm will "
"be allowed to trigger. The alarm will recur at the specified frequency, but "
"whenever it triggers on an unselected day of the week it will be suppressed."
msgstr ""
"Za dnevno ponavljanje označite vsak dan v tednu, ko se alarm lahko sproži. "
"Alarm se bo ponavljal z določeno frekvenco, vendar bo vsakič preprečen, ko "
"bi se sprožil na neizbran dan v tednu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1793
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For a weekly recurrence, check each day in the week on which you wish to "
"trigger the alarm."
msgstr ""
"Za tedensko ponavljanje označite vsak dan v tednu, ko želite sprožiti alarm."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1798
#, no-c-format
msgid "For a monthly recurrence, you may select either:"
msgstr "Za mesečno ponavljanje lahko izberete eno od naslednjih možnosti:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1800
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A fixed day in the month or the last day of the month. Note that if you "
"select for example the 31st day in the month, the alarm will not trigger in "
"any month with less than 31 days."
msgstr ""
"Fiksni dan v mesecu ali zadnji dan v mesecu. Upoštevajte, da če izberete na "
"primer 31. dan v mesecu, se alarm ne bo sprožil v nobenem mesecu z manj kot "
"31 dnevi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1805
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A position in the month, &eg; the second Tuesday or the last Friday of the "
"month."
msgstr "Položaj v mesecu, &eg; drugi torek ali zadnji petek v mesecu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1812
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For a yearly recurrence, you may select either a fixed day in the month or a "
"position in the month, as described for monthly recurrences. Check each "
"month of the year in which you wish to trigger the alarm."
msgstr ""
"Za letno ponavljanje lahko izberete fiksni dan v mesecu ali položaj v "
"mesecu, kot je opisano za mesečno ponavljanje. Označite vsak mesec v letu, v "
"katerem želite sprožiti alarm."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1817
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you set up a yearly recurrence for February 29th, you can specify how it "
"is to be handled in non-leap years by selecting the appropriate "
"<guilabel>February 29th alarm in non-leap years</guilabel> option:"
msgstr ""
"Če nastavite letno ponavljanje za 29. februar, lahko z izbiro ustrezne "
"možnosti <guilabel> 29. februar v prestopnih letih</guilabel> določite, kako "
"naj se obravnava v prestopnih letih: položaj v mesecu (npr. zadnja sobota v "
"maju). Označite vsak mesec v letu, v katerem želite sprožiti alarm:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1824
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>None</guilabel>: the alarm will occur on February 29th in leap "
"years, but will be suppressed in non-leap years."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Brez</guilabel>: v prestopnih letih se alarm pojavi 29. februarja, "
"v neprestopnih letih pa je izključen."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1829
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>28 Feb</guilabel>: the alarm will occur on February 29th in leap "
"years, and on February 28th in non-leap years."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>28 Feb</guilabel>: alarm se v prestopnih letih pojavi 29. "
"februarja, v neprestopnih letih pa 28. februarja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1834
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>1 Mar</guilabel>: the alarm will occur on February 29th in leap "
"years, and on March 1st in non-leap years."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>1. marec</guilabel>: v prestopnih letih se alarm pojavi 29. "
"februarja, v neprestopnih letih pa 1. marca."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1842
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To set a daily alarm to occur only on weekdays, use a weekly recurrence and "
"check each weekday."
msgstr ""
"Če želite dnevni alarm nastaviti tako, da se bo pojavljal samo ob "
"delavnikih, uporabite tedensko ponavljanje in preverite vsak delavnik."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1848
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <guilabel>Recurrence End</guilabel> group box, set the overall "
"recurrence time span as follows:"
msgstr ""
"V skupinskem polju <guilabel>Konec ponavljanja</guilabel> nastavite skupni "
"časovni razpon ponovitve, kot sledi:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1852
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select <guilabel>No end</guilabel> to continue the repetitions indefinitely."
msgstr ""
"Izberite <guilabel>Brez konca</guilabel>, če želite nadaljevati s "
"ponavljanjem za nedoločen čas."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1855
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select <guilabel>End after</guilabel> to specify the total number of "
"occurrences of the alarm."
msgstr ""
"Izberite <guilabel>Končaj po</guilabel>, da določite skupno število "
"pojavitev alarma."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1858
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select <guilabel>End by</guilabel> to specify the date/time until which the "
"alarm will be repeated. Note that this uses the same time zone as the "
"alarm's start time."
msgstr ""
"Izberite <guilabel>Končaj do</guilabel>, da določite datum/čas, do katerega "
"se bo alarm ponavljal. Upoštevajte, da se pri tem uporablja isti časovni pas "
"kot čas začetka alarma."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1862
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The end date/time determines when the last main recurrence will be, but does "
"not limit sub-repetitions. If sub-repetitions are configured, they will "
"trigger as normal after the last main recurrence, regardless of the end date/"
"time."
msgstr ""
"Končni datum/čas določa, kdaj bo zadnje glavno ponavljanje, vendar ne "
"omejuje pod-ponovitev. Če so konfigurirane pod-ponovitve, se bodo sprožile "
"kot običajno po zadnji glavni ponovitvi, ne glede na končni datum/čas."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1869
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Exceptions</guilabel> group box allows you to exclude certain "
"date/times from the recurrence which you have set up. Note that these "
"controls are not shown in the simplified form of the Alarm Edit dialog: to "
"see them, click <guibutton>More Options</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Polje skupine <guilabel>Izjeme</guilabel> vam omogoča, da iz nastavljenega "
"ponavljanja izključite določene datume/čase. Upoštevajte, da ti gumbi niso "
"prikazani v poenostavljeni obliki pogovornega okna Urejanje alarmov: če jih "
"želite videti, kliknite <guibutton>Več možnosti</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1877
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The list of exceptions (&ie; excluded date/times) is shown on the left. To "
"add a new exception, enter a date on the right and press <guibutton>Add</"
"guibutton>. To change an exception, highlight it in the list, enter the new "
"date on the right and press <guibutton>Change</guibutton>. To delete an "
"exception, highlight it in the list and press <guibutton>Delete</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Seznam izjem (&ie; izločeni datum/čas) je prikazan na levi strani. Če želite "
"dodati novo izjemo, na desni strani vnesite datum in pritisnite "
"<guibutton>Dodaj</guibutton>. Če želite spremeniti izjemo, jo označite na "
"seznamu, na desni strani vnesite nov datum in pritisnite "
"<guibutton>Spremeni</guibutton>. Če želite izbrisati izjemo, jo označite na "
"seznamu in pritisnite <guibutton>Izbriši</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1886
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can restrict an alarm not to occur on holidays by checking "
"<guilabel>Exclude holidays</guilabel>. This does not change the way the "
"alarm is scheduled; it simply suppresses the alarm whenever it happens to "
"trigger on a holiday. You can select your holiday country or region in the "
"<link linkend=\"preferences-time\">Configuration dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"Z izbiro možnosti <guilabel>Izključi praznike</guilabel> lahko omejite, da "
"se alarm ne pojavi ob praznikih. To ne spremeni načina načrtovanja alarma, "
"temveč ga preprosto odpravi, kadar se sproži na praznik. Državo ali regijo "
"počitnic lahko izberete v <link linkend=\"preferences-time\">Pogovornem oknu "
"za konfiguracijo</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1895
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can restrict an alarm to occur only during working time by checking "
"<guilabel>Only during working hours</guilabel>. This does not change the way "
"the alarm is scheduled; it simply suppresses the alarm whenever it happens "
"to trigger outside working hours. Work days and working hours are set in the "
"<link linkend=\"preferences-time\">Configuration dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"Z izbiro možnosti <guilabel>Tudi med delovnim časom</guilabel> lahko "
"omejite, da se alarm pojavi samo med delovnim časom. To ne spremeni načina "
"načrtovanja alarma, temveč ga preprosto izključi, kadar se sproži zunaj "
"delovnega časa. Delovni dnevi in delovni čas so nastavljeni v <link linkend="
"\"preferences-time\">Pogovornem oknu konfiguracije</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1905
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sub-Repetition"
msgstr "Pod-ponavljanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1907
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can use the <guibutton>Sub-Repetition</guibutton> button to set up a "
"repetition within a repetition. In this case, each time the alarm is due as "
"specified in the main recurrence, instead of being triggered just once it is "
"triggered repeatedly in accordance with your sub-repetition specification. "
"For example, to set up an alarm which repeats every hour from noon to 6 pm "
"each Thursday, you would set up a weekly recurrence on Thursday at 12:00, "
"and use the Sub-Repetition dialog to specify an interval of 1 hour and "
"either a count of 6 or a duration of 6 hours."
msgstr ""
"Z gumbom <guibutton>Pod-ponavljanje</guibutton> lahko nastavite ponovitev "
"znotraj ponovitve. V tem primeru se alarm vsakič, ko zapade, kot je določeno "
"v glavnem ponavljanju, namesto da bi se sprožil samo enkrat, sproži večkrat "
"v skladu z vašo specifikacijo pod-ponavljanja. Če želite na primer nastaviti "
"alarm, ki se ponavlja vsako uro od poldneva do 18. ure vsak četrtek, "
"nastavite tedensko ponavljanje v četrtek ob 12:00 in v pogovornem oknu Pod-"
"ponovitev določite interval 1 ure in število 6 ali trajanje 6 ur."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1917
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sub-repetitions are only triggered after a main recurrence which actually "
"triggers. If a main recurrence is suppressed by an exception date/time or by "
"holiday or working time restrictions, the sub-repetitions for that instance "
"of the recurrence will not be triggered."
msgstr ""
"Podponovitve se sprožijo šele po glavni ponovitvi, ki se dejansko sproži. Če "
"glavno ponovitev prepreči datum/čas izjeme ali omejitve praznikov ali "
"delovnega časa, se podponovitve za to ponovitev ne bodo sprožale."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1923
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Individual sub-repetitions will also be suppressed if they occur at an "
"exception date/time, or during holiday or working time restrictions."
msgstr ""
"Posamezne podponovitve bodo prav tako preprečene, če se pojavijo na datum/"
"čas izjeme ali med omejitvami praznikov ali delovnega časa."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1927
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the Sub-Repetition dialog which is displayed when you click the "
"<guibutton>Sub-Repetition</guibutton> button, check <guilabel>Repeat every</"
"guilabel> to set up a repetition, or uncheck it to remove the repetition. If "
"<guilabel>Repeat every</guilabel> is checked, set up the repetition as "
"follows:"
msgstr ""
"V pogovornem oknu Pod-Ponavljanje, ki se prikaže, ko kliknete gumb "
"<guibutton>Pod-ponavljanje</guibutton>, označite <guilabel>Ponovi vsakih</"
"guilabel>, če želite nastaviti ponavljanje, ali ga odstranite, če želite "
"odstraniti ponavljanje. Če je označen <guilabel>Ponavljaj vsakič</guilabel>, "
"nastavite ponavljanje na naslednji način:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1934
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter the time interval between repetitions in the controls beside "
"<guilabel>Repeat every</guilabel>. Select the desired time units (&eg; "
"<guilabel>days</guilabel>) and then enter the number of units."
msgstr ""
"Časovni razmik med ponovitvami vnesite v kontrolne elemente poleg "
"<guilabel>Ponavljaj vsakič</guilabel>. Izberite želene časovne enote (&eg; "
"<guilabel>dni</guilabel>) in nato vnesite število enot."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1940
#, no-c-format
msgid "Specify either the repetition count or its duration:"
msgstr "Določite število ponovitev ali njihovo trajanje:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1944
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select <guilabel>Number of times</guilabel> to enter how many times the "
"alarm should be triggered after the main recurrence. So, for example, to "
"make the alarm occur 4 times at each main recurrence, &ie; 3 additional "
"times, you should enter 3 here."
msgstr ""
"Izberite <guilabel>Število ponovitev</guilabel>, da vnesete, kolikokrat naj "
"se alarm sproži po glavnem ponavljanju. Če želite na primer, da se alarm pri "
"vsakem glavnem ponovitvi pojavi 4-krat, &ie; 3-krat dodatno, morate tukaj "
"vnesti 3."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1951
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select <guilabel>Duration</guilabel> to enter the total time period during "
"which the alarm should be repeated. This need not be an exact multiple of "
"the repetition interval; it will automatically be rounded down when you "
"click <guibutton>OK</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Izberite <guilabel>Trajanje</guilabel> in vnesite skupno časovno obdobje, v "
"katerem naj se alarm ponovi. Ni nujno, da je to natančen večkratnik "
"intervala ponavljanja; ko kliknete <guibutton>OK</guibutton>, se samodejno "
"zaokroži navzdol."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1961
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To prevent overlapping sub-repetitions for the same alarm, a sub-"
"repetition's duration is restricted to be less than the longest interval "
"between main recurrences. Each time the alarm recurs as specified in the "
"main recurrence, any still active sub-repetition which started at the "
"previous recurrence is automatically cancelled."
msgstr ""
"Da bi preprečili prekrivanje podponudb za isti alarm, je trajanje podponudbe "
"omejeno tako, da je krajše od najdaljšega intervala med glavnimi "
"ponovitvami. Vsakič, ko se alarm ponovi, kot je določeno v glavnem "
"ponavljanju, se samodejno prekličejo vsa še vedno aktivna podponavljanja, ki "
"so se začela ob prejšnjem ponavljanju."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1972
#, no-c-format
msgid "Other Controls"
msgstr "Drugi nadzori"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1974
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the system configuration allows multiple alarms to wake the system from "
"suspension, you can select <guilabel>Wake from suspend</guilabel> to wake "
"the system if it is currently suspended when the alarm becomes due. This "
"function is not available for date-only alarms because their time is not "
"defined. See <link linkend=\"wake-suspend\">Wake From Suspend</link> for "
"more information."
msgstr ""
"Če sistemska konfiguracija dovoljuje več alarmov, da prebudijo sistem iz "
"začasne zaustavitve, lahko izberete <guilabel>Prebudi iz začasne "
"zaustavitve</guilabel>, da prebudite sistem, če je trenutno začasno "
"zaustavljen, ko pride do alarma. Ta funkcija ni na voljo za alarme samo z "
"datumom, ker njihov čas ni določen. Za več informacij glejte <link linkend="
"\"wake-suspend\">Prebujanje iz stanja mirovanja</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1982
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For display alarms, the <guilabel>Confirm acknowledgment</guilabel> check "
"box lets you specify whether you will be prompted for confirmation when you "
"close the alarm message window. This may be used as a safeguard against "
"accidental acknowledgment of alarms."
msgstr ""
"Pri prikaznih alarmih lahko s potrditvenim poljem <guilabel>Potrdi "
"seznanjenost</guilabel> določite, ali boste ob zaprtju okna z alarmnim "
"sporočilom pozvani k potrditvi. To se lahko uporablja kot varovalo pred "
"naključnim potrditvijo alarmov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1988
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Display alarms are normally suspended while notifications are inhibited for "
"the desktop, and do not display on top of full screen applications. To "
"override these restrictions and always display the alarm if at all possible, "
"select the <guilabel>Never inhibit alarm</guilabel> check box. Note that the "
"ability to display messages over full screen applications may depend on your "
"window manager, and currently only the X11 windowing system allows this."
msgstr ""
"Prikaz alarmov je običajno začasno zaustavljen, ko so obvestila za namizje "
"onemogočena, in se ne prikazujejo čez celozaslonske aplikacije. Če želite "
"preglasiti te omejitve in vedno prikazovati alarm, če je le mogoče, izberite "
"potrditveno polje <guilabel>Nikoli ne onemogoči alarmov</guilabel>. "
"Upoštevajte, da je možnost prikaza sporočil čez celozaslonske aplikacije "
"lahko odvisna od vašega upravljalnika oken, trenutno pa to omogoča samo "
"okenski sistem X11."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1997
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select <guilabel>Show in &korganizer;</guilabel> to add the alarm to "
"&korganizer;'s active calendar, where it will appear as an event without an "
"alarm. This option allows you to track alarms in &korganizer; while still "
"making use of &kalarm;'s functions."
msgstr ""
"Izberite <guilabel>Pokaži v &korganizer;</guilabel>, da dodate alarm v "
"aktivni koledar &korganizer;, kjer bo prikazan kot dogodek brez alarma. Ta "
"možnost omogoča sledenje alarmom v programu &korganizer; in hkrati uporabo "
"funkcij programa &kalarm;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2002
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you later modify or delete the alarm in &kalarm;, the &korganizer; event "
"will be modified or deleted correspondingly. But if you change the event in "
"&korganizer;, the alarm in &kalarm; will not be affected."
msgstr ""
"Če pozneje spremenite ali izbrišete alarm v &kalarm;, se ustrezno spremeni "
"ali izbriše tudi dogodek &korganizer;. Če pa spremenite dogodek v "
"&korganizer;, to ne bo vplivalo na alarm v &kalarm;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2007
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press the <guibutton>Load Template</guibutton> button to select a template "
"to preset the dialog with, as described in <link linkend=\"create-edit"
"\">Creating and Manipulating Alarms</link>."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite gumb <guibutton>Za nalaganje predloge</guibutton> in izberite "
"predlogo, s katero boste prednastavili pogovorno okno, kot je opisano v "
"<link linkend=\"create-edit\">Ustvarjanje in upravljanje alarmov</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2011
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press the <guibutton>Try</guibutton> button to test the alarm and check "
"whether it works correctly. The alarm is executed just as if it had been "
"scheduled in the normal way. In the case of an audio alarm, press the "
"<guibutton>Try</guibutton> button a second time to stop playing the sound "
"file."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite gumb <guibutton>Poskusi</guibutton>, da preizkusite alarm in "
"preverite, ali deluje pravilno. Alarm se izvede, kot če bi bil načrtovan na "
"običajen način. V primeru zvočnega alarma pritisnite gumb "
"<guibutton>Poskusi</guibutton> drugič, da ustavite predvajanje zvočne "
"datoteke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2017
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press the <guibutton>OK</guibutton> button when all details are correct, to "
"add the alarm to the scheduled list. Note that when editing an existing "
"alarm, the <guibutton>OK</guibutton> button is disabled while no changes "
"have been made."
msgstr ""
"Ko so vsi podatki pravilni, pritisnite gumb <guibutton>V redu</guibutton>, "
"da alarm dodate na seznam načrtovanih. Upoštevajte, da je pri urejanju "
"obstoječega alarma gumb <guibutton>V redu</guibutton> onemogočen, dokler "
"niso opravljene nobene spremembe."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2027
#, no-c-format
msgid "Alarm Message Display"
msgstr "Prikaz alarmnega sporočila"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2029
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Alarm messages may be displayed in windows or as notifications, depending on "
"the option chosen in the <link linkend=\"alarm-edit-dlg\">Alarm Edit dialog</"
"link>. These two display options are described below."
msgstr ""
"Alarmna sporočila so lahko prikazana v oknih ali kot obvestila, odvisno od "
"možnosti, izbrane v <link linkend=\"alarm-edit-dlg\">Pogovorno okno Uredi "
"alarm</link>. Ti dve možnosti prikaza sta opisani v nadaljevanju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2034
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you inhibit notifications for the desktop, the execution of display "
"alarms will be suspended until notifications are re-enabled, except for "
"alarms which you have specified in the <link linkend=\"alarm-edit-dlg-other"
"\">Alarm Edit dialog</link> should never be inhibited. Note that this "
"applies to all display alarms, regardless of whether they are displayed in "
"windows or as notifications."
msgstr ""
"Če onemogočite obvestila za namizje, bo izvajanje prikaznih alarmov začasno "
"ustavljeno, dokler obvestila niso ponovno omogočena, razen alarmov, ki ste "
"jih določili v <link linkend=\"alarm-edit-dlg-other\">pogovornem oknu za "
"urejanje alarmov</link>, ki ne smejo biti nikoli onemogočeni. Upoštevajte, "
"da to velja za vse prikazne alarme, ne glede na to, ali so prikazani v oknih "
"ali kot obvestila."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2041
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that on a single screen system, the window manager may inhibit "
"notifications while any application is running full screen, which will "
"automatically suspend the execution of display alarms."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da lahko v sistemu z enim zaslonom upravitelj oken prepreči "
"obvestila, medtem ko se katera koli aplikacija izvaja v celozaslonskem "
"načinu, kar samodejno prekine izvajanje opozoril zaslona."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2046
#, no-c-format
msgid "Alarm Message Window"
msgstr "Okno s sporočilom o alarmu"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2048
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Alarm messages which are displayed in windows provide the fullest "
"functionality."
msgstr ""
"Alarmna sporočila, ki so prikazana v oknih, zagotavljajo največjo "
"funkcionalnost."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2051
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When an alarm message is due, it is if possible displayed on each desktop "
"and cannot be covered by ordinary windows, to ensure that you see it. (Note "
"that only the X11 windowing system currently provides this facility.) The "
"message window shows the time for which the alarm was scheduled, so that you "
"can see when it popped up if you were away from the computer at the time. If "
"the alarm's scheduled time is in a different time zone from your local "
"computer's setting, its time zone will also be displayed. (For reminder "
"messages, the date/time shown is that for the main alarm or its recurrence, "
"not the reminder message time, and the window title is <quote>Reminder</"
"quote>.)"
msgstr ""
"Ko pride alarmno sporočilo, je po možnosti prikazano na vsakem namizju in ga "
"ne morejo prekriti navadna okna, da zagotovite, da ga vidite. (Upoštevajte, "
"da to možnost trenutno omogoča samo okenski sistem X11.) Okno s sporočilom "
"prikazuje čas, za katerega je bil načrtovan alarm, tako da lahko vidite, "
"kdaj se je pojavil, če niste bili takrat pri računalniku. Če je načrtovani "
"čas alarma v drugem časovnem pasu od nastavitve vašega lokalnega "
"računalnika, bo prikazan tudi njegov časovni pas. (Pri sporočilih z opomniki "
"je prikazan datum/čas glavnega alarma ali njegove ponovitve, ne čas "
"sporočila z opomniki, naslov okna pa je <quote>Opomnik</quote>.)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2062
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Alarm message windows remain visible until you acknowledge them, unless "
"<guilabel>Auto-close window after late-cancelation time</guilabel> was "
"checked in the <link linkend=\"alarm-edit-dlg-cancel\">Alarm Edit dialog</"
"link>. In the case of a recurring alarm, if an unacknowledged message window "
"remains from a previous occurrence of the alarm, the existing window is "
"simply popped up when the alarm recurs. This avoids having to acknowledge "
"multiple copies of the same message should you not wish, or be unable, to "
"acknowledge a message at the time it appears."
msgstr ""
"Okna z alarmnimi sporočili ostanejo vidna, dokler jih ne potrdite, razen če "
"je bila v <link linkend=\"alarm-edit-dlg-cancel\">pogovornem oknu za "
"urejanje alarmov</link> označena možnost <guilabel>Samodejno zapri okno po "
"času poznega preklica</guilabel>. V primeru ponavljajočega se alarma, če od "
"prejšnjega pojava alarma ostane nepotrjeno okno s sporočilom, se obstoječe "
"okno preprosto prikaže, ko se alarm ponovi. S tem se izognete potrditvi več "
"kopij istega sporočila, če sporočila ne želite ali ne morete potrditi v "
"trenutku, ko se pojavi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2072
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The alarm message window provides whichever of the following options are "
"applicable to the displayed alarm:"
msgstr ""
"V oknu s sporočilom alarma je na voljo katera koli od naslednjih možnosti, "
"ki veljajo za prikazani alarm:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2077
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Acknowledge the alarm by clicking the <guibutton>Close</guibutton> button. "
"This closes the window (after a prompt for confirmation, if you selected "
"<guilabel>Confirm acknowledgment</guilabel>)."
msgstr ""
"Alarm potrdite s klikom na gumb <guibutton>Zapri</guibutton>. S tem se okno "
"zapre (po pozivu za potrditev, če ste izbrali možnost <guilabel>Potrdi "
"seznanjenost</guilabel>)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2084
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Edit the alarm by clicking the <guibutton>Edit...</guibutton> button. This "
"displays the <link linkend=\"alarm-edit-dlg\">Alarm Edit dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"Alarm uredite s klikom na gumb <guibutton>Uredi...</guibutton>. Prikaže se "
"<link linkend=\"alarm-edit-dlg\">Pogovorno okno za urejanje alarmov</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2090
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Display options to defer the alarm until later by clicking the "
"<guibutton>Defer...</guibutton> button. Then select <guilabel>Defer for</"
"guilabel> to enter how long after now the message should be redisplayed (the "
"<guilabel>Preset</guilabel> button lets you select from a list of common "
"time intervals), or select <guilabel>Defer until</guilabel> to enter the "
"date and time when the message is to be redisplayed. Then click "
"<guibutton>OK</guibutton> to defer the alarm message and close its window."
msgstr ""
"S klikom na gumb <guibutton>Odloži...</guibutton> prikažite možnosti za "
"odložitev alarma na pozneje. Nato izberite <guilabel>Odloži za</guilabel>, "
"da vnesete, čez koliko časa naj se sporočilo ponovno prikaže (gumb "
"<guilabel>Prednastavitev</guilabel> omogoča izbiro s seznama običajnih "
"časovnih intervalov), ali izberite <guilabel>Odloži do</guilabel>, da "
"vnesete datum in čas, ko naj se sporočilo ponovno prikaže. Nato kliknite "
"<guibutton>V redu</guibutton>, da odložite alarmno sporočilo in zaprete "
"njegovo okno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2100
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The time the alarm is deferred to must be earlier than its next scheduled "
"occurrence or next advance reminder. For this reason, the <guibutton>Defer..."
"</guibutton> button in the alarm message window and the <guibutton>OK</"
"guibutton> button in the Deferral dialog are disabled one minute before the "
"next occurrence or advance reminder."
msgstr ""
"Čas, na katerega je alarm odložen, mora biti zgodnejši od naslednjega "
"načrtovanega dogodka ali naslednjega vnaprejšnjega opomnika. Zato sta gumb "
"<guibutton>Odloži...</guibutton> v oknu z alarmnim sporočilom in gumb "
"<guibutton>V redu</guibutton> v pogovornem oknu Odložitev onemogočena eno "
"minuto pred naslednjim dogodkom ali predhodnim opomnikom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that if a reminder is configured <emphasis>after</emphasis> the alarm, "
"you <emphasis>can</emphasis> defer the alarm past its reminder time. In this "
"case, the reminder will be suppressed."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da če je opomnik konfiguriran <emphasis>za</emphasis> alarmom, "
"lahko <emphasis>odložite</emphasis> alarm po času opomnika. V tem primeru se "
"opomnik izklopi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2111
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guibutton>Defer...</guibutton> button is not available for alarms which "
"are displayed at login due to the <guilabel>Repeat at login</guilabel> "
"option having been selected."
msgstr ""
"Gumb <guibutton>Odloži...</guibutton> ni na voljo za alarme, ki se prikažejo "
"ob prijavi, ker je bila izbrana možnost <guilabel>Ponovi ob prijavi</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2118
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Stop playing the alarm's sound file by clicking the button showing the "
"<quote>stop playing</quote> symbol."
msgstr ""
"Prekinite predvajanje zvočne datoteke alarma s klikom na gumb s simbolom "
"<quote>prenehaj predvajati</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the alarm message was created by dragging an email from &kmail;, you can "
"directly access the email in &kmail; by clicking the button showing the "
"&kmail; icon. This will display the email and select the folder containing "
"the email in &kmail;'s folder list."
msgstr ""
"Če je bilo alarmno sporočilo ustvarjeno z vlečenjem e-poštnega sporočila iz "
"storitve &kmail;, lahko neposredno dostopate do e-poštnega sporočila v "
"storitvi &kmail; s klikom na gumb z ikono &kmail;. Tako se prikaže e-poštno "
"sporočilo in na seznamu map &kmail; se izbere mapa, ki vsebuje e-poštno "
"sporočilo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2128
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If &kmail;'s indexes are regenerated, the link to the email in &kmail; will "
"be lost."
msgstr ""
"Če se indeksi &kmail; obnovijo, se povezava do e-pošte v &kmail; izgubi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2133
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The button showing the <guiicon>&kalarm;</guiicon> icon provides a "
"convenient way to activate &kalarm;'s main window, with that alarm "
"highlighted."
msgstr ""
"Gumb z ikono <guiicon>&kalarm;</guiicon> omogoča priročen način za "
"aktiviranje glavnega okna &kalarm; s poudarjenim alarmom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2139
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The way that alarm message windows are displayed depends on the windowing "
"system in use."
msgstr ""
"Način prikaza oken z alarmnimi sporočili je odvisen od uporabljenega "
"okenskega sistema."

#. Tag: application
#: index.docbook:2144 index.docbook:3188
#, no-c-format
msgid "X11 Windowing System"
msgstr "X11 okenski sistem"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2146
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can choose in the <link linkend=\"preferences-view\">Configuration "
"dialog</link> which of two different modes should be used to display alarm "
"message windows:"
msgstr ""
"V <link linkend=\"preferences-view\">Pogovornem oknu za konfiguracijo</link> "
"lahko izberete, kateri od dveh različnih načinov se bo uporabil za prikaz "
"oken z alarmnimi sporočili:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2153
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As a normal window. In this mode, the keyboard focus is taken by the alarm "
"message window when it appears, so if you are typing at the time your "
"keystrokes will be diverted to it rather than your original application."
msgstr ""
"Kot običajno okno. V tem načinu fokus tipkovnice prevzame okno z alarmnim "
"sporočilom, ko se prikaže, zato bodo vaši pritiski na tipke preusmerjeni "
"nanj in ne na prvotno aplikacijo, če v tem času tipkate."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2160
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As a non-modal window. In this mode, the keyboard focus is unaffected when "
"the alarm message window appears, so it will not interfere with your typing. "
"However in this mode the window has no titlebar or frame, so you cannot move "
"it or resize it."
msgstr ""
"Kot nemodalno okno. V tem načinu fokus tipkovnice ne vpliva na prikaz okna z "
"alarmnim sporočilom, zato ne ovira vašega tipkanja. Vendar v tem načinu okno "
"nima naslovne vrstice ali okvirja, zato ga ne morete premikati ali "
"spreminjati njegove velikosti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2167
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can choose in the <link linkend=\"preferences-view\">Configuration "
"dialog</link> which of two schemes should be used to position alarm message "
"windows:"
msgstr ""
"V <link linkend=\"preferences-view\">Pogovornem oknu za konfiguracijo</link> "
"lahko izberete, katera od dveh shem naj se uporabi za postavitev oken "
"alarmnih sporočil:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2173
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The windows are displayed as far away from the current mouse cursor as "
"possible. This minimizes disruption to your work flow and minimizes the "
"possibility of accidentally acknowledging the alarm."
msgstr ""
"Okna se prikažejo čim dlje od trenutnega kazalca miške. S tem čim manj "
"motite svoj delovni proces in zmanjšate možnost, da bi pomotoma potrdili "
"alarm."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2180
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The windows are displayed in the center of the screen. To reduce the chance "
"of accidentally acknowledging the alarm, the buttons on the window are "
"initially disabled, becoming active only after a configurable delay."
msgstr ""
"Okna so prikazana na sredini zaslona. Da bi zmanjšali možnost nenamerne "
"potrditve alarma, so gumbi na oknu sprva onemogočeni in postanejo aktivni "
"šele po nastavljivem zakasnitvi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2187
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have several alarm message windows, or error messages, displayed, you "
"can spread the windows out across the screen to make them all visible, or "
"group them all together again in the top left corner of the screen, by means "
"of the <menuchoice> <guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem>Spread Windows</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice> menu option. If you wish, you can set up a global "
"shortcut key for this action."
msgstr ""
"Če imate prikazanih več oken z alarmnimi sporočili ali sporočili o napakah, "
"lahko okna razporedite po zaslonu, da so vidna vsa, ali pa jih ponovno "
"združite v zgornjem levem kotu zaslona s pomočjo menijske možnosti "
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guimenuitem>Razširi okna</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. Če želite, lahko za to dejanje nastavite "
"globalno bližnjico."

#. Tag: application
#: index.docbook:2198 index.docbook:3219
#, no-c-format
msgid "Wayland Windowing System"
msgstr "Wayland okenski sistem"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2200
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Wayland windowing system does not allow applications to control the "
"position or decoration of their windows, so the display options are much "
"more limited."
msgstr ""
"Okenski sistem Wayland aplikacijam ne dovoljuje nadzora položaja ali "
"dekoracije svojih oken, zato so možnosti prikaza veliko bolj omejene."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2204
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To reduce the chance of accidentally acknowledging the alarm, the buttons on "
"the window are initially disabled, becoming active only after a configurable "
"delay."
msgstr ""
"Da bi zmanjšali možnost nenamerne potrditve alarma, so gumbi na oknu sprva "
"onemogočeni in postanejo aktivni šele po nastavljivi zakasnitvi."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2215
#, no-c-format
msgid "Alarm Message Notifications"
msgstr "Obvestila o alarmnih sporočilih"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2217
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Alarm messages which are displayed as notifications provide less "
"functionality than those displayed in windows."
msgstr ""
"Alarmna sporočila, ki so prikazana kot obvestila, imajo manj funkcij kot "
"tista, ki so prikazana v oknih."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2220
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When an alarm message is due, it is displayed as a notification. The "
"notification shows the time for which the alarm was scheduled. If the "
"alarm's scheduled time is in a different time zone from your local "
"computer's setting, its time zone will also be displayed. (For reminder "
"messages, the date/time shown is that for the main alarm or its recurrence, "
"not the reminder message time, and a “Reminder” heading is shown.)"
msgstr ""
"Ko zapade alarmno sporočilo, se prikaže kot obvestilo. Obvestilo prikazuje "
"čas, za katerega je bil načrtovan alarm. Če je načrtovani čas alarma v "
"drugem časovnem pasu, kot je nastavljen v lokalnem računalniku, bo prikazan "
"tudi njegov časovni pas. (Pri opomnikih je prikazan datum/čas glavnega "
"alarma ali njegove ponovitve in ne čas opomnika, poleg tega je prikazan "
"naslov \"Opomnik\".)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2228
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The notification automatically closes after a short time-out. (Note that the "
"time-out is common to all applications; it can be changed in "
"&systemsettings;.) After a notification times out, it can still be seen in "
"the notification history until you remove it or until you log out. Because "
"applications have no way to access the notification history, &kalarm; cannot "
"remove or replace notifications in the history as it would for alarm "
"windows. So the history may contain multiple notifications for the same "
"alarm, including reminders and recurrences."
msgstr ""
"Obvestilo se po kratkem času samodejno zapre. (Upoštevajte, da je časovna "
"omejitev skupna vsem aplikacijam; spremenite jo lahko v nastavitvah "
"&systemsettings;.) Ko se obvestilo izteče, je še vedno vidno v zgodovini "
"obvestil, dokler ga ne odstranite ali dokler se ne odjavite. Ker aplikacije "
"nimajo dostopa do zgodovine obvestil, &kalarm; ne more odstraniti ali "
"zamenjati obvestil v zgodovini, kot bi to storil za alarmna okna. Tako lahko "
"zgodovina vsebuje več obvestil za isti alarm, vključno z opomniki in "
"ponovitvami."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2238
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The alarm message notification provides the following options. Note that "
"selecting any option will immediately close the notification, and prevent it "
"being shown in the notification history. Note also that these options are "
"only available while the notification is active, before it times out. If you "
"subsequently access the notification in the notification history, then due "
"to the limitations of the notification system, the only interaction "
"available is to remove it from the history."
msgstr ""
"Obvestilo o alarmnem sporočilu omogoča naslednje možnosti. Upoštevajte, da "
"se z izbiro katere koli možnosti obvestilo takoj zapre in se ne prikaže v "
"zgodovini obvestil. Upoštevajte tudi, da so te možnosti na voljo le, dokler "
"je obvestilo aktivno, preden se prekine. Če do obvestila pozneje dostopate v "
"zgodovini obvestil, je zaradi omejitev sistema obvestil edina razpoložljiva "
"interakcija odstranitev obvestila iz zgodovine."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2249
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Acknowledge the alarm by clicking the <guibutton>Close</guibutton> button. "
"This closes the notification."
msgstr ""
"Alarm potrdite s klikom na gumb <guibutton>Zapri</guibutton>. S tem zaprete "
"obvestilo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2254
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Edit the alarm by clicking the <guibutton>Edit</guibutton> button. This "
"displays the <link linkend=\"alarm-edit-dlg\">Alarm Edit dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"Alarm uredite s klikom na gumb <guibutton>Uredi</guibutton>. Prikaže se "
"<link linkend=\"alarm-edit-dlg\">Pogovorno okno za urejanje alarmov</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2260
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Display options to defer the alarm until later by clicking the "
"<guibutton>Defer</guibutton> button. This button is only shown if it is "
"possible to defer the alarm. See the description of the defer option in the "
"<link linkend=\"message-window\">Alarm Message Window</link> section for "
"details."
msgstr ""
"S klikom na gumb <guibutton>Odloži</guibutton> prikažite možnosti za "
"odložitev alarma na pozneje. Ta gumb se prikaže le, če je mogoče alarm "
"odložiti. Za podrobnosti glejte opis možnosti odlog v razdelku <link linkend="
"\"message-window\">Okno alarmnega sporočila</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2269
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking the notification anywhere other than a button will activate "
"&kalarm;'s main window, with that alarm highlighted."
msgstr ""
"Če kliknete obvestilo kjer koli drugje kot na gumb, se aktivira glavno okno "
"programa &kalarm; z označenim alarmom."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2279
#, no-c-format
msgid "System Tray Operation"
msgstr "Delovanje v sistemskem predalu"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2281
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kalarm; by default displays an icon in the system tray. The icon provides "
"both control and an alarm monitoring status indication. A normal &kalarm; "
"icon indicates that all alarms are being monitored, while two different "
"modified icons indicate either that some alarms, or that all alarms, are not "
"being monitored. The icon modifications depend on the icon theme being used."
msgstr ""
"&kalarm; privzeto prikaže ikono v sistemski vrstici. Ikona omogoča nadzor in "
"spremljanje stanja alarma. Običajna ikona &kalarm; pomeni, da se spremljajo "
"vsi alarmi, medtem ko dve različni spremenjeni ikoni pomenita, da se "
"nekateri alarmi ali vsi alarmi ne spremljajo. Spremembe ikon so odvisne od "
"uporabljene teme ikon."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2288
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kalarm;'s system tray icon is by default automatically hidden whenever "
"there are no alarms due in the next 24 hours. You can change the auto-hide "
"time limit, or always show the system tray icon, using the <link linkend="
"\"preferences-view\">Configuration dialog</link>. To show the icon when it "
"has been automatically hidden, click the arrow in the system tray to reveal "
"hidden icons."
msgstr ""
"Ikona v sistemski vrstici programa &kalarm; se privzeto samodejno skrije, "
"kadar v naslednjih 24 urah ni predvidenih alarmov. Časovno omejitev "
"samodejnega skrivanja lahko spremenite ali vedno prikažete ikono v sistemski "
"vrstici z uporabo <link linkend=\"preferences-view\">Pogovorno okno za "
"konfiguracijo</link>. Če želite prikazati ikono, ki je bila samodejno "
"skrita, kliknite puščico v sistemski vrstici za prikaz skritih ikon."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2295
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you hover the mouse cursor over the system tray icon, a summary of the "
"first few message alarms due in the next 24 hours are displayed as a "
"tooltip. You can switch this feature off, or configure the number of alarms "
"to display and their format, in the <link linkend=\"preferences-view"
"\">Configuration dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"Če se z miškinim kazalcem pomaknete nad ikono v sistemski vrstici, se kot "
"namig prikaže povzetek prvih nekaj alarmov s sporočili, ki jih je treba "
"poslati v naslednjih 24 urah. To funkcijo lahko izklopite ali konfigurirate "
"število prikazanih alarmov in njihovo obliko v <link linkend=\"preferences-"
"view\">Pogovorno okno Konfiguracija</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2301
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<mousebutton>Left</mousebutton> click on the system tray icon to toggle "
"between displaying and hiding the &kalarm; main window."
msgstr ""
"<mousebutton>Levi</mousebutton> klik na ikono v sistemski vrstici za "
"preklapljanje med prikazom in skrivanjem glavnega okna &kalarm;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2304
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<mousebutton>Right</mousebutton> click on the system tray icon to display "
"its context menu:"
msgstr ""
"<mousebutton>Desno</mousebutton> kliknite ikono v sistemski vrstici, da "
"prikažete njen kontekstni meni:"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:2309
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable Alarms"
msgstr "Omogoči alarme"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:2310
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enables or disables monitoring of alarms."
msgstr "Omogoči ali onemogoči spremljanje alarmov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2311
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"See <link linkend=\"enable-disable\">Enabling and Disabling Alarms</link> "
"for details."
msgstr ""
"Za podrobnosti glejte <link linkend=\"enable-disable\">Omogočanje in izklop "
"alarmov</link>."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:2318
#, no-c-format
msgid "New Alarm"
msgstr "Nov alarm"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:2319
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After you select the alarm type from the list which appears, opens the Alarm "
"Edit dialog to create a new alarm."
msgstr ""
"Ko izberete vrsto alarma s seznama, ki se prikaže, se odpre pogovorno okno "
"Urejanje alarma za ustvarjanje novega alarma."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:2326
#, no-c-format
msgid "Stop Play"
msgstr "Ustavi predvajanje"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:2327
#, no-c-format
msgid "Halts playback of the audio file currently playing."
msgstr "Ustavi predvajanje zvočne datoteke, ki se trenutno predvaja."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:2333
#, no-c-format
msgid "Spread Windows"
msgstr "Razprši okna"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:2334
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Spreads alarm and error message windows across the screen, or groups them "
"together again."
msgstr ""
"Okna z alarmnimi sporočili in sporočili o napakah razporedi po zaslonu ali "
"jih ponovno združi."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:2340
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configure &kalarm;..."
msgstr "Konfiguriranje &kalarm;..."

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:2341
#, no-c-format
msgid "Displays the &kalarm; Configuration dialog."
msgstr "Prikaže pogovorno okno &kalarm; Konfiguracija."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2342
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Configuration dialog is described in <link linkend=\"preferences"
"\">Configuring &kalarm;</link>. It includes options relating to the &kalarm; "
"system tray icon."
msgstr ""
"Pogovorno okno za konfiguracijo je opisano v <link linkend=\"preferences"
"\">Konfiguriranje alarmov;</link>. Vključuje možnosti, povezane z ikono "
"&kalarm; sistemskega pladnja."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:2349
#, no-c-format
msgid "Restore / Minimize"
msgstr "Obnovi / zmanjšaj"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:2350
#, no-c-format
msgid "Restores or minimizes the main &kalarm; window."
msgstr "Obnovi ali zmanjša glavno okno &kalarm;."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:2355
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quit"
msgstr "Izhod"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:2356
#, no-c-format
msgid "Closes the &kalarm; system tray icon and main windows."
msgstr "Zapre ikono &kalarm; v sistemski vrstici in glavna okna."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2358
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quits &kalarm; if no alarm message windows are displayed."
msgstr ""
"Zaključi program &kalarm;, če ni prikazano nobeno okno z alarmnim sporočilom."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2364
#, no-c-format
msgid "Displaying &kalarm; in the System Tray"
msgstr "Prikaz &kalarm; v sistemskem pladnju"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2366
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You must be running the &plasma; desktop or another suitable window manager "
"in order to display &kalarm; in the system tray."
msgstr ""
"Za prikaz &kalarm; v sistemskem pladnju mora biti nameščeno namizje &plasma; "
"ali drug ustrezen upravljalnik oken."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2369
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select <menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show in System Tray</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> to display &kalarm; in the system tray according "
"to the preferences set in the <link linkend=\"preferences-view\">View</link> "
"tab of the Configuration dialog."
msgstr ""
"Izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pokaži v "
"sistemski vrstici</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, če želite prikazati &kalarm; v "
"sistemski vrstici v skladu z nastavitvami, določenimi v <link linkend="
"\"preferences-view\">Pogled</link> zavihku Configuration dialog dialogue."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2375
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To remove &kalarm; from the system tray, deselect <menuchoice><guimenu>View</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show in System Tray</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite &kalarm; odstraniti iz sistemske vrstice, odstranite izbiro "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pokaži v sistemski "
"vrstici</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2379
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To choose whether or not &kalarm; will be shown at startup in the system "
"tray, use the <link linkend=\"preferences-view\">View</link> tab of the "
"Configuration dialog."
msgstr ""
"Če želite izbrati, ali bo &kalarm; ob zagonu prikazan v sistemski vrstici, "
"uporabite zavihek <link linkend=\"preferences-view\">Pogled</link> v "
"pogovornem oknu Konfiguracija."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2386
#, no-c-format
msgid "Refreshing Alarms"
msgstr "Osveževanje alarmov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2388
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If in the unlikely event that any alarm was not triggered when it should "
"have been, you can refresh the alarm list and trigger any missed alarms by "
"selecting <menuchoice> <guimenu>Actions</guimenu><guimenuitem>Refresh "
"Alarms</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. This causes &kalarm; to reload all alarm "
"calendars."
msgstr ""
"Če se v malo verjetnem primeru kakšen alarm ni sprožil, ko bi se moral, "
"lahko osvežite seznam alarmov in sprožite vse zamujene alarme z izbiro "
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Dejanja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Osveži alarme</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. To povzroči, da &kalarm; ponovno naloži vse "
"koledarje alarmov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2396
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can reload an individual calendar and refresh its alarms in the alarm "
"list by <mousebutton>Right</mousebutton> clicking the calendar in the "
"calendars list and selecting the <menuchoice><guimenuitem>Reload</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu option. See <link linkend=\"calendars\">Alarm "
"Calendars</link> for details."
msgstr ""
"Posamezen koledar lahko ponovno naložite in osvežite njegove alarme na "
"seznamu alarmov tako, da <mousebutton>Desno</mousebutton> kliknete koledar "
"na seznamu koledarjev in izberete možnost menija "
"<menuchoice><guimenuitem>Ponovno naloži</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Za "
"podrobnosti glejte <link linkend=\"calendars\">Koledarji alarmov</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2407
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enabling and Disabling Alarms"
msgstr "Omogočanje in onemogočanje alarmov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2409
#, no-c-format
msgid "Alarms may be enabled and disabled either as a whole or individually:"
msgstr "Alarme je mogoče omogočiti in onemogočiti v celoti ali posamezno:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2414
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<quote>Alarm monitoring</quote> applies to alarms as a whole. While alarm "
"monitoring is disabled, no alarms are triggered at all. While alarm "
"monitoring is enabled (the normal situation), all alarms which are not "
"individually disabled will trigger at the appropriate times."
msgstr ""
"<quote>Nadzor alarmov</quote> velja za alarme kot celoto. Če je spremljanje "
"alarmov onemogočeno, se alarmi sploh ne sprožijo. Ko je omogočeno "
"spremljanje alarmov (običajna situacija), se vsi alarmi, ki niso posamično "
"onemogočeni, sprožijo ob ustreznem času."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2420
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When alarm monitoring is re-enabled, alarms which would have triggered while "
"it was disabled are now triggered (unless any late-cancel option prevents "
"this). In other words, disabling alarm monitoring has the same effect as "
"stopping &kalarm; &ndash; alarms are postponed until it is re-enabled."
msgstr ""
"Ko je spremljanje alarmov ponovno omogočeno, se sprožijo alarmi, ki bi se "
"sprožili, ko je bilo spremljanje onemogočeno (razen če to preprečuje možnost "
"pozne preklica). Z drugimi besedami, onemogočanje spremljanja alarmov ima "
"enak učinek kot ustavitev funkcije &kalarm; &ndash; alarmi so odloženi, "
"dokler ni ponovno omogočena."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2428
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Alarms may be individually enabled and disabled, independently of the alarm "
"monitoring status. So the enabled/disabled status of individual alarms will "
"be unchanged by disabling and then re-enabling alarm monitoring. Unlike "
"alarm monitoring which could potentially be disabled due to &kalarm; not "
"running, individual alarms can only be disabled if you use menu commands to "
"do so."
msgstr ""
"Alarme je mogoče posamično omogočiti in onemogočiti, neodvisno od stanja "
"spremljanja alarma. Tako se stanje vključenosti/izključenosti posameznih "
"alarmov ne bo spremenilo, če onemogočite in nato ponovno omogočite "
"spremljanje alarmov. V nasprotju s spremljanjem alarmov, ki ga je mogoče "
"onemogočiti, če se program &kalarm; ne izvaja, je mogoče posamezne alarme "
"onemogočiti le, če to storite z menijskimi ukazi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2435
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When an alarm is individually re-enabled, it is not now triggered if it "
"became due while disabled. In other words, disabling an individual alarm "
"cancels all its occurrences until it is re-enabled."
msgstr ""
"Ko je alarm ponovno posamično omogočen, se zdaj ne sproži, če se je sprožil, "
"ko je bil onemogočen. Z drugimi besedami, onemogočanje posameznega alarma "
"prekliče vse njegove dogodke, dokler ga ponovno ne omogočite."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2440
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An alarm's individual enabled/disabled status is indicated by its color in "
"the alarm list (the color being configurable in the <link linkend="
"\"preferences-view\">View</link> tab of the Configuration dialog)."
msgstr ""
"Status posameznega alarma, ki je omogočen/izključen, je označen z barvo na "
"seznamu alarmov (barvo je mogoče konfigurirati v zavihku <link linkend="
"\"preferences-view\">Pogled</link> pogovornega okna Configuration)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2447
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For an alarm to trigger, it must be individually enabled as well as alarm "
"monitoring being enabled."
msgstr ""
"Da se alarm sproži, mora biti omogočen individualno in omogočeno mora biti "
"nad alarma."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2451
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enabling Alarm Monitoring"
msgstr "Omogočanje nadzora alarma"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2453
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For alarm monitoring to occur, &kalarm; must be running. Once you run "
"&kalarm;, it will from then on start automatically whenever you log in "
"unless you later disable it in the <link linkend=\"preferences-general"
"\">General</link> tab of the Configuration dialog."
msgstr ""
"Za spremljanje alarma mora delovati program &kalarm;. Ko zaženete program "
"&kalarm;, se bo od takrat naprej samodejno zagnal ob vsaki prijavi, razen če "
"ga pozneje onemogočite v zavihku <link linkend=\"preferences-general"
"\">Splošno</link> pogovornega okna Configuration."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2459
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If alarm monitoring is currently disabled, do one of the following to enable "
"alarms:"
msgstr ""
"Če je spremljanje alarmov trenutno onemogočeno, naredite eno od naslednjih "
"dejanj, da omogočite alarme:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2464
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select <menuchoice><guimenu>Actions</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Enable Alarms</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Dejanja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Omogoči Alarme</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2469
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<mousebutton>Right</mousebutton> click on the system tray icon and choose "
"<menuchoice><guimenuitem>Enable Alarms</guimenuitem></menuchoice> from the "
"context menu."
msgstr ""
"<mousebutton>Desno</mousebutton> kliknite ikono v sistemski vrstici in v "
"kontekstnem meniju izberite <menuchoice><guimenuitem>Omogoči alarme</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2479
#, no-c-format
msgid "Disabling Alarm Monitoring"
msgstr "Onemogočanje nadzora alarma"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2481
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can temporarily disable alarm monitoring, which prevents &kalarm; from "
"checking any alarms either until you re-enable alarms, or &ndash; assuming "
"that &kalarm; is configured to start at login &ndash; until the next time "
"you log in."
msgstr ""
"Začasno lahko onemogočite spremljanje alarmov, kar prepreči, da bi program "
"&kalarm; preverjal vse alarme, dokler jih ponovno ne omogočite, ali &ndash; "
"če je program &kalarm; konfiguriran tako, da se začne ob prijavi &ndash; do "
"naslednje prijave."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2488
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Unselect <menuchoice><guimenu>Actions</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Enable Alarms</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Dejanja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Omogoči Alarme</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2493
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<mousebutton>Right</mousebutton> click on the system tray icon and uncheck "
"<menuchoice><guimenuitem>Enable Alarms</guimenuitem></menuchoice> from the "
"context menu."
msgstr ""
"<mousebutton>Desno</mousebutton> kliknite ikono v sistemski vrstici in v "
"kontekstnem meniju odstranite kljukico <menuchoice><guimenuitem>Omogoči "
"alarme</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2500
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Run &kalarm; with the command line option <option>--disable-all</option>."
msgstr ""
"Zaženite &kalarm; z možnostjo ukazne vrstice <option>--disable-all</option>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2505
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Stop &kalarm; as described in <link linkend=\"quitting\">Quitting &kalarm;</"
"link>."
msgstr ""
"Ustavite &kalarm;, kot je opisano v <link linkend=\"quitting\">Ustavitev "
"&kalarm;</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2510
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Alarms may be permanently disabled by preventing &kalarm; from being started "
"at login using the <link linkend=\"preferences-general\">General</link> tab "
"of the Configuration dialog."
msgstr ""
"Alarme lahko trajno onemogočite tako, da preprečite, da bi se ob prijavi "
"sprožila funkcija &kalarm; z uporabo zavihka <link linkend=\"preferences-"
"general\">Splošno</link> v pogovornem oknu Konfiguracija."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2518
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enabling and Disabling Individual Alarms"
msgstr "Omogočanje in onemogočanje posameznih alarmov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2520
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To enable individual alarms which are currently disabled, do one of the "
"following:"
msgstr ""
"Če želite omogočiti posamezne alarme, ki so trenutno onemogočeni, naredite "
"eno od naslednjih dejanj:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2525
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select one or more alarms by clicking on their entries in the alarm list. "
"Then choose <menuchoice> <guimenu>Actions</guimenu><guimenuitem>Enable</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Izberite enega ali več alarmov s klikom na njihove vnose na seznamu alarmov. "
"Nato izberite <menuchoice> <guimenu>Dejanja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Omogoči</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2532
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<mousebutton>Right</mousebutton> click on the desired entries in the alarm "
"list and choose <menuchoice><guimenuitem>Enable</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"from the context menu."
msgstr ""
"<mousebutton>Desno</mousebutton> kliknite želene vnose na seznamu alarmov in "
"v kontekstnem meniju izberite <menuchoice><guimenuitem>Omogoči</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2539
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To disable individual alarms which are currently enabled, do one of the "
"following:"
msgstr ""
"Če želite onemogočiti posamezne alarme, ki so trenutno omogočeni, naredite "
"eno od naslednjih dejanj:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2544
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select one or more alarms by clicking on their entries in the alarm list. "
"Then choose <menuchoice> <guimenu>Actions</guimenu><guimenuitem>Disable</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Izberite enega ali več alarmov s klikom na njihove vnose na seznamu alarmov. "
"Nato izberite <menuchoice> <guimenu>Dejanja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Onemogoči</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2551
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<mousebutton>Right</mousebutton> click on the desired entries in the alarm "
"list and choose <menuchoice><guimenuitem>Disable</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"from the context menu."
msgstr ""
"<mousebutton>Desno</mousebutton> kliknite želene vnose na seznamu alarmov in "
"v kontekstnem meniju izberite <menuchoice><guimenuitem>Onemogoči</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2561
#, no-c-format
msgid "Skipping Individual Alarms"
msgstr "Preskakovanje posamičnih alarmov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2563
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can choose to skip the next few (1 - 10) activations of an alarm. This "
"temporarily disables the alarm until that number of recurrences or sub-"
"repetitions have passed without activation. The alarm will resume triggering "
"as normal after that."
msgstr ""
"Lahko izberete preskok naslednjih nekaj (1–10) aktivacij alarma. S tem "
"začasno onemogočite alarme, dokler ne mine določeno število ponovitev ali "
"podponovitev brez aktivacije. Po tem se bo alarm znova sprožal kot običajno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2568
#, no-c-format
msgid "No reminders will be displayed for skipped activations."
msgstr "Za preskočene aktivacije ne bodo prikazani opomniki."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2569
#, no-c-format
msgid "Skipping does not affect any outstanding deferral of the alarm."
msgstr "Preskakovanje ne vpliva na morebitno preostalo odložitev alarma."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2572
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To skip the next activation(s) of individual alarms, do one of the "
"following, and then enter the number of activations to skip:"
msgstr ""
"Če želite preskočiti naslednje aktivacije posameznih alarmov, naredite nekaj "
"od naslednjega in nato vnesite število aktivacij, ki jih želite preskočiti:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2577
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select one or more alarms by clicking on their entries in the alarm list. "
"Then choose <menuchoice> <guimenu>Actions</guimenu><guimenuitem>Skip</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Izberite enega ali več alarmov s klikom na njihove vnose na seznamu alarmov. "
"Nato izberite <menuchoice> <guimenu>Dejanja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Preskoči</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2584
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<mousebutton>Right</mousebutton> click on the desired entries in the alarm "
"list and choose <menuchoice><guimenuitem>Skip</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"from the context menu."
msgstr ""
"<mousebutton>Z desno miškino tipko</mousebutton> kliknite želene vnose na "
"seznamu alarmov in v kontekstnem meniju izberite "
"<menuchoice><guimenuitem>Preskoči</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2591
#, no-c-format
msgid "To cancel skipping individual alarms, do one of the following:"
msgstr ""
"Če želite preklicati preskakovanje posameznih alarmov, naredite nekaj od "
"naslednjega:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2595
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select one or more alarms by clicking on their entries in the alarm list. "
"Then choose <menuchoice> <guimenu>Actions</guimenu><guimenuitem>Cancel skip</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Izberite enega ali več alarmov s klikom na njihove vnose na seznamu alarmov. "
"Nato izberite <menuchoice> <guimenu>Dejanja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Prekliči "
"preskok</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2602
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<mousebutton>Right</mousebutton> click on the desired entries in the alarm "
"list and choose <menuchoice><guimenuitem>Cancel skip</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> from the context menu."
msgstr ""
"<mousebutton>Z desno miškino tipko</mousebutton> kliknite na želene vnose na "
"seznamu alarmov in v kontekstnem meniju izberite "
"<menuchoice><guimenuitem>Prekliči preskok</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2613
#, no-c-format
msgid "Wake From Suspend"
msgstr "Prebudi se iz mirovanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2615
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Alarms can be configured to wake your computer from hibernation or "
"suspension when the alarm triggers, so that the alarm action can occur even "
"when the system is shut down. The mechanism used by &kalarm; to wake the "
"system, and the user interface to control it, depend on the type of system "
"and user permissions. There are two possibilities:"
msgstr ""
"Alarme je mogoče konfigurirati tako, da ob sprožitvi alarma prebudijo "
"računalnik iz mirovanja ali mirovanja, tako da se lahko alarmno dejanje "
"izvede tudi, ko je sistem izklopljen. Mehanizem, ki ga &kalarm; uporablja za "
"prebujanje sistema, in uporabniški vmesnik za nadzor sistema sta odvisna od "
"vrste sistema in uporabniških pooblastil. Obstajata dve možnosti:"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2623
#, no-c-format
msgid "Linux Kernel Timer Wake From Suspend"
msgstr "Časovnik Linuxovega jedra Prebudi se iz mirovanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2625
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On Linux systems, if the user has kernel alarm timer "
"(<literal>cap_wake_alarm</literal>) capability, any number of alarms can be "
"set to wake from suspend. In this case, wake from suspend is configured for "
"each individual alarm in the <link linkend=\"alarm-edit-dlg-other\">Alarm "
"Edit dialog</link> using its <guilabel>Wake from suspend</guilabel> option."
msgstr ""
"V sistemih Linux lahko uporabnik, če ima zmožnost jedrnega časovnika alarma "
"(<literal>cap_wake_alarm</literal>), nastavi poljubno število alarmov za "
"prebujanje iz stanja mirovanja. V tem primeru je prebujanje iz stanja "
"mirovanja konfigurirano za vsak posamezen alarm v <link linkend=\"alarm-edit-"
"dlg-other\">pogovornem oknu za urejanje alarmov</link> z uporabo možnosti "
"<guilabel>Prebujanje iz stanja mirovanja</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2632
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can configure how long before the alarm to wake from suspend, to ensure "
"that the system has time to fully restore itself before the alarm triggers, "
"in the <link linkend=\"preferences-time\">Configuration dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"V pogovornem oknu <link linkend=\"preferences-time\">Configuration dialog</"
"link> lahko nastavite, koliko časa pred alarmom naj se sistem zbudi iz "
"stanja mirovanja, da se zagotovi čas za popolno obnovitev pred sprožitvijo "
"alarma."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2640
#, no-c-format
msgid "RTC Wake From Suspend"
msgstr "RTC Prebudi se iz mirovanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2642
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On non-Linux systems, or on Linux systems where the user does not have "
"<literal>cap_wake_alarm</literal> capability, the real time clock "
"(<acronym>RTC</acronym>) alarm is used. This can only be set for one alarm "
"at a time. In this case, a special Wake From Suspend dialog is used to "
"configure it. The dialog allows the Wake From Suspend alarm to be set, "
"cancelled or displayed. To access the dialog, select "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Actions</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Wake From Suspend</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"V sistemih, ki niso sistemi Linux, ali v sistemih Linux, kjer uporabnik nima "
"možnosti <literal>cap_wake_alarm</literal>, se uporabi alarm ure realnega "
"časa (<acronym>RTC</acronym>). To lahko nastavite samo za en alarm naenkrat. "
"V tem primeru se za konfiguracijo uporabi posebno pogovorno okno Wake From "
"Suspend. Pogovorno okno omogoča nastavitev, preklic ali prikaz alarma Wake "
"From Suspend. Za dostop do pogovornega okna izberite "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Dejanja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prebudi se iz mirovanja</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2651
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use of the Wake From Suspend function requires administrative privileges. "
"You will be prompted for the root password when you set or cancel a Wake "
"From Suspend alarm."
msgstr ""
"Uporaba funkcije Prebudi se iz mirovanja zahteva upraviteljske privilegije. "
"Ko nastavite ali prekličete alarm Obujanje iz stanja mirovanja, boste "
"pozvani k vpisu korenskega gesla."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2655
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Wake From Suspend is not supported on some computers, especially older ones, "
"and some computers only support setting a wakeup time up to 24 hours ahead. "
"There may also be restrictions on which suspend mode the function will wake "
"from. You should consider setting up test alarms to check your system's "
"capability before relying on this feature."
msgstr ""
"V nekaterih računalnikih, zlasti starejših, funkcija zbujanja iz stanja "
"mirovanja ni podprta, nekateri računalniki pa podpirajo le nastavitev časa "
"zbujanja za največ 24 ur vnaprej. Obstajajo lahko tudi omejitve glede načina "
"mirovanja, iz katerega se bo funkcija prebudila. Preden se zanesete na to "
"funkcijo, razmislite o nastavitvi testnih alarmov, da preverite zmogljivost "
"sistema."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2662
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Your computer can only schedule a single Wake From Suspend at a time. If you "
"use this function with &kalarm;, you must ensure that this does not conflict "
"with any other application which also uses Wake From Suspend. Whenever an "
"application schedules or clears Wake From Suspend, this cancels any "
"previously set Wake From Suspend, no matter whether set by &kalarm; or any "
"other application."
msgstr ""
"Računalnik lahko naenkrat načrtuje le eno prebuditev iz stanja mirovanja. Če "
"to funkcijo uporabljate s funkcijo &kalarm;, morate zagotoviti, da ne pride "
"do konflikta z drugimi aplikacijami, ki prav tako uporabljajo funkcijo "
"Prebudi se iz mirovanja. Kadar koli aplikacija načrtuje ali izbriše funkcijo "
"Bujenje iz stanja mirovanja, to razveljavi vse predhodno nastavljene "
"funkcije Bujenje iz stanja mirovanja, ne glede na to, ali jih je nastavil "
"&kalarm; ali katera koli druga aplikacija."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2670
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Wake From Suspend dialog is used in conjunction with the alarm list in "
"&kalarm;'s main window."
msgstr ""
"Pogovorno okno Prebuditev iz stanja mirovanja se uporablja v povezavi s "
"seznamom alarmov v glavnem oknu programa &kalarm;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2675
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Use highlighted alarm</guibutton>: this sets the alarm currently "
"highlighted in the alarm list as the Wake From Suspend alarm. Any existing "
"scheduled Wake From Suspend is cancelled, as explained above. The button is "
"enabled only if exactly one alarm is highlighted."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Uporabi poudarjen alarm</guibutton>: s tem nastavite alarm, ki je "
"trenutno označen na seznamu alarmov, kot alarm v stanju mirovanja. Vsako "
"obstoječe načrtovano prebujanje iz stanja mirovanja se prekliče, kot je "
"pojasnjeno zgoraj. Gumb je omogočen le, če je označen natanko en alarm."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2683
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Cancel wake from suspend</guibutton>: this cancels any existing "
"Wake From Suspend (whether set by &kalarm; or any other application - see "
"above). Note that this only cancels the wakeup function associated with the "
"alarm; the alarm itself is not deleted and will continue to operate as "
"normal."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Prekliči prebuditev iz stanja mirovanja</guibutton>: prekliče vse "
"obstoječe prebuditve iz stanja mirovanja (ki jih je nastavil &kalarm; ali "
"katera koli druga aplikacija - glej zgoraj). Upoštevajte, da se s tem "
"prekliče samo funkcija zbujanja, povezana z alarmom; sam alarm se ne izbriše "
"in bo še naprej deloval kot običajno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2691
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Show current alarm</guibutton>: this highlights the current Wake "
"From Suspend alarm in the alarm list, so that it can be identified. The "
"button is disabled if no Wake From Suspend is currently configured."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Pokaži trenutni alarm</guibutton>: s tem na seznamu alarmov "
"poudarite trenutni alarm Prebujanje iz stanja mirovanja, da ga lahko "
"prepoznate. Gumb je onemogočen, če trenutno ni konfigurirana funkcija "
"Prebudi iz stanja mirovanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2698
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Number of minutes before alarm to wake from suspend</guilabel> "
"control allows you, if you wish, to ensure that the system has time to fully "
"restore itself before the alarm triggers, so that the alarm can trigger at "
"the correct time."
msgstr ""
"S kontrolnikom <guilabel>Število minut pred alarmom za prebuditev iz stanja "
"mirovanja</guilabel> lahko po želji zagotovite, da ima sistem čas, da se "
"pred sprožitvijo alarma popolnoma obnovi, tako da se alarm lahko sproži ob "
"pravem času."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2709
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quitting &kalarm;"
msgstr "Zapiranje &kalarm;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2711
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Quit &kalarm; by selecting <menuchoice> <guimenu>File</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, or "
"<menuchoice><guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem></menuchoice> in the system tray "
"icon context menu. Alternatively, if the system tray icon is not visible, "
"close all &kalarm;'s windows."
msgstr ""
"&kalarm; zaprete tako, da izberete <menuchoice> <guimenu>Datoteka</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Končaj</guimenuitem></menuchoice> ali "
"<menuchoice><guimenuitem>Končaj</guimenuitem></menuchoice> v kontekstnem "
"meniju ikone v sistemski vrstici. Če ikona v sistemski vrstici ni vidna, "
"zaprite vsa okna programa &kalarm;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2721
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring &kalarm;"
msgstr "Konfiguriranje &kalarm;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2723
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To configure &kalarm;'s operation to suit your system and your personal "
"preferences, select <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Configure &kalarm;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. This displays "
"the Configuration dialog."
msgstr ""
"Če želite konfigurirati delovanje &kalarm; tako, da ustreza vašemu sistemu "
"in vašim osebnim željam, izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Konfiguracija &kalarm;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Prikaže "
"se pogovorno okno Konfiguracija."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2729
#, no-c-format
msgid "General"
msgstr "Splošno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2731
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>General</guilabel> section lets you control &kalarm;'s overall "
"behavior:"
msgstr ""
"V razdelku <guilabel>Splošno</guilabel> lahko upravljate splošno obnašanje "
"programa &kalarm;:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2736
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Run Mode</guilabel>: This allows you to select whether &kalarm; "
"should run automatically, manually or not at all."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Način izvajanja</guilabel>: To vam omogoča, da izberete, ali se "
"mora &kalarm; izvajati samodejno, ročno ali pa sploh ne."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2741
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Run automatically</guilabel>: Select this to run &kalarm; "
"automatically at login to ensure that it always runs. This option must be "
"selected for &kalarm; to function normally and to always trigger alarms."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Samodejno zaženi</guilabel>: izberite to možnost za zagon &kalarm; "
"samodejno ob prijavi, da zagotovite, da se vedno izvaja. To možnost morate "
"izbrati za &kalarm; da deluje normalno in da vedno sproža alarme."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2748
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Run manually only</guilabel>: Select this if you only want to use "
"&kalarm; occasionally. It will not run automatically, and you will need to "
"run it manually when you require it. Once it quits (or after you log out), "
"it will no longer function or trigger alarms until you run it manually again."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Zaženi samo ročno</guilabel>: izberite to možnost, če želite "
"uporabljati &kalarm; samo občasno. Ne bo se zagnal samodejno in ga boste "
"morali zagnati ročno, ko ga boste potrebovali. Ko se zapre (ali ko se "
"odjavite), ne bo več deloval ali sprožal alarmov, dokler ga znova ne "
"zaženete ročno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2756
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Do not run</guilabel>: Select this if you want to stop using "
"&kalarm;. It will no longer be started at login and after it quits or you "
"log out, it will no longer trigger alarms."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Ne zaženi</guilabel>: izberite to možnost, če želite prenehati "
"uporabljati &kalarm;. Ne bo se več zagnal ob prijavi in ​​ko se zapre ali se "
"odjavite, ne bo več sprožal alarmov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2760
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that if you later run &kalarm; again after selecting this option, "
"&kalarm; will then resume normal functioning and will be run automatically "
"at login. If you still do not want to use &kalarm; after that, you will need "
"to select this <guilabel>Do not run</guilabel> option once more."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da če znova kasneje zaženete &kalarm; po izbiri te možnosti, bo "
"&kalarm; nato ponovno začel normalno delovati in se samodejno zagnal ob "
"prijavi. Če še vedno &kalarm; ne želite uporabljati po tem, boste morali še "
"enkrat izbrati to možnost <guilabel>Ne zaženi</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2770
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Warn before quitting</guilabel>: &kalarm; must be running for "
"alarms to trigger. Select this option so that if you attempt to terminate "
"&kalarm; using its <menuchoice><guimenu>Quit</guimenu></menuchoice> option, "
"you will be warned that alarms will be disabled and prompted for "
"confirmation. This prevents accidental disabling of alarms. For safety, this "
"option is automatically re-enabled by default whenever you change run mode."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Opozori pred izhodom</guilabel>: &kalarm; mora delovati, da se "
"sprožijo alarmi. To možnost izberite tako, da če poskušate prekiniti "
"&kalarm; z njegovo možnostjo <menuchoice><guimenu>Izhod</guimenu></"
"menuchoice> boste opozorjeni, da bodo alarmi onemogočeni in pozvani k "
"potrditvi. To preprečuje nenamerno onemogočanje alarmov. Zaradi varnosti je "
"ta možnost privzeto samodejno znova omogočena vsakič, ko spremenite način "
"delovanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2780
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Enable alarm names</guilabel>: Specify whether each alarm can be "
"given a name to help you to identify it. This determines whether the "
"<guilabel>Name</guilabel> column will be shown in the <link linkend=\"alarm-"
"list\">alarm list</link>, and whether the <guilabel>Alarm name</guilabel> "
"field will appear in the <link linkend=\"alarm-edit-dlg\">Alarm Edit dialog</"
"link>."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Omogoči namena alarmov</guilabel>: Določite, ali lahko vsak alarm "
"dobi ime, ki vam bo pomagalo pri njegovi identifikaciji. To določa, ali bo "
"stolpec <guilabel>Ime</guilabel> prikazan v <link linkend=\"alarm-list"
"\">seznam alarmov</link> in ali bo polje <guilabel>Ime alarma</guilabel> "
"prikazano v <link linkend=\"alarm-edit-dlg\">Pogovorno okno urejanja "
"alarmov</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2788
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Confirm alarm deletions</guilabel>: Specify whether you should be "
"prompted for confirmation each time you delete an alarm."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Potrdi brisanje alarma</guilabel>: Določite, ali naj se ob vsakem "
"brisanju alarma zahteva potrditev."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2793
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Default defer time interval</guilabel>: Enter the default time "
"interval, in hours and minutes, to show initially when the Defer Alarm "
"dialog is displayed. Note that if an alarm has been deferred previously, the "
"interval shown initially in the Defer Alarm dialog will be equal to the "
"deferral interval used the last time that alarm was deferred."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Privzeto časovno obdobje odložitve</guilabel>: Vnesite privzeti "
"časovni interval v urah in minutah, ki se na začetku prikaže, ko je "
"prikazano pogovorno okno Odloži alarm. Upoštevajte, da če je bil alarm že "
"prej odložen, bo interval, ki je na začetku prikazan v pogovornem oknu "
"Odloži alarm, enak intervalu odložitve, ki je bil uporabljen ob zadnjem "
"odlaganju tega alarma."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2801
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Terminal for Command Alarms</guilabel>: Here, you can select which "
"type of terminal window should be used for command alarms which are executed "
"in a terminal window. Some of the most common terminal window applications "
"are preconfigured, &eg; <application>xterm</application>, &konsole;, "
"although only those which are installed on your system will be shown here. "
"You can view the actual command options used for each application by "
"displaying the context help for its radio button."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Terminal za alarmne ukaze</guilabel>: Tukaj lahko izberete, katera "
"vrsta terminalskega okna naj se uporabi za alarmne ukaze, ki se izvajajo v "
"terminalskem oknu. Nekatere najpogostejše aplikacije terminalskega okna so "
"vnaprej konfigurirane, &eg; <application>xterm</application>, &konsole;, "
"vendar bodo tukaj prikazane le tiste, ki so nameščene v vašem sistemu. "
"Dejanske možnosti ukazov, ki se uporabljajo za vsako aplikacijo, si lahko "
"ogledate tako, da prikažete kontekstno pomoč za njen radijski gumb."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2810
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to use another application, or want to use one of those listed "
"but with different command options, select <guilabel>Other</guilabel> and "
"enter the command to invoke the terminal window. By default, the alarm's "
"command string will be appended to what you specify. Alternatively, you may "
"specify where the alarm's command string should be inserted, by use of the "
"following codes:"
msgstr ""
"Če želite uporabiti drugo aplikacijo ali če želite uporabiti eno od naštetih "
"aplikacij, vendar z drugimi možnostmi ukazov, izberite <guilabel>Drugo</"
"guilabel> in vnesite ukaz za priklic terminalskega okna. Privzeto se niz "
"ukazov alarma doda tistemu, ki ga določite. Lahko pa določite, kam naj se "
"vstavi niz ukazov alarma, in sicer z uporabo naslednjih kod:"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2820
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>%c</term>"
msgstr "<term>%c</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2822
#, no-c-format
msgid "The alarm's command string will be substituted."
msgstr "Nadomeščen bo niz ukazov alarma."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2826
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>%w</term>"
msgstr "<term>%w</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2828
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The alarm's command string will be substituted, with a <literal>sleep</"
"literal> appended."
msgstr "Nadomeščen bo ukazni niz alarma z dodanim <literal>spanjem</literal>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2832
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>%C</term>"
msgstr "<term>%C</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2834
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A temporary command file containing the alarm's command string will be "
"created, and the command to execute the file will be substituted."
msgstr ""
"Ustvarjena bo začasna datoteka z ukazom, ki vsebuje niz ukazov alarma, in "
"zamenjan bo ukaz za izvršitev datoteke."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2838
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>%W</term>"
msgstr "<term>%W</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2840
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A temporary command file containing the alarm's command string will be "
"created with a <literal>sleep</literal> appended, and the command to execute "
"the file will be substituted."
msgstr ""
"Ustvarjena bo začasna datoteka z ukazi, ki bo vsebovala niz ukazov alarma, z "
"dodanim <literal>spanjem</literal>, ukaz za izvršitev datoteke pa bo "
"zamenjan."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2844
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>%t</term>"
msgstr "<term>%t</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2846
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kalarm;'s name in the current language will be substituted."
msgstr ""
"nadomeščeno bo ime &kalarm; v trenutnem jeziku.Ko se sproži alarm ukaza, se "
"njegov ukazni niz pred vstavitvijo v ukaz terminalskega okna navede v "
"narekovajih."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2851
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When the command alarm is triggered, its command string will be quoted "
"before being inserted into the terminal window command."
msgstr ""
"Ko se sproži alarm ukaza, se njegov ukazni niz pred vstavitvijo v ukaz "
"terminalskega okna navede v narekovajih."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2856
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Plugins</guilabel>: This section allows you to choose which of "
"&kalarm;'s installed plugins to use."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Vtičniki</guilabel>: Ta razdelek vam omogoča, da izberete, katere "
"od nameščenih vtičnikov &kalarm; boste uporabili."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2860
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Audio Backend</guilabel>: Choose which audio system to use to play "
"sound files. Only installed audio plugins are listed; if none is installed, "
"this option is not shown."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Avdio ozadje</guilabel>: Izberite, kateri avdio sistem želite "
"uporabiti za predvajanje zvočnih datotek. Navedeni so samo nameščeni zvočni "
"vtičniki; če ni nameščeno nobenega, ta možnost ni prikazana."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2866
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Enable Akonadi</guilabel>: Choose whether to use &akonadi; to "
"provide features which depend on it. See <link linkend=\"akonadi-plugin"
"\">Akonadi plugin</link> for details. Note that this option is only shown if "
"the Akonadi plugin is installed."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Omogoči Akonadi</guilabel>: Izberite, ali želite uporabljati "
"&akonadi; za zagotavljanje funkcij, ki so od njega odvisne. Za podrobnosti "
"glejte <link linkend=\"akonadi-plugin\">Vtičnik Akonadi</link>. Upoštevajte, "
"da je ta možnost prikazana le, če je nameščen vtičnik Akonadi."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2879
#, no-c-format
msgid "Time &amp; Date"
msgstr "Čas &amp; Datum"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2881
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Time &amp; Date</guilabel> section lets you set options "
"relating to time and date:"
msgstr ""
"V razdelku <guilabel>Čas in datum</guilabel> lahko nastavite možnosti v "
"zvezi s časom in datumom:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2885
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Time zone</guilabel>: Select your time zone. &kalarm; uses this "
"time zone throughout, except when you override it for individual alarms."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Časovni pas</guilabel>: Izberite svoj časovni pas. &kalarm; "
"uporablja ta časovni pas ves čas, razen kadar ga prekrijete za posamezne "
"alarme."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2890
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Holiday region</guilabel>: Select which country's or region's "
"holidays to use. This affects recurring alarms for which the option to "
"exclude holidays is selected."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Prazniki za območje</guilabel>: Izberite države ali regije, "
"katerih praznike želite uporabiti. To vpliva na ponavljajoče se alarme, za "
"katere je izbrana možnost izključitve praznikov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2895
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Wake from suspend before alarm</guilabel>: Enter the number of "
"minutes before the alarm trigger time to wake the system, for alarms set to "
"wake from suspend. This allows you to ensure that the system has time to "
"fully restore itself before the alarm triggers, so that the alarm can "
"trigger at the correct time. This option is only shown if the system "
"configuration allows multiple alarms to wake the system from suspension. See "
"<link linkend=\"wake-suspend\">Wake From Suspend</link> for more information."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Prebujanje iz mirovanja pred alarmom</guilabel>: Vnesite število "
"minut pred časom sprožitve alarma za prebujanje sistema za alarme, "
"nastavljene na prebujanje iz mirovanja. Tako lahko zagotovite, da ima sistem "
"čas, da se pred sprožitvijo alarma popolnoma obnovi, tako da se alarm sproži "
"ob pravem času. Ta možnost je prikazana le, če konfiguracija sistema "
"omogoča, da več alarmov prebudi sistem iz stanja mirovanja. Za več "
"informacij glejte <link linkend=\"wake-suspend\">Prebujanje iz stanja "
"mirovanja</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2906
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Start of day for date-only alarms</guilabel>: Set the start-of-day "
"time for the purposes of triggering date-only alarms, &ie; ones for which "
"the <guilabel>Any time</guilabel> option was selected. On the date when they "
"are due, such alarms will be output at the earliest opportunity during the "
"24 hours starting from the start-of-day time."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Začetek dneva za datumske alarme</guilabel>: Nastavite čas začetka "
"dneva za namene sprožitve alarmov samo z datumom, &eg; tistih, za katere je "
"bila izbrana možnost <guilabel>Katerakoli ura</guilabel>. Na dan, ko so ti "
"alarmi potrebni, se bodo sprožili ob prvi priložnosti v 24 urah od začetka "
"dneva."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2914
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Working Hours</guilabel> group box: These options let you define "
"your working hours, needed when the <guilabel>Only during working hours</"
"guilabel> option is selected for a recurrence in the <link linkend=\"alarm-"
"edit-dlg-recur\">Alarm Edit dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"Skupinsko polje <guilabel>Delovni čas</guilabel>: Te možnosti vam omogočajo, "
"da določite delovni čas, ki je potreben, ko je v <link linkend=\"alarm-edit-"
"dlg-recur\">pogovornem oknu za urejanje alarma</link> izbrana možnost "
"<guilabel>Samo med delovnim časom</guilabel> za ponavljanje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2921
#, no-c-format
msgid "Check each day which is a working day."
msgstr "Preverite vsak dan, ki je delovni dan."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2924
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Daily start time</guilabel>: enter the time at which you start "
"work each day."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Začetni čas dneva</guilabel>: vnesite čas, ob katerem začnete "
"delati vsak dan."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2928
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Daily end time</guilabel>: enter the time at which you finish work "
"each day."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Končni čas dneva</guilabel>: vnesite čas, ob katerem vsak dan "
"zaključite delo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2934
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>KOrganizer event duration</guilabel>: Enter the event duration to "
"set in &korganizer; for alarms which are copied to &korganizer;. The default "
"duration is zero."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Trajanje dogodka za KOrganizer</guilabel>: Vnesite trajanje "
"dogodka, ki ga nastavite v &korganizer; za alarme, ki se kopirajo v "
"&korganizer;. Privzeto trajanje je nič."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2943
#, no-c-format
msgid "Storage"
msgstr "Shranjevanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2945
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Storage</guilabel> section lets you choose options for saving "
"and archiving alarms:"
msgstr ""
"V razdelku <guilabel>Shranjevanje</guilabel> lahko izberete možnosti za "
"shranjevanje in arhiviranje alarmov:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2950
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>New Alarms &amp; Templates</guilabel>: Specify which calendar to "
"store new alarms and alarm templates in when using multiple alarm calendars:"
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Novi alarmi &amp; predloge</guilabel>: Določite, v katerem "
"koledarju se shranijo novi alarmi in predloge za alarme, če uporabljate več "
"koledarjev za alarme:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2956
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Store in default calendar</guilabel>: New alarms and alarm "
"templates are automatically added to the default alarm calendar without "
"prompting for confirmation."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Shrani v privzeti koledar</guilabel>: Novi alarmi in predloge "
"alarmov se samodejno dodajo v privzeti koledar alarmov brez poziva za "
"potrditev."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2962
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Prompt for which calendar to store in</guilabel>: When you create "
"a new alarm or alarm template and there is more than one writeable alarm "
"calendar, you will be prompted to choose which calendar to save it in. Note "
"that when alarms are saved on expiry, they are always stored in the default "
"archived alarm calendar without prompting."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Vprašaj, po koledarju za shranjevanje</guilabel>: Ko ustvarite nov "
"alarm ali predlogo za alarm in obstaja več kot en koledar za zapisovanje "
"alarmov, boste pozvani, da izberete, v kateri koledar naj se shrani. "
"Upoštevajte, da so alarmi, shranjeni ob izteku veljavnosti, brez poziva "
"vedno shranjeni v privzeti arhivirani koledar za alarme."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2972
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Archived Alarms</guilabel> group box: These options control the "
"storage of archived alarms in the default archived alarm calendar."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Arhivirani alarmi</guilabel>: Te možnosti nadzorujejo shranjevanje "
"arhiviranih alarmov v privzetem koledarju arhiviranih alarmov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2977
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Keep alarms after expiry</guilabel>: Select this option to archive "
"expired and deleted alarms. Deselect it to keep no record of alarms once "
"they cease to be active. Note that deleted alarms are only archived if they "
"have previously been triggered. If you delete an alarm before it ever "
"triggers, it is discarded."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Ohrani alarme po preteku</guilabel>: Izberite to možnost, če "
"želite arhivirati pretečene in izbrisane alarme. Izberite jo, če želite, da "
"se alarmi ne beležijo več, ko prenehajo biti aktivni. Upoštevajte, da se "
"izbrisani alarmi arhivirajo le, če so bili predhodno sproženi. Če alarm "
"izbrišete, preden se sploh sproži, se zavrže."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2985
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Discard archived alarms after</guilabel>: Set the number of days "
"to store expired and deleted alarms in the archive, after which they are "
"permanently deleted."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Zavrzi arhivirane alarme po</guilabel>: Nastavite število dni za "
"shranjevanje pretečenih in izbrisanih alarmov v arhivu, nato pa se trajno "
"izbrišejo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2990
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Clear archived alarms</guibutton>: This button discards all "
"currently archived alarms from the default archived alarm calendar. (Other "
"archived alarm calendars are left unchanged in case they are shared with "
"other people.) This has no effect on alarms which subsequently expire or are "
"deleted; they will continue to be archived according to the selected options."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Počisti arhivirane alarme</guibutton>: Ta gumb izbriše vse "
"trenutno arhivirane alarme iz privzetega koledarja arhiviranih alarmov. "
"(Drugi arhivirani koledarji budilke ostanejo nespremenjeni, če jih delite z "
"drugimi osebami.) To ne vpliva na alarme, ki jim pozneje poteče veljavnost "
"ali so izbrisani; še naprej se bodo arhivirali v skladu z izbranimi "
"možnostmi."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3004
#, no-c-format
msgid "Email"
msgstr "E-pošta"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3006
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Email</guilabel> section lets you choose options for sending "
"and addressing email alarms:"
msgstr ""
"Razdelek <guilabel>E-pošta</guilabel> vam omogoča izbiro možnosti za "
"pošiljanje in naslavljanje e-poštnih alarmov:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3009
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Options dependent on &kmail; are only available if &kalarm;'s <link linkend="
"\"akonadi-plugin\">Akonadi plugin</link> is installed and enabled."
msgstr ""
"Možnosti, odvisne od &kmail; so na voljo le, če je &kalarm; <link linkend="
"\"akonadi-plugin\">vtičnik Akonadi</link> nameščen in omogočen."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3016
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Email client</guilabel>: Specify the email client to be used to "
"send email alarms:"
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Odjemalec E-pošte</guilabel>: Določite e-poštni odjemalec, ki bo "
"uporabljen za pošiljanje e-poštnih alarmov:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3020
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>KMail</guilabel>: When an email alarm is triggered, the email is "
"sent automatically using &kmail;."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>KMail</guilabel>: Ko se sproži e-poštni alarm, se e-pošta "
"samodejno pošlje z &kmail;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3024
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Sendmail</guilabel>: When an email alarm is triggered, the email "
"is sent automatically using &Sendmail;. This option will only work if your "
"system is configured to use &Sendmail;, or a &Sendmail; compatible mail "
"transport agent such as <application>postfix</application> or "
"<application>qmail</application>."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Sendmail</guilabel>: Ko se sproži e-poštni alarm, se e-pošta "
"samodejno pošlje s &Sendmail;. Ta možnost bo delovala samo, če je vaš sistem "
"konfiguriran za uporabo &Sendmail; ali &Sendmail; združljiv posrednik za "
"prenos pošte, kot je <application>postfix</application> ali "
"<application>qmail</application>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3036
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Copy sent emails into &kmail;'s \"sent-mail\" folder</guilabel>: "
"Select this option if, every time an email alarm is triggered, you want a "
"copy of the transmitted email to be stored in &kmail;'s <filename>sent-mail</"
"filename> folder."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Skopiraj poslana e-pošto sporočila v &kmail;ovo mapo »poslano«</"
"guilabel>: izberite to možnost, če želite, da se kopija poslanega e-poštnega "
"sporočila shrani v &kmail;' s mapo <filename>poslano</filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3041
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option is not available when &kmail; is selected as the email client, "
"since &kmail; automatically does this."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost ni na voljo, ko &kmail; je izbran kot e-poštni odjemalec, saj "
"&kmail; samodejno naredi to."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3046
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Notify when remote emails are queued</guilabel>: Select this "
"option to display a notification whenever an email alarm queues an email for "
"sending to a remote system. This may be useful if, for example, you have a "
"dial-up connection, or email is queued in &kmail;'s <filename>outbox</"
"filename> folder, so that you can ensure that you do whatever is needed to "
"actually transmit the email."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Obvesti, ko so oddaljena e-poštna sporočila postavljena v vrsto</"
"guilabel>: izberite to možnost, če želite prikazati obvestilo vsakič, ko e-"
"poštni alarm postavi e-pošto v čakalno vrsto za pošiljanje v oddaljeni "
"sistem. To je lahko uporabno, če imate na primer klicno povezavo ali je e-"
"pošta v čakalni vrsti v &kmail; mapi <filename>odhajajoče</filename>, tako "
"da lahko zagotovite, da naredite vse, kar je potrebno za dejansko pošiljanje "
"e-pošta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3056
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select your email address to be used as the sender's address in email alarms:"
msgstr ""
"Izberite svoj e-poštni naslov, ki bo uporabljen kot naslov pošiljatelja v e-"
"poštnih alarmih:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3060
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select <guilabel>From</guilabel> to enter an email address."
msgstr "Izberite <guilabel>Od</guilabel>, da vnesete e-poštni naslov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3064 index.docbook:3089
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select <guilabel>Use default KMail identity</guilabel> to use your default "
"email address which is configured in &kmail;."
msgstr ""
"Izberite <guilabel>Uporabi privzeto istovetnosti KMail</guilabel>, da "
"uporabite svoj privzeti e-poštni naslov, ki je nastavljen v &kmail;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3068
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select <guilabel>Use &kmail; identities</guilabel> to be able to choose at "
"the time you configure an email alarm which of &kmail;'s email identities to "
"use. &kmail;'s default identity will be used for alarms which were already "
"configured before you selected this option."
msgstr ""
"Izberite <guilabel>Uporabi istovetnosti &kmail;a</guilabel>, da lahko med "
"konfiguracijo e-poštnega alarma izberete, katero e-poštno identiteto &kmail; "
"želite uporabiti. Privzeta identiteta &kmail; bo uporabljena za alarme, ki "
"so bili že nastavljeni, preden ste izbrali to možnost."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3078
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select your email address to be used for sending blind copies of email "
"alarms to yourself when the <guilabel>Copy email to self</guilabel> option "
"is selected:"
msgstr ""
"Izberite svoj e-poštni naslov, ki bo uporabljen za pošiljanje slepih kopij e-"
"poštnih alarmov sebi, ko je izbrana možnost <guilabel>Kopiraj e-pošto sebi</"
"guilabel>:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3083
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select <guilabel>Bcc</guilabel> to enter an email address. If blind copies "
"are to be sent to your account on the computer which &kalarm; runs on, you "
"could simply enter your user login name here."
msgstr ""
"Izberite <guilabel>Skp</guilabel>, da vnesete e-poštni naslov. Če naj bodo "
"slepe kopije poslane na vaš račun v računalniku, ki ga &kalarm; deluje, "
"lahko tukaj preprosto vnesete svoje uporabniško ime za prijavo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3098
#, no-c-format
msgid "View"
msgstr "Pogled"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3100
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>View</guilabel> section lets you control some aspects of "
"&kalarm;'s appearance. In the <guilabel>General</guilabel> tab:"
msgstr ""
"Razdelek <guilabel>Pogled</guilabel> vam omogoča nadzor nekaterih vidikov "
"videza &kalarm;. Na zavihku <guilabel>Splošno</guilabel>:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Show in system tray</guilabel> group box: When selected, the "
"system tray icon is displayed while &kalarm; is running, subject to the "
"selected option:"
msgstr ""
"Skupinsko polje <guilabel>Pokaži v sistemskem pladnju</guilabel>: Ko je "
"izbrano, je prikazana ikona sistemske vrstice, medtem ko &kalarm; teče glede "
"na izbrano možnost:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3112
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Always show</guilabel>: The system tray icon is always displayed."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Vedno prikaži</guilabel>: Ikona sistemske vrstice je vedno "
"prikazana."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3117
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Automatically hide if no active alarms</guilabel>: The system tray "
"icon is hidden if there are no active alarms."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Samodejno skrij, če ni aktivnih alarmov</guilabel>: ikona v "
"sistemski vrstici je skrita, če ni aktivnih alarmov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3122
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Automatically hide if no alarm due within time period</guilabel>: "
"The system tray icon is hidden if no alarm is due within the entered time "
"period, starting from now."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Samodejno skrij, če v določenem časovnem obdobju ni alarma</"
"guilabel>: ikona v sistemski vrstici je skrita, če v vnesenem časovnem "
"obdobju ni alarma, od zdaj naprej."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3128
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When the system tray icon is automatically hidden, you can make it visible "
"by means of the system tray option to show hidden icons."
msgstr ""
"Ko je ikona sistemske vrstice samodejno skrita, jo lahko naredite vidno z "
"možnostjo sistemske vrstice za prikaz skritih ikon."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3131
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When <guilabel>Show in system tray</guilabel> is selected, closing the "
"system tray icon closes all &kalarm; main windows, and if no message windows "
"are visible, quits the application."
msgstr ""
"Ko je izbrana možnost <guilabel>Pokaži v sistemski vrstici</guilabel>, "
"zapiranje ikone sistemske vrstice zapre vse &kalarm; glavna okna, in če ni "
"vidnih oken s sporočili, zapre aplikacijo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3137
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>System Tray Tooltip</guilabel> group box: These options control "
"what information is shown in the tooltip which appears when the mouse cursor "
"hovers over &kalarm;'s system tray icon."
msgstr ""
"Skupinsko okno <guilabel>Orodni namig v sistemski vrstici</guilabel>: Te "
"možnosti nadzirajo, katere informacije so prikazane v orodni vrstici, ki se "
"pojavi, ko miškin kazalec premaknete nad ikono sistemske vrstice &kalarm;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3143
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Show next 24 hours' alarms</guilabel>: When selected, a summary of "
"the first few alarms due in the next 24 hours is displayed."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Pokaži alarme v naslednjih 24 urah</guilabel>: Ko izberete, se "
"prikaže povzetek prvih nekaj alarmov v naslednjih 24 urah."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3149
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Maximum number of alarms to show</guilabel>: Deselect this option "
"to display all of the next 24 hours' alarms. Select it to set the maximum "
"number of alarms which will be displayed."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Največje število alarmov, ki naj bodo prikazani</guilabel>: "
"Odznačite to možnost, če želite prikazati vse alarme za naslednjih 24 ur. "
"Izberite ga, da nastavite največje število alarmov, ki bodo prikazani."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3155
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Show alarm time</guilabel>: Select this option to show the time at "
"which each alarm is scheduled."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Pokaži čas alarma</guilabel>: izberite to možnost, če želite "
"prikazati čas, ob katerem je načrtovan vsak alarm."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3160
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Show time until alarm</guilabel>: Select this option to show the "
"length of time remaining before each alarm's next scheduled occurrence. The "
"length of time is shown in hours and minutes."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Pokaži čas do alarma</guilabel>: izberite to možnost, če želite "
"prikazati preostali čas do naslednjega načrtovanega pojava vsakega alarma. "
"Dolžina časa je prikazana v urah in minutah."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3166
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Prefix</guilabel>: Specify a symbol or text to show in front of "
"the length of time until the alarm, to distinguish it from the time at which "
"the alarm is scheduled."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Predpona</guilabel>: Določite simbol ali besedilo, ki naj bo "
"prikazano pred časom do alarma, da ga ločite od ure, na katero je alarm "
"načrtovan."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3176
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Alarm List</guilabel> group box allows the selection of the "
"colors used in the alarm list in &kalarm;'s main window, to show disabled "
"and archived alarms."
msgstr ""
"Polje skupine <guilabel>Seznam alarmov</guilabel> omogoča izbiro barv, "
"uporabljenih na seznamu alarmov v glavnem oknu &kalarm;, za prikaz "
"onemogočenih in arhiviranih alarmov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3182
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Alarm Windows</guilabel> tab contains options to control the "
"appearance of alarm message windows. The available options depend on the "
"windowing system in use."
msgstr ""
"Zavihek <guilabel>Alarmna okna</guilabel> vsebuje možnosti za nadzor videza "
"oken z alarmnimi sporočili. Razpoložljive možnosti so odvisne od "
"uporabljenega okenskega sistema."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3192
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Position windows far from mouse cursor</guilabel>: Select this "
"option to display alarm message windows as far away from the current mouse "
"cursor position as possible. This minimizes the chance of accidentally "
"acknowledging an alarm by unintentionally clicking on a button just as the "
"message window appears."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Postavi okna čim dlje od miškine kazalke</guilabel>: Izberite to "
"možnost, če želite prikazati okna alarmnih sporočil čim dlje od trenutnega "
"položaja miškine kazalke. To zmanjša možnost nenamerne potrditve alarma z "
"nenamernim klikom na gumb, ravno ko se prikaže okno s sporočilom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3200
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Center windows, delay activating window buttons</guilabel>: Select "
"this option to display alarm message windows in the center of the screen. To "
"reduce the chance of accidentally acknowledging the alarm, the window's "
"buttons are initially disabled. The delay in seconds before they become "
"active is set in <guilabel>Button activation delay (seconds)</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Usredini okna, zakasni omogočanje gumbov v oknih</guilabel>: "
"izberite to možnost, če želite okna z alarmnimi sporočili prikazati na "
"sredini zaslona. Da bi zmanjšali možnost nenamerne potrditve alarma, so "
"gumbi okna na začetku onemogočeni. Zakasnitev v sekundah, preden postanejo "
"aktivni, je nastavljena v <guilabel>Zakasnitev omogočanja gumbov (sekunde)</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3209
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Message windows have a titlebar and take keyboard focus</"
"guilabel>: This option controls whether alarm message windows are modal or "
"not, &ie; whether they grab the keyboard focus when they appear. See the "
"<link linkend=\"message-display\">Alarm Message Display</link> section for "
"details."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Sporočilna okna imajo nazivno vrstico in prevzamejo žarišče "
"tipkovnice</guilabel>: Ta možnost nadzoruje, ali so okna z alarmnimi "
"sporočili modalna ali ne, &ie;. ali zgrabijo fokus tipkovnice, ko se "
"pojavijo. Za podrobnosti glejte razdelek <link linkend=\"message-display"
"\">Prikaz alarmnih sporočil</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3223
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To reduce the chance of accidentally acknowledging the alarm, the window's "
"buttons are initially disabled. The delay in seconds before they become "
"active is set in <guilabel>Button activation delay (seconds)</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Da bi zmanjšali možnost nenamerne potrditve alarma, so gumbi okna na začetku "
"onemogočeni. Zakasnitev v sekundah, preden postanejo aktivni, je nastavljena "
"v <guilabel>Zakasnitev aktiviranja gumba (sekunde)</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3235
#, no-c-format
msgid "Edit"
msgstr "Uredi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3237
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Edit</guilabel> section lets you choose default values for the "
"options in the <link linkend=\"alarm-edit-dlg\">Alarm Edit dialog</link>:"
msgstr ""
"V razdelku <guilabel>Uredi</guilabel> lahko izberete privzete vrednosti za "
"možnosti v <link linkend=\"alarm-edit-dlg\">pogovornem oknu za urejanje "
"alarma</link>:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3242
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>General</guilabel> tab contains options which apply to all "
"alarm types."
msgstr ""
"Zavihek <guilabel>Splošno</guilabel> vsebuje možnosti, ki veljajo za vse "
"vrste alarmov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3246
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set the default method for displaying alarm messages."
msgstr "Nastavite privzeti način za prikaz alarmnih sporočil."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3250
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the default states for the <guilabel>Show in KOrganizer</guilabel> and "
"<guilabel>Cancel if late</guilabel> check boxes."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite privzeta stanja za potrditveni polji <guilabel>Pokaži v "
"KOrganizerju</guilabel> in <guilabel>Prekliči, če zamuja</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3255
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set the default recurrence type."
msgstr "Nastavi privzeto vrsto ponavljanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3258
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the default handling in non-leap years of yearly recurrences "
"scheduled for February 29th."
msgstr ""
"Izberite privzeto obravnavanje v neprestopnih letih letnih ponovitev, "
"načrtovanih za 29. februar."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3264
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Alarm Types</guilabel> tab contains options which apply to "
"specific types of alarm."
msgstr ""
"Zavihek <guilabel>Vrste alarmov</guilabel> vsebuje možnosti, ki veljajo za "
"določene vrste alarmov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3269
#, no-c-format
msgid "For display alarms:"
msgstr "Za prikazne alarme:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3272
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the default states for the <guilabel>Auto-close window after this time</"
"guilabel> and <guilabel>Confirm acknowledgment</guilabel> check boxes."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite privzeta stanja za potrditveni polji <guilabel>Samodejno zapri "
"okno po tem času</guilabel> in <guilabel>Potrdi seznanjenost</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3277
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set the default reminder period units."
msgstr "Nastavite privzete enote obdobja opomina."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3280
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set the default special display alarm actions."
msgstr "Nastavite privzeta posebna dejanja alarma zaslona."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3283
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the default sound options. Note that a default sound file may be "
"specified even if the sound type is not set to <guilabel>Sound file</"
"guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite privzete možnosti zvoka. Upoštevajte, da je lahko določena "
"privzeta zvočna datoteka, tudi če vrsta zvoka ni nastavljena na "
"<guilabel>Zvočna datoteka</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3291
#, no-c-format
msgid "For command alarms:"
msgstr "Za ukazne alarme:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3294
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the default states for the <guilabel>Enter a script</guilabel> and "
"<guilabel>Execute in terminal window</guilabel> check boxes."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite privzeta stanja za potrditveni polji <guilabel>Vnesi skript</"
"guilabel> in <guilabel>Izvedi v terminalskem oknu</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3302
#, no-c-format
msgid "For email alarms:"
msgstr "Za e-poštne alarme:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3305
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the default state for the <guilabel>Copy email to self</guilabel> check "
"box."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite privzeto stanje za potrditveno polje <guilabel>Pošlji kopijo e-"
"pošte sebi</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3313
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Font &amp; Color</guilabel> tab lets you set the default "
"appearance of alarm messages. Select their default font, and foreground and "
"background colors."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Pisava &amp; Zavihek Barva</guilabel> omogoča nastavitev "
"privzetega videza alarmnih sporočil. Izberite njihovo privzeto pisavo ter "
"barve ospredja in ozadja."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3323
#, no-c-format
msgid "Command Line Operation"
msgstr "Delovanje ukazne vrstice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3325
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When command line parameters are supplied, &kalarm; does not display the "
"list of scheduled alarms as described in <link linkend=\"using-kalarm"
"\">Using &kalarm;</link> above. Command line options specific to &kalarm; "
"may be used to perform the following operations:"
msgstr ""
"Ko so podani parametri ukazne vrstice, &kalarm; ne prikaže seznama "
"načrtovanih alarmov, kot je opisano v <link linkend=\"using-kalarm\">Uporaba "
"&kalarm;</link> zgoraj. Možnosti ukazne vrstice, specifične za &kalarm; se "
"lahko uporablja za izvajanje naslednjih operacij:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3332 index.docbook:3738
#, no-c-format
msgid "schedule a new alarm"
msgstr "načrtuj nov alarm"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3334
#, no-c-format
msgid "control &kalarm;'s display mode"
msgstr "nadzor &kalarm; načina prikaza"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3336
#, no-c-format
msgid "obtain help"
msgstr "pridobi pomoč"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3340
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additional command line options are provided primarily to enable other "
"programs to interface to &kalarm;. They are described in the chapter <link "
"linkend=\"cmdline-interface\">Developer's Guide to &kalarm;</link>."
msgstr ""
"Dodatne možnosti ukazne vrstice so na voljo predvsem zato, da drugim "
"programom omogočijo vmesnik do &kalarm;. Opisani so v poglavju <link linkend="
"\"cmdline-interface\">Razvijalski vodnik za &kalarm;</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3345
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The command line must only contain options applicable to one &kalarm; "
"operation. If you want to perform multiple operations, you must invoke "
"&kalarm; multiple times with a single set of options each time."
msgstr ""
"Ukazna vrstica mora vsebovati samo možnosti, ki veljajo za en &kalarm; "
"delovanje. Če želite izvesti več operacij, morate priklicati &kalarm; "
"večkrat z enim naborom možnosti vsakič."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3351
#, no-c-format
msgid "Schedule a New Alarm"
msgstr "Načrtuj nov alarm"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3353
#, no-c-format
msgid "The following options are used to schedule a new alarm:"
msgstr "Za načrtovanje novega alarma se uporabljajo naslednje možnosti:"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3359 index.docbook:3665 index.docbook:4956
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option"
msgstr "Možnost"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3360 index.docbook:3666 index.docbook:4957
#, no-c-format
msgid "<entry>Description</entry>"
msgstr "<entry>Opis</entry>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3365
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>-a</option>, <option>--ack-confirm</option>"
msgstr "<option>-a</option>, <option>--ack-confirm</option>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3366
#, no-c-format
msgid "Prompt for confirmation when the alarm message is acknowledged."
msgstr "Poziv za potrditev, ko je alarmno sporočilo potrjeno."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3370
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<option>-A</option>, <option>--attach <replaceable>URL</replaceable></option>"
msgstr ""
"<option>-A</option>, <option>--attach <replaceable>URL</replaceable></option>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3371
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specify the path or &URL; of a file which is to be attached to the email. "
"This option may be repeated as necessary. <option>--mail</option> must be "
"specified with this option."
msgstr ""
"Navedite pot ali &URL; datoteke, ki bo priložena e-pošti. To možnost lahko "
"po potrebi ponovite. <option>--mail</option> mora biti določena s to "
"možnostjo."

#. Tag: option
#: index.docbook:3376
#, no-c-format
msgid "--auto-close"
msgstr "--auto-close"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3377
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Automatically close the alarm window after the expiry of the <option>--late-"
"cancel</option> period. <option>--late-cancel</option> must be specified "
"with this option."
msgstr ""
"Samodejno zapre okno alarma po poteku obdobja <option>--late-cancel</"
"option>. <option>--late-cancel</option> mora biti določena s to možnostjo."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3383
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>-b</option>, <option>--beep</option>"
msgstr "<option>-b</option>, <option>--beep</option>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3384
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Make an audible beep when the message is displayed. <option>--speak</"
"option>, <option>--play</option> and <option>--play-repeat</option> cannot "
"be specified with this option."
msgstr ""
"Ob prikazu sporočila se oglasi zvočni signal. <option>--speak</option>, "
"<option>--play</option> in <option>--play-repeat</option> ni mogoče določiti "
"s to možnostjo."

#. Tag: option
#: index.docbook:3390
#, no-c-format
msgid "--bcc"
msgstr "--bcc"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3391
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Blind copy the email to yourself. <option>--mail</option> must be specified "
"with this option."
msgstr ""
"Slepo kopirajte e-pošto sebi. <option>--mail</option> mora biti določena s "
"to možnostjo."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3395
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<option>-c</option>, <option>--color</option>, <option>--colour "
"<replaceable>color</replaceable></option>"
msgstr ""
"<option>-c</option>, <option>--color</option>, <option>--colour "
"<replaceable>color</replaceable></option>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3397
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the message background color to the specified &Qt; color name or hex "
"code 0xRRGGBB."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite barvo ozadja sporočila na določeno ime barve &Qt; ali "
"šestnajstiško kodo 0xRRGGBB."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3401
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<option>-C</option>, <option>--colorfg</option>, <option>--colourfg "
"<replaceable>color</replaceable></option>"
msgstr ""
"<option>-C</option>, <option>--colorfg</option>, <option>--colourfg "
"<replaceable>color</replaceable></option>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3403
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the message foreground color to the specified &Qt; color name or hex "
"code 0xRRGGBB."
msgstr ""
"Nastavi barvo sporočila v ospredju na določeno &Qt; ime barve ali "
"šestnajstiško kodo 0xRRGGBB."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3407
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>-d</option>, <option>--disable</option>"
msgstr "<option>-d</option>, <option>--disable</option>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3408
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Disable the alarm. It will not trigger until it has been manually enabled."
msgstr "Onemogočite alarm. Ne bo se sprožila, dokler ne bo ročno omogočena."

#. Tag: option
#: index.docbook:3412 index.docbook:3714
#, no-c-format
msgid "--disable-all"
msgstr "--disable-all"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3413
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Disable alarm monitoring. This prevents any alarms from being triggered "
"until you re-enable alarms or restart &kalarm;, &eg; at next login. "
"<option>--triggerEvent</option> cannot be specified with this option."
msgstr ""
"Onemogočite spremljanje alarma. To prepreči sprožitev vseh alarmov, dokler "
"ob naslednji prijavi ponovno ne omogočite alarmov ali ponovno zaženete "
"&kalarm;, &eg;. <option>--sprožiDogodek</option> ni mogoče določiti s to "
"možnostjo."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3420
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<option>-e</option>, <option>--exec <replaceable>commandline</replaceable></"
"option>"
msgstr ""
"<option>-e</option>, <option>--exec <replaceable>commandline</replaceable></"
"option>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3421
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specify a shell command to execute. If specified, this option must be the "
"last &kalarm; option in &kalarm;'s command line. All subsequent command "
"parameters and options are interpreted as forming the command line to "
"execute. <option>--file</option> and <option>--exec-display</option> and "
"<option>--mail</option> cannot be specified with this option. <option>--ack-"
"confirm</option>, <option>--beep</option>, <option>--color</option> and "
"<option>--colorfg</option> are ignored with this option."
msgstr ""
"Navedite ukaz lupine, ki se izvede. Če je ta možnost določena, mora biti "
"zadnja možnost &kalarm; v ukazni vrstici programa &kalarm;. Vsi naslednji "
"parametri in možnosti ukaza se interpretirajo, kot da tvorijo ukazno vrstico "
"za izvedbo. <option>--file</option> in <option>--exec-display</option> ter "
"<option>--mail</option> ni mogoče določiti s to možnostjo. <option>--ack-"
"confirm</option>, <option>--beep</option>, <option>--color</option> in "
"<option>--colorfg</option> se pri tej možnosti ne upoštevajo."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3432
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<option>-E</option>, <option>--exec-display <replaceable>commandline</"
"replaceable></option>"
msgstr ""
"<option>-E</option>, <option>--exec-display <replaceable>commandline</"
"replaceable></option>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3433
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specify a shell command to execute to generate the alarm message text. If "
"specified, this option must be the last &kalarm; option in &kalarm;'s "
"command line. All subsequent command parameters and options are interpreted "
"as forming the command line to execute. <option>--exec</option>, <option>--"
"file</option> and <option>--mail</option> cannot be specified with this "
"option."
msgstr ""
"Navedite ukaz lupine, ki se izvede za ustvarjanje besedila alarmnega "
"sporočila. Če je ta možnost določena, mora biti zadnja možnost &kalarm; v "
"ukazni vrstici programa &kalarm;. Vsi naslednji parametri in možnosti ukaza "
"se interpretirajo kot ukazna vrstica za izvedbo. <option>--exec</option>, "
"<option>--file</option> in <option>--mail</option> ni mogoče določiti s to "
"možnostjo."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3441
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<option>-f</option>, <option>--file <replaceable>URL</replaceable></option>"
msgstr ""
"<option>-f</option>, <option>--file <replaceable>URL</replaceable></option>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3442
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specify the path or &URL; of a text or image file whose contents are to form "
"the alarm message. <option>--exec</option>, <option>--exec-display</option> "
"and <option>--mail</option> cannot be specified, and <replaceable>message</"
"replaceable> must not be present with this option."
msgstr ""
"Navedite pot ali &URL; besedilne ali slikovne datoteke, katere vsebina bo "
"tvorila alarmno sporočilo. <option>--exec</option>, <option>--exec-display</"
"option> in <option>--mail</option> ni mogoče navesti, možnost "
"<replaceable>sporočilo</replaceable> pa ne sme biti prisotna s to možnostjo."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3449
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<option>-F</option>, <option>--from-id <replaceable>ID</replaceable></option>"
msgstr ""
"<option>-F</option>, <option>--from-id <replaceable>ID</replaceable></option>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3451
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the specified &kmail; identity as the sender of the email. <option>--"
"mail</option> must be specified with this option."
msgstr ""
"Kot pošiljatelja e-pošte uporabite določeno identiteto &kmail;. <option>--"
"mail</option> mora biti določena s to možnostjo."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3456
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<option>-i</option>, <option>--interval <replaceable>period</replaceable></"
"option>"
msgstr ""
"<option>-i</option>, <option>--interval <replaceable>period</replaceable></"
"option>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3458
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the interval between repetitions of the alarm. Hours/minutes are "
"specified in the format <replaceable>nHnM</replaceable>, where "
"<replaceable>n</replaceable> is a number, &eg; 3H30M. Other time periods are "
"specified in the format <replaceable>nX</replaceable>, where <replaceable>n</"
"replaceable> is a number and <replaceable>X</replaceable> is one of the "
"following letters: Y (years), M (months), W (weeks), D (days). If <option>--"
"recurrence</option> is also specified, Y (years) and M (months) are not "
"allowed. Mandatory if <option>--repeat</option> or <option>--until</option> "
"is specified."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite interval med ponovitvami alarma. Ure/minute so navedene v obliki "
"<replaceable>nHnM</replaceable>, kjer je <replaceable>n</replaceable> "
"številka, npr. 3H30M. Druga časovna obdobja so navedena v obliki "
"<replaceable>nX</replaceable>, kjer je <replaceable>n</replaceable> "
"številka, <replaceable>X</replaceable> pa ena od naslednjih črk: L (leta), M "
"(meseci), T (tedni), D (dnevi). Če je navedena tudi možnost <option>--"
"recurrence</option>, L (leta) in M (meseci) nista dovoljena. Obvezno, če je "
"določena možnost <option>--repeat</option> ali <option>--until</option>."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3472
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>-k</option>, <option>--korganizer</option>"
msgstr "<option>-k</option>, <option>--korganizer</option>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3473
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show the alarm as an event in &korganizer;'s active calendar."
msgstr "Prikažite alarm kot dogodek v aktivnem koledarju naprave &korganizer;."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3477
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<option>-l</option>, <option>--late-cancel <replaceable>period</"
"replaceable></option>"
msgstr ""
"<option>-l</option>, <option>--late-cancel <replaceable>period</"
"replaceable></option>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3479
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Cancel the alarm if it cannot be triggered within the specified "
"<replaceable>period</replaceable> after the correct time. Hours/minutes are "
"specified in the format <replaceable>nHnM</replaceable>, where "
"<replaceable>n</replaceable> is a number, &eg; 3H30M. Other time periods are "
"specified in the format <replaceable>nX</replaceable>, where <replaceable>n</"
"replaceable> is a number and <replaceable>X</replaceable> is one of the "
"following letters: W (weeks), D (days). The default value of "
"<replaceable>period</replaceable> is 1 minute."
msgstr ""
"Prekličite alarm, če ga ni mogoče sprožiti v določenem <replaceable>obdobju</"
"replaceable> po pravem času. Ure/minute so navedene v obliki "
"<replaceable>nHnM</replaceable>, kjer je <replaceable>n</replaceable> "
"številka, npr. 3H30M. Druga časovna obdobja so navedena v obliki "
"<replaceable>nX</replaceable>, kjer je <replaceable>n</replaceable> "
"številka, <replaceable>X</replaceable> pa ena od naslednjih črk: T (tedni), "
"D (dnevi). Privzeta vrednost <replaceable>obdobje</replaceable> je 1 minuta."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3492
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>-L</option>, <option>--login</option>"
msgstr "<option>-L</option>, <option>--login</option>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3493
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Trigger the alarm every time you log in. <option>--interval</option>, "
"<option>--repeat</option> and <option>--until</option> cannot be specified "
"with this option."
msgstr ""
"Alarm se sproži ob vsaki prijavi. <option>--interval</option>, <option>--"
"repeat</option> in <option>--until</option> s to možnostjo ni mogoče "
"določiti."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3499
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<option>-m</option>, <option>--mail <replaceable>address</replaceable></"
"option>"
msgstr ""
"<option>-m</option>, <option>--mail <replaceable>address</replaceable></"
"option>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3501
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Send an email to the specified address. This option may be repeated as "
"necessary. <option>--exec</option>, <option>--exec-display</option> and "
"<option>--file</option> cannot be specified with this option. <option>--ack-"
"confirm</option>, <option>--beep</option>, <option>--color</option> and "
"<option>--colorfg</option> are ignored with this option."
msgstr ""
"Pošljite e-poštno sporočilo na določen naslov. Ta možnost se lahko po "
"potrebi ponovi. <option>--exec</option>, <option>--exec-display</option> in "
"<option>--file</option> s to možnostjo ni mogoče določiti. <option>--ack-"
"confirm</option>, <option>--beep</option>, <option>--color</option> in "
"<option>--colorfg</option> se s to možnostjo ne upoštevajo."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3510
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<option>-n</option>, <option>--name <replaceable>name</replaceable></option>"
msgstr ""
"<option>-n</option>, <option>--name <replaceable>name</replaceable></option>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3511
#, no-c-format
msgid "Specify a name to help you to identify the alarm."
msgstr "Določite ime, ki vam bo pomagalo prepoznati alarm."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3514
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>-N</option>, <option>--notify</option>"
msgstr "<option>-N</option>, <option>--notify</option>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3515
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Display the alarm as a notification, not in a window. <option>--color</"
"option>, <option>--colorfg</option>, <option>--play</option>, <option>--ack-"
"confirm</option> and <option>--auto-close</option> cannot be specified with "
"this option."
msgstr ""
"Alarm se prikaže kot obvestilo in ne v oknu. <option>--color</option>, "
"<option>--colorfg</option>, <option>--play</option>, <option>--ack-confirm</"
"option> in <option>--auto-close</option> s to možnostjo ni mogoče določiti."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3522
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<option>-p</option>, <option>--play <replaceable>URL</replaceable></option>"
msgstr ""
"<option>-p</option>, <option>--play <replaceable>URL</replaceable></option>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3523
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specify the path or &URL; of an audio file to be played once, either as an "
"audio alarm or when the alarm message is displayed. <option>--play-repeat</"
"option>, <option>--beep</option> and <option>--speak</option> cannot be "
"specified with this option."
msgstr ""
"Določite pot ali &URL; do zvočne datoteke, ki se enkrat predvaja kot zvočni "
"alarm ali ob prikazu alarmnega sporočila. <option>--play-repeat</option>, "
"<option>--beep</option> in <option>--speak</option> ni mogoče določiti s to "
"možnostjo."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3530
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<option>-P</option>, <option>--play-repeat <replaceable>URL</replaceable></"
"option>"
msgstr ""
"<option>-P</option>, <option>--play-repeat <replaceable>URL</replaceable></"
"option>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3531
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specify the path or &URL; of an audio file to be played repeatedly, either "
"until <guilabel>Stop Play</guilabel> is used, or for as long as the alarm "
"message is displayed. <option>--play</option>, <option>--beep</option> and "
"<option>--speak</option> cannot be specified with this option."
msgstr ""
"Navedite pot ali &URL; do zvočne datoteke, ki se bo večkrat predvajala, "
"dokler ne uporabite <guilabel>Ustavi predvajanje</guilabel> ali dokler je "
"prikazano alarmno sporočilo. <option>--play</option>, <option>--beep</"
"option> in <option>--speak</option> ni mogoče določiti s to možnostjo."

#. Tag: option
#: index.docbook:3539
#, no-c-format
msgid "--recurrence <replaceable>spec</replaceable>"
msgstr "--recurrence <replaceable>spec</replaceable>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3541
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the alarm to recur. Specify the recurrence using iCalendar syntax "
"(defined in <ulink url=\"http://www.w3.org/2002/12/cal/rfc2445.html"
"\">RFC2445</ulink>), &eg; <quote>FREQ=MONTHLY;COUNT=4;INTERVAL=3;BYDAY=-1MO</"
"quote>. <option>--until</option> cannot be specified with this option."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite alarm na ponavljanje. Navedite ponavljanje s sintakso iCalendar "
"(opredeljeno v <ulink url=\"http://www.w3.org/2002/12/cal/rfc2445.html"
"\">RFC2445</ulink>), &eg; <quote>FREQ=MONTHLY;COUNT=4;INTERVAL=3;BYDAY=-1MO</"
"quote>. <option>--until</option> s to možnostjo ni mogoče določiti."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3549
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<option>-r</option>, <option>--repeat <replaceable>count</replaceable></"
"option>"
msgstr ""
"<option>-r</option>, <option>--repeat <replaceable>count</replaceable></"
"option>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3551
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the number of times the alarm should be triggered, or if a recurrence is "
"specified with <option>--recurrence</option>, the number of times the alarm "
"should be triggered each time <option>--recurrence</option> activates it "
"(&ie; a repetition within a recurrence). If <option>--recurrence</option> is "
"not present, specify -1 to repeat the alarm indefinitely. <option>--"
"interval</option> must be, and <option>--until</option> cannot be, specified "
"with this option."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite število ponovitev sprožitve alarma ali, če je z možnostjo "
"<option>--recurrence</option> določeno ponavljanje, število ponovitev "
"sprožitve alarma vsakič, ko ga aktivira <option>--recurrence</option> (&ie; "
"ponovitev znotraj ponavljanja). Če možnosti <option>--recurrence</option> "
"ni, določite -1, da se alarm ponavlja za nedoločen čas. <option>--interval</"
"option> mora biti, <option>--until</option> pa ne more biti določen s to "
"možnostjo."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3561
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<option>-R</option>, <option>--reminder <replaceable>period</replaceable></"
"option>"
msgstr ""
"<option>-R</option>, <option>--reminder <replaceable>period</replaceable></"
"option>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3563
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Output a reminder alarm the specified length of time before or after the "
"main alarm and each of its recurrences (if any). The <replaceable>period</"
"replaceable> is specified in the same format as described for <option>--late-"
"cancel</option>. By default, the reminder will occur before the alarm. To "
"specify a reminder after the alarm, prefix <replaceable>period</replaceable> "
"with <replaceable>+</replaceable>, &eg; +3D. This option cannot be specified "
"with <option>--exec</option>, <option>--mail</option> or <option>--reminder-"
"once</option>."
msgstr ""
"Izpiše opozorilni alarm v določenem časovnem obdobju pred ali po glavnem "
"alarmu in vsakem od njegovih ponovitev (če obstajajo). <replaceable>obdobje</"
"replaceable> je določeno v enaki obliki, kot je opisano za <option>--late-"
"cancel</option>. Privzeto se opomnik prikaže pred alarmom. Če želite "
"določiti opomnik po alarmu, uporabite predpono <replaceable>obdobje</"
"replaceable> z <replaceable>+</replaceable>, &eg; +3D. Te možnosti ni mogoče "
"določiti z možnostmi <option>--exec</option>, <option>--mail</option> ali "
"<option>--reminder-once</option>."

#. Tag: option
#: index.docbook:3574
#, no-c-format
msgid "--reminder-once <replaceable>period</replaceable>"
msgstr "--reminder-once <replaceable>period</replaceable>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3576
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Output a reminder alarm once, the specified length of time before or after "
"the first recurrence of the alarm. No reminder will be displayed before or "
"after subsequent recurrences (if any). The <replaceable>period</replaceable> "
"is specified in the same format as described for <option>--reminder</"
"option>. This option cannot be specified with <option>--exec</option>, "
"<option>--mail</option> or <option>--reminder</option>."
msgstr ""
"Enkrat sproži alarm za opomnik v določenem časovnem obdobju pred ali po prvi "
"ponovitvi alarma. Pred naslednjimi ponovitvami (če obstajajo) ali po njih se "
"ne prikaže noben opomnik. <replaceable>obdobje</replaceable> je določeno v "
"enaki obliki, kot je opisana za <option>--option>-reminder</option>. Te "
"možnosti ni mogoče določiti z možnostmi <option>--exec</option>, <option>--"
"mail</option> ali <option>--reminder</option>."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3585
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>-s</option>, <option>--speak</option>"
msgstr "<option>-s</option>, <option>--speak</option>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3586
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Speak the message when it is displayed. This option requires &kalarm; to "
"have been built with speech enabled and the &Qt; Speech module to be "
"installed and working. <option>--beep</option>, <option>--play</option> and "
"<option>--play-repeat</option> cannot be specified with this option."
msgstr ""
"Izgovori sporočilo, ko se prikaže. Ta možnost zahteva, da je bil program "
"&kalarm; zgrajen z omogočenim govorom in da je modul &Qt; Speech nameščen in "
"deluje. <option>--beep</option>, <option>--play</option> in <option>--play-"
"repeat</option> ni mogoče določiti s to možnostjo."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3593
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<option>-S</option>, <option>--subject <replaceable>subject</replaceable></"
"option>"
msgstr ""
"<option>-S</option>, <option>--subject <replaceable>zadeva</replaceable></"
"option>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3595
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The subject line of the email. <option>--mail</option> must be specified "
"with this option."
msgstr ""
"Vsebinska vrstica e-pošte. <option>--mail</option> mora biti določena s to "
"možnostjo."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3600
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<option>-t</option>, <option>--time <replaceable>date/time</replaceable></"
"option>"
msgstr ""
"<option>-t</option>, <option>--time <replaceable>date/time</replaceable></"
"option>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3602
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Trigger alarm on the date or at the date/time specified. Specify a date "
"without a time in the format <replaceable>yyyy-mm-dd[ TZ]</replaceable>; "
"specify a date and time by <replaceable>[[[yyyy-]mm-]dd-]hh:mm[ TZ]</"
"replaceable> (where omitted, date fields default to the values for today). "
"If no time zone is specified, the local system time zone is assumed. If a "
"time zone specifier <replaceable>TZ</replaceable> is present, it may be the "
"name of a system time zone (&eg; <userinput>Europe/London</userinput>), or "
"<userinput>UTC</userinput> representing the UTC time zone."
msgstr ""
"Sprožite alarm na določen datum ali ob določenem datumu/času. Navedite datum "
"brez časa v obliki <replaceable>llll-mm-dd[ TZ]</replaceable>; navedite "
"datum in čas z <replaceable>[[[llll-]mm-]dd-]hh:mm[ TZ]</replaceable> (če je "
"izpuščen, so v datumskih poljih privzete vrednosti za danes). Če časovni pas "
"ni določen, se predpostavlja lokalni sistemski časovni pas. Če je prisoten "
"določevalec časovnega pasu <replaceable>TZ</replaceable>, je to lahko ime "
"sistemskega časovnega pasu (&eg; <userinput>Evropa/London</userinput>) ali "
"<userinput>UTC</userinput>, ki predstavlja časovni pas UTC."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3614
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<option>-v</option>, <option>--volume <replaceable>percentage</replaceable></"
"option>"
msgstr ""
"<option>-v</option>, <option>--volume <replaceable>percentage</replaceable></"
"option>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3616
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the audio volume for playing the audio file. This option can only be "
"used when <option>--play</option> or <option>--play-repeat</option> is "
"specified."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite glasnost zvoka za predvajanje zvočne datoteke. To možnost lahko "
"uporabite le, če je določena možnost <option>--play</option> ali <option>--"
"play-repeat</option>."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3621
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<option>-u</option>, <option>--until <replaceable>date/time</replaceable></"
"option>"
msgstr ""
"<option>-u</option>, <option>--until <replaceable>date/time</replaceable></"
"option>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3623
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Repeat the alarm until the date or date/time specified. Specify the date or "
"date/time using the same syntax as for <option>--time</option>. Note that if "
"<option>--time</option> is specified, the time zone will be taken from its "
"value and no time zone may be included in the <option>--until</option> "
"value. <option>--interval</option> must be, and <option>--repeat</option> "
"and <option>--recurrence</option> cannot be, specified with this option."
msgstr ""
"Ponavlja alarm do določenega datuma ali datuma/časa. Določite datum ali "
"datum/čas z isto sintakso kot za <option>--time</option>. Upoštevajte, da če "
"je podan <option>--time</option>, bo časovni pas vzet iz njegove vrednosti "
"in noben časovni pas ne sme biti vključen v vrednost <option>--until</"
"option>. <option>--interval</option> mora biti, in <option>--repeat</option> "
"in <option>--recurrence</option> ni mogoče določiti s to možnostjo."

#. Tag: replaceable
#: index.docbook:3633
#, no-c-format
msgid "<replaceable>message</replaceable>"
msgstr "<replaceable>sporočilo</replaceable>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3634
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Message text to display or, if <option>--mail</option> is specified, the "
"body of the email message."
msgstr ""
"Besedilo sporočila za prikaz ali, če je podana <option>--mail</option>, telo "
"e-poštnega sporočila."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3641
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Either a message text, <option>--file</option>, <option>--exec</option>, "
"<option>--exec-display</option>, <option>--play</option> or <option>--play-"
"repeat</option> must be specified; except as noted above, all the options "
"are optional."
msgstr ""
"Bodisi besedilo sporočila, <option>--file</option>, <option>--exec</option>, "
"<option>--exec-display</option>, <option>--play</option> ali <option>--play-"
"repeat</option> je treba določiti; razen kot je navedeno zgoraj, so vse "
"možnosti neobvezne."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3646
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Two alternative examples which display a multi-line message with a red "
"background at 10 p.m. on the 27th of this month are:"
msgstr ""
"Dva alternativna primera, ki prikazujeta večvrstično sporočilo z rdečim "
"ozadjem ob 22. uri. 27. tega meseca so:"

#. Tag: screen
#: index.docbook:3649
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<prompt>%</prompt> <userinput><command>kalarm</command> <option>-c "
"<replaceable>red</replaceable></option> <option>-t <replaceable>27-22:00</"
"replaceable></option> <option><replaceable>\"Remember to\\nSTOP\"</"
"replaceable></option></userinput>\n"
"<prompt>%</prompt> <userinput><command>kalarm</command> <option>-c "
"<replaceable>0xFF0000</replaceable></option> <option>-t "
"<replaceable>27-22:00</replaceable></option> <option><replaceable>\"Remember "
"to\\nSTOP\"</replaceable></option></userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<prompt>%</prompt> <userinput><command>kalarm</command> <option>-c "
"<replaceable>red</replaceable></option> <option>-t <replaceable>27-22:00</"
"replaceable></option> <option><replaceable>\"Spomni se \\nUSTAVITI\"</"
"replaceable></option></userinput>\n"
"<prompt>%</prompt> <userinput><command>kalarm</command> <option>-c "
"<replaceable>0xFF0000</replaceable></option> <option>-t "
"<replaceable>27-22:00</replaceable></option> <option><replaceable>\"Spomni "
"se \\nUSTAVITI\"</replaceable></option></userinput>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3655
#, no-c-format
msgid "Other Options"
msgstr "Druge možnosti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3657
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The following options are used to perform various functions, including "
"displaying the <link linkend=\"alarm-edit-dlg\">Alarm Edit dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"Naslednje možnosti se uporabljajo za izvajanje različnih funkcij, vključno s "
"prikazom <link linkend=\"alarm-edit-dlg\">pogovornega okna za urejanje "
"alarma</link>."

#. Tag: option
#: index.docbook:3671
#, no-c-format
msgid "--edit <replaceable>eventID</replaceable>"
msgstr "--edit <replaceable>dogodekID</replaceable>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3672
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Display the Alarm Edit dialog to edit the alarm with the specified event ID. "
"The event ID is the unique ID of the event, optionally prefixed by the "
"configuration name or numeric ID of the resource containing the event, in "
"the format <replaceable>[resourceID:]eventUID</replaceable>."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže pogovorno okno za urejanje alarma, da uredite alarm z navedenim ID-"
"jem dogodka. ID dogodka je enoličen ID dogodka, ki mu je neobvezno predpona "
"ime konfiguracije ali številčni ID vira, ki vsebuje dogodek, v obliki "
"<replaceable>[resourceID:]eventUID</replaceable>."

#. Tag: option
#: index.docbook:3679
#, no-c-format
msgid "--edit-new-audio"
msgstr "--edit-new-audio"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3680
#, no-c-format
msgid "Display the Alarm Edit dialog, in order to edit a new audio alarm."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže pogovorno okno za urejanje alarma, da uredite nov zvočni alarm."

#. Tag: option
#: index.docbook:3684
#, no-c-format
msgid "--edit-new-command"
msgstr "--edit-new-command"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3685
#, no-c-format
msgid "Display the Alarm Edit dialog, in order to edit a new command alarm."
msgstr "Prikaže pogovorno okno Urejanje alarma, da uredite nov ukazni alarm."

#. Tag: option
#: index.docbook:3689
#, no-c-format
msgid "--edit-new-display"
msgstr "--edit-new-display"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3690
#, no-c-format
msgid "Display the Alarm Edit dialog, in order to edit a new display alarm."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže pogovorno okno za urejanje alarma, če želite urediti nov prikaz "
"alarma."

#. Tag: option
#: index.docbook:3694
#, no-c-format
msgid "--edit-new-email"
msgstr "--edit-new-email"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3695
#, no-c-format
msgid "Display the Alarm Edit dialog, in order to edit a new email alarm."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže pogovorno okno za urejanje alarma, da uredite nov e-poštni alarm."

#. Tag: option
#: index.docbook:3699
#, no-c-format
msgid "--edit-new-preset <replaceable>templateName</replaceable>"
msgstr "--edit-new-preset <replaceable>imePredloge</replaceable>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3700
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Display the Alarm Edit dialog, preset with the alarm template of the "
"specified name, in order to edit a new alarm."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže pogovorno okno za urejanje alarma, prednastavljeno s predlogo alarma "
"z določenim namenom, da uredite nov alarm."

#. Tag: option
#: index.docbook:3704
#, no-c-format
msgid "--list"
msgstr "--list"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3705
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Output a list of scheduled alarms to <filename>stdout</filename>. The list "
"shows brief details of each pending alarm: its resource identifier, UID, "
"next scheduled time and message text or file."
msgstr ""
"Oddaj seznam načrtovanih alarmov v <filename>stdout</filename>. Seznam "
"prikazuje kratke podrobnosti vsakega čakajočega alarma: njegov identifikator "
"vira, UID, naslednji načrtovani čas in besedilo ali datoteko sporočila."

#. Tag: option
#: index.docbook:3710
#, no-c-format
msgid "--tray"
msgstr "--list"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3711
#, no-c-format
msgid "Display &kalarm; as an icon in the system tray."
msgstr "Prikaže &kalarm; kot ikono v sistemski vrstici."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:3715
#, no-c-format
msgid "Disable monitoring of all alarms."
msgstr "Onemogoči spremljanje vseh alarmov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3721
#, no-c-format
msgid "See also:"
msgstr "Poglejte tudi:"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:3723
#, no-c-format
msgid "kf6options(7)"
msgstr "kf6options(7)"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:3724
#, no-c-format
msgid "qt6options(7)"
msgstr "qt6options(7)"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3732
#, no-c-format
msgid "Developer's Guide to &kalarm;"
msgstr "Vodnik za razvijalce za &kalarm;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3734
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kalarm; provides an interface to allow other applications to request the "
"following functions:"
msgstr ""
"&kalarm; nudi vmesnik, ki omogoča drugim aplikacijam, da zahtevajo naslednje "
"funkcije:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3739
#, no-c-format
msgid "cancel an already scheduled alarm"
msgstr "preklic že načrtovanega alarma"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3740
#, no-c-format
msgid "trigger an already scheduled alarm"
msgstr "sprožitev že načrtovanega alarma"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3741
#, no-c-format
msgid "display the Alarm Edit dialog"
msgstr "prikaz pogovornega okna za urejanje alarma"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3742
#, no-c-format
msgid "list scheduled alarms"
msgstr "naštetje načrtovanih alarmov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3745
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each of the above functions is implemented both by a &DBus; call and by the "
"command line. &DBus; calls should be used in preference if &kalarm; is "
"already running."
msgstr ""
"Vsaka od zgornjih funkcij je implementirana z &DBus; klic in z ukazno "
"vrstico. &DBus; klice je treba uporabiti prednostno, če &kalarm; že teče."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3750
#, no-c-format
msgid "&DBus; Interface"
msgstr "&DBus; Vmesnik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3752
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &DBus; calls described in this document are all implemented in "
"&kalarm;'s <constant>/kalarm</constant> &DBus; object path. The interface is "
"defined in the files <filename>org.kde.kalarm.kalarm.xml</filename> and "
"<filename>kalarmiface.h</filename>."
msgstr ""
"Vsi klici &DBus;, opisani v tem dokumentu, se izvajajo v &kalarm; <constant>/"
"kalarm</constant> &DBus; objektni poti. Vmesnik je opredeljen v datotekah "
"<filename>org.kde.kalarm.kalarm.xml</filename> in <filename>kalarmiface.h</"
"filename>."

#. Tag: refentrytitle
#: index.docbook:3760
#, no-c-format
msgid "<refentrytitle>cancelEvent</refentrytitle>"
msgstr "<refentrytitle>cancelEvent</refentrytitle>"

#. Tag: refname
#: index.docbook:3763
#, no-c-format
msgid "<refname>cancelEvent</refname>"
msgstr "<refname>cancelEvent</refname>"

#. Tag: refpurpose
#: index.docbook:3764
#, no-c-format
msgid "cancel an already scheduled alarm."
msgstr "preklic že načrtovanega alarma."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: index.docbook:3767
#, no-c-format
msgid "void cancelEvent(const QString&amp; <replaceable>eventID</replaceable>)"
msgstr "void cancelEvent(const QString"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3770 index.docbook:3807 index.docbook:3853 index.docbook:4081
#: index.docbook:4279 index.docbook:4444 index.docbook:4640 index.docbook:4808
#: index.docbook:4854
#, no-c-format
msgid "Parameters"
msgstr "Parametri"

#. Tag: parameter
#: index.docbook:3773 index.docbook:3810 index.docbook:4811
#, no-c-format
msgid "eventID"
msgstr "dogodekID"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3775
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specifies the unique ID of the event to be canceled, optionally prefixed by "
"the configuration name or numeric ID of the resource containing the event, "
"in the format <replaceable>[resourceID:]eventUID</replaceable>."
msgstr ""
"Določa edinstven ID dogodka, ki ga je treba preklicati, po želji s predpono "
"namena konfiguracije ali številčnega ID vira, ki vsebuje dogodek, v obliki "
"<replaceable>[resourceID:]eventUID</replaceable>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3786 index.docbook:3823 index.docbook:4047 index.docbook:4253
#: index.docbook:4418 index.docbook:4613 index.docbook:4785 index.docbook:4831
#: index.docbook:4886 index.docbook:4916
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Description</title>"
msgstr "<title>Opis</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3788
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<function>cancelEvent()</function> is a &DBus; call to cancel the specified "
"alarm. &kalarm; deletes the alarm from the calendar without displaying or "
"executing it."
msgstr ""
"<function>cancelEvent()</function> je klic &DBus; za preklic določenega "
"alarma. &kalarm; izbriše alarm iz koledarja, ne da bi ga prikazal ali "
"izvedel."

#. Tag: refentrytitle
#: index.docbook:3797
#, no-c-format
msgid "<refentrytitle>triggerEvent</refentrytitle>"
msgstr "<refentrytitle>triggerEvent</refentrytitle>"

#. Tag: refname
#: index.docbook:3800
#, no-c-format
msgid "<refname>triggerEvent</refname>"
msgstr "<refname>triggerEvent</refname>"

#. Tag: refpurpose
#: index.docbook:3801
#, no-c-format
msgid "trigger an already scheduled alarm."
msgstr "sproži že načrtovani alarm."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: index.docbook:3804
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"void triggerEvent(const QString&amp; <replaceable>eventID</replaceable>)"
msgstr ""
"void sprožiDogodek(const QString&amp; <replaceable>dogodekID</replaceable>)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3812
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specifies the unique ID of the event to be triggered, optionally prefixed by "
"the configuration name or numeric ID of the resource containing the event, "
"in the format <replaceable>[resourceID:]eventUID</replaceable>."
msgstr ""
"Določa edinstven ID dogodka, ki se sproži, po želji s predpono namena "
"konfiguracije ali številčnega ID vira, ki vsebuje dogodek, v obliki "
"<replaceable>[resourceID:]eventUID</replaceable>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3825
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<function>triggerEvent()</function> is a &DBus; call to trigger the "
"immediate display or execution of the specified alarm (regardless of what "
"time it is scheduled for). &kalarm; retrieves the alarm from the calendar "
"and then displays or executes it."
msgstr ""
"<function>sprožiDogodek()</function> je klic &DBus; za sprožitev takojšnjega "
"prikaza ali izvedbe določenega alarma (ne glede na to, za kateri čas je "
"načrtovan). &kalarm; pridobi alarm iz koledarja in ga nato prikaže ali "
"izvede."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3830
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the alarm is already due, &kalarm; then deletes all scheduled occurrences "
"of the alarm up to the current time, and if no repetitions of the alarm "
"still remain, the alarm is deleted from the calendar. If the alarm is not "
"due yet, its scheduled occurrences are left unchanged."
msgstr ""
"Če je alarm že zapadel, se s funkcijo &kalarm; izbrišejo vse načrtovane "
"ponovitve alarma do trenutnega časa, in če ni več ponovitev alarma, se alarm "
"izbriše iz koledarja. Če alarm še ni zapadel, se njegovi načrtovani dogodki "
"ne spremenijo."

#. Tag: refentrytitle
#: index.docbook:3841
#, no-c-format
msgid "<refentrytitle>scheduleMessage</refentrytitle>"
msgstr "<refentrytitle>scheduleMessage</refentrytitle>"

#. Tag: refname
#: index.docbook:3844
