#. Tag: parameter
#: index.docbook:3856 index.docbook:4084 index.docbook:4282 index.docbook:4447
#: index.docbook:4643
#, no-c-format
msgid "name"
msgstr "ime"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3858 index.docbook:4086 index.docbook:4284 index.docbook:4449
#: index.docbook:4645
#, no-c-format
msgid "Specifies an optional name for the alarm."
msgstr "Določa neobvezno ime za alarm."

#. Tag: parameter
#: index.docbook:3863 index.docbook:4478
#, no-c-format
msgid "<parameter>message</parameter>"
msgstr "<parameter>sporočilo</parameter>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3865
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specifies the text of the message to be scheduled, or if <parameter>flags</"
"parameter> has the <userinput>DISPLAY_COMMAND</userinput> bit set, specifies "
"the command line to execute to generate the message text."
msgstr ""
"Določa besedilo sporočila, ki ga je treba načrtovati, ali, če je pri "
"<parameter>zastavice</parameter> nastavljen bit <userinput>DISPLAY_COMMAND</"
"userinput>, določa ukazno vrstico, ki se izvede za ustvarjanje besedila "
"sporočila."

#. Tag: parameter
#: index.docbook:3873 index.docbook:4099 index.docbook:4298 index.docbook:4493
#: index.docbook:4665
#, no-c-format
msgid "startDateTime"
msgstr "začetekDatumČas"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3875 index.docbook:4101 index.docbook:4300 index.docbook:4495
#: index.docbook:4667
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specifies the scheduled date, or date and time, at which the message should "
"be displayed. For a date-only alarm, the string should be in the format "
"<replaceable>YYYY-MM-DD[ TZ]</replaceable> (as returned by "
"<methodname>QDate::toString(Qt::ISODate)</methodname>). For an alarm with a "
"date and time, the string should be in the format <replaceable>YYYY-MM-DDTHH:"
"MM[:SS][ TZ]</replaceable> (as returned by <methodname>QDateTime::"
"toString(Qt::ISODate)</methodname>) or <replaceable>HH:MM[:SS]</replaceable> "
"(as returned by <methodname>QTime::toString(Qt::ISODate)</methodname>). If "
"no date is specified, today's date is used. Note that any seconds value is "
"ignored."
msgstr ""
"Določa načrtovani datum ali datum in čas, ko naj se sporočilo prikaže. Za "
"alarm samo z datumom mora biti niz v obliki <replaceable>RRRR-MM-DD[ TZ]</"
"replaceable> (kot ga vrne <methodname>QDate::toString(Qt::ISODate)</"
"methodname>). Za alarm z datumom in časom mora biti niz v obliki "
"<replaceable>LLLL-MM-DDTHH:MM[:SS][ TZ]</replaceable> (kot ga vrne "
"<methodname>QDateTname::toString(Qt::ISODate)</methodname>) ali "
"<replaceable>HH:MM[:SS]</replaceable> (kot ga vrne <methodname>QTname::"
"toString(Qt::ISODate)</methodname>). Če datum ni naveden, se uporabi "
"današnji datum. Upoštevajte, da se vse vrednosti sekund ne upoštevajo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3887 index.docbook:4113 index.docbook:4312 index.docbook:4507
#: index.docbook:4679
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If no time zone is specified, the local system time zone is assumed. If a "
"time zone specifier <replaceable>TZ</replaceable> is present, it may be the "
"name of a system time zone (&eg; <userinput>Europe/London</userinput>), or "
"<userinput>UTC</userinput> representing the UTC time zone."
msgstr ""
"Če časovni pas ni določen, se predpostavlja lokalni sistemski časovni pas. "
"Če je prisoten določevalec časovnega pasu <replaceable>TZ</replaceable>, je "
"to lahko ime sistemskega časovnega pasu (&eg; <userinput>Evropa/London</"
"userinput>) ali <userinput>UTC</userinput>, ki predstavlja časovni pas UTC."

#. Tag: parameter
#: index.docbook:3896 index.docbook:4122 index.docbook:4321 index.docbook:4516
#: index.docbook:4688
#, no-c-format
msgid "lateCancel"
msgstr "pozenZaključek"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3898 index.docbook:4124 index.docbook:4323 index.docbook:4518
#: index.docbook:4690
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Causes the alarm to be canceled if it cannot be triggered within the "
"specified number of minutes after the alarm's scheduled time. If the value "
"is 0, the alarm will not be canceled no matter how late it is triggered."
msgstr ""
"Povzroči preklic alarma, če ga ni mogoče sprožiti v določenem številu minut "
"po načrtovanem času alarma. Če je vrednost 0, alarm ne bo preklican ne glede "
"na to, kako pozno je bil sprožen."

#. Tag: parameter
#: index.docbook:3906 index.docbook:4132 index.docbook:4331 index.docbook:4526
#: index.docbook:4698
#, no-c-format
msgid "flags"
msgstr "zastavice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3908
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specifies the logical OR of the desired alarm flags. The flag bits are those "
"defined in class <classname>KAlarmIface</classname> in <filename>kalarmiface."
"h</filename>. Note that not all flag bits are applicable to message alarms."
msgstr ""
"Določa logično ALI želenih alarmnih zastavic. Biti zastavic so tisti, ki so "
"opredeljeni v razredu <classname>KAlarmIface</classname> v "
"<filename>kalarmiface.h</filename>. Upoštevajte, da se vsi biti zastavic ne "
"uporabljajo za alarmna sporočila."

#. Tag: parameter
#: index.docbook:3916 index.docbook:4142
#, no-c-format
msgid "bgColor"
msgstr "bgBarva"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3918
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specifies the background color for displaying the message. The string may be "
"in the format <quote>#RRGGBB</quote> (as returned by <methodname>QColor::"
"name()</methodname>) where RR, GG and BB are two-digit hexadecimal values "
"for red, green and blue. Alternatively the string may be in any of the other "
"formats accepted by <methodname>QColor::setNamedColor()</methodname>, such "
"as a name from the X color database (&eg; <quote>red</quote> or "
"<quote>steelblue</quote>). Set the string to null to specify the current "
"default background color."
msgstr ""
"Določa barvo ozadja za prikaz sporočila. Niz je lahko v obliki "
"<quote>#RRGGBB</quote> (kot ga vrne <methodname>QColor::name()</"
"methodname>), kjer so RR, GG in BB dvomestne šestnajstmestne vrednosti za "
"rdečo, zeleno in modro. Alternativno je lahko niz v kateri koli drugi "
"obliki, ki jo sprejme <methodname>QColor::setNamedColor()</methodname>, na "
"primer name iz baze barv X (&eg; <quote>rdeča</quote> ali <quote>modra</"
"quote>). Nastavite niz na nič, da določite trenutno privzeto barvo ozadja."

#. Tag: parameter
#: index.docbook:3931
#, no-c-format
msgid "fgColor"
msgstr "fgBarva"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3933
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specifies the foreground color for displaying the message. The format of the "
"string is the same as for <parameter>bgColor</parameter>, or alternatively "
"set the string to null to specify the current default foreground color."
msgstr ""
"Določa barvo ospredja za prikaz sporočila. Oblika niza je enaka kot za "
"<parameter>bgBarva</parameter>, lahko pa niz nastavite na nič, da določite "
"trenutno privzeto barvo ospredja."

#. Tag: parameter
#: index.docbook:3941
#, no-c-format
msgid "font"
msgstr "pisava"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3943
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specifies the font for displaying the message. The format of the string is "
"that output by <methodname>QFont::toString()</methodname>. Set the string to "
"null to use the default message font current at the time the message is "
"displayed."
msgstr ""
"Določa pisavo za prikaz sporočila. Oblika niza je takšna, kot jo izpiše "
"<methodname>QFont::toString()</methodname>. Niz nastavite na nič, če želite "
"uporabiti privzeto pisavo sporočila, ki je aktualna v času, ko je sporočilo "
"prikazano."

#. Tag: parameter
#: index.docbook:3951 index.docbook:4157 index.docbook:4650
#, no-c-format
msgid "audioURL"
msgstr "zvočniURL"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3953 index.docbook:4159
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specifies the audio file which is to be played when the message is "
"displayed. Set the value to null if no audio file is to be played."
msgstr ""
"Določa zvočno datoteko, ki se bo predvajala ob prikazu sporočila. Vrednost "
"nastavite na nič, če ne želite predvajati nobene zvočne datoteke."

#. Tag: parameter
#: index.docbook:3960 index.docbook:4166
#, no-c-format
msgid "reminderMins"
msgstr "opomnikMins"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3962 index.docbook:4168
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specifies the number of minutes in advance of the main alarm and of each of "
"its recurrences (if any) at which a reminder alarm should be displayed. "
"Specify a negative value for a reminder to be displayed after the main "
"alarm. Specify 0 if no reminder is required."
msgstr ""
"Določa število minut pred glavnim alarmom in vsako njegovo ponovitvijo (če "
"obstaja), ko naj se prikaže opozorilni alarm. Določite negativno vrednost za "
"opomnik, ki se prikaže po glavnem alarmu. Navedite 0, če opomnik ni potreben."

#. Tag: parameter
#: index.docbook:3970 index.docbook:4176 index.docbook:4341 index.docbook:4536
#: index.docbook:4708
#, no-c-format
msgid "recurrence"
msgstr "ponovitev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3972 index.docbook:4178 index.docbook:4343 index.docbook:4538
#: index.docbook:4710
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specifies a regular recurrence for the alarm, using iCalendar syntax as "
"defined in <ulink url=\"http://www.w3.org/2002/12/cal/rfc2445.html"
"\">RFC2445</ulink>. For example, <quote>FREQ=MONTHLY;COUNT=4;INTERVAL=3;"
"BYDAY=-1MO</quote> would specify 4 repetitions at 3-monthly intervals on the "
"last Monday of the month. For a non-recurring alarm, specify an empty string."
msgstr ""
"Določa redno ponavljanje za alarm z uporabo sintakse iCalendar, kot je "
"opredeljena v <ulink url=\"http://www.w3.org/2002/12/cal/rfc2445.html"
"\">RFC2445</ulink>. Na primer, <quote>FREQ=MONTHLY;COUNT=4;INTERVAL=3;"
"BYDAY=-1MO</quote> bi določil 4 ponovitve v trnamesečnih intervalih na "
"zadnji ponedeljek v mesecu. Za alarm, ki se ne ponavlja, določite prazen niz."

#. Tag: parameter
#: index.docbook:3983 index.docbook:4189 index.docbook:4354 index.docbook:4549
#: index.docbook:4721
#, no-c-format
msgid "recurType"
msgstr "vrstaPonovitve"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3985 index.docbook:4191 index.docbook:4356 index.docbook:4551
#: index.docbook:4723
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specifies the recurrence type for the alarm. The permissible values are "
"MINUTELY, DAILY, WEEKLY, MONTHLY, YEARLY. These are defined in class "
"<classname>KAlarmIface</classname> in <filename>kalarmiface.h</filename>. "
"Monthly recurrences are of the day of the month type, and yearly recurrences "
"are of the date in the year type, with the date in both cases taken from the "
"<parameter>startDateTime</parameter> parameter."
msgstr ""
"Določa vrsto ponovitve za alarm. Dovoljene vrednosti so MINUTNO, DNEVNO, "
"TEDNSKO, MESEČNO, LETNO. Opredeljeni so v razredu <classname>KAlarmIface</"
"classname> v <filename>kalarmiface.h</filename>. Mesečna ponavljanja so tipa "
"dan v mesecu, letna ponavljanja pa tipa datum v letu, pri čemer je datum v "
"obeh primerih vzet iz parametra <parameter>startDateTname</parameter>."

#. Tag: parameter
#: index.docbook:3996 index.docbook:4202 index.docbook:4367 index.docbook:4562
#: index.docbook:4734
#, no-c-format
msgid "recurInterval"
msgstr "intervalPonovitve"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3998 index.docbook:4204 index.docbook:4369 index.docbook:4564
#: index.docbook:4736
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specifies the number of periods (minutes/days/weeks/months/years as "
"specified by <parameter>recurType</parameter>) between recurrences of the "
"alarm."
msgstr ""
"Določa število obdobij (minut/dni/teden/mesec/leto, kot je določeno s "
"parametrom <parameter>recurType</parameter>) med ponovitvami alarma."

#. Tag: parameter
#: index.docbook:4006 index.docbook:4212 index.docbook:4377 index.docbook:4572
#: index.docbook:4744
#, no-c-format
msgid "recurCount"
msgstr "številoPonovitev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4008 index.docbook:4214 index.docbook:4379 index.docbook:4574
#: index.docbook:4746
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specifies the number of times that the alarm should be repeated. Specify -1 "
"to repeat the alarm indefinitely."
msgstr ""
"Določa, kolikokrat naj se alarm ponovi. Če želite alarm ponavljati za "
"nedoločen čas, navedite -1."

#. Tag: parameter
#: index.docbook:4014 index.docbook:4220 index.docbook:4385 index.docbook:4580
#: index.docbook:4752
#, no-c-format
msgid "endDateTime"
msgstr "konecDatumČas"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4016 index.docbook:4222 index.docbook:4387 index.docbook:4582
#: index.docbook:4754
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specifies the end date, or date and time, for recurrences of the alarm. If "
"<parameter>startDateTime</parameter> includes a time, this parameter must "
"also include a time; if <parameter>startDateTime</parameter> contains only a "
"date, this parameter must also contain only a date. It must not contain a "
"time zone specifier; the same time zone as for <parameter>startDateTime</"
"parameter> is used to interpret this parameter's value."
msgstr ""
"Določa končni datum ali datum in uro za ponovitve alarma. Če "
"<parameter>startDateTname</parameter> vsebuje čas, mora tudi ta parameter "
"vsebovati čas; če <parameter>startDateTname</parameter> vsebuje samo datum, "
"mora tudi ta parameter vsebovati samo datum. Ne sme vsebovati označevalca "
"časovnega pasu; za interpretacijo vrednosti tega parametra se uporabi isti "
"časovni pas kot za <parameter>startDateTname</parameter>."

#. Tag: parameter
#: index.docbook:4027 index.docbook:4233 index.docbook:4398 index.docbook:4593
#: index.docbook:4765
#, no-c-format
msgid "subRepeatInterval"
msgstr "podIntervalPonovitve"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4029 index.docbook:4235 index.docbook:4400 index.docbook:4595
#: index.docbook:4767
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specifies the number of minutes between sub-repetitions of the alarm. "
"Specify 0 for no sub-repetition. Ignored if no recurrence is specified."
msgstr ""
"Določa število minut med posameznimi ponovitvami alarma. Navedite 0, če "
"želite, da ni ponovitev. Ne upošteva se, če ponovitev ni določena."

#. Tag: parameter
#: index.docbook:4036 index.docbook:4242 index.docbook:4407 index.docbook:4602
#: index.docbook:4774
#, no-c-format
msgid "subRepeatCount"
msgstr "podŠteviloPonovitev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4038 index.docbook:4244 index.docbook:4409 index.docbook:4604
#: index.docbook:4776
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specifies the number of sub-repetitions of the alarm, including the initial "
"occurrence."
msgstr "Določa število ponovitev alarma, vključno z začetnim pojavom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4048
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<function>scheduleMessage()</function> is a &DBus; call to schedule the "
"specified alarm message for display at the specified date and time. It has "
"three forms. The most general form allows an arbitrary recurrence to be "
"specified &ndash; use this also for non-repeating alarms. The other forms "
"provide convenient access to a restricted set of alarm recurrence types, one "
"specifying a repetition count and the other an end time."
msgstr ""
"<function>scheduleMessage()</function> je klic &DBus; za načrtovanje "
"prikazovanja določenega alarmnega sporočila ob določenem datumu in času. Ima "
"tri oblike. Najsplošnejša oblika omogoča določitev poljubnega ponavljanja; "
"uporabite jo tudi za alarme, ki se ne ponavljajo. Drugi obrazci omogočajo "
"priročen dostop do omejenega nabora vrst ponovitev alarma, pri čemer ena "
"določa število ponovitev, druga pa končni čas."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4056
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the scheduled time (including any repetitions) has already passed, "
"&kalarm; immediately displays the message (unless the <parameter>lateCancel</"
"parameter> value indicates that it is now too late to display the alarm, in "
"which case &kalarm; ignores the request). If the scheduled time (or a "
"repetition) is in the future, &kalarm; adds the alarm message to the default "
"active alarm calendar for later display."
msgstr ""
"Če je načrtovani čas (vključno z morebitnimi ponovitvami) že potekel, "
"&kalarm; takoj prikaže sporočilo (razen če vrednost <parameter>lateCancel</"
"parameter> kaže, da je za prikaz alarma že prepozno; v tem primeru &kalarm; "
"ignorira zahtevo). Če je načrtovani čas (ali ponovitev) v prihodnosti, "
"funkcija &kalarm; doda alarmno sporočilo v privzeti aktivni koledar alarmov "
"za poznejši prikaz."

#. Tag: refentrytitle
#: index.docbook:4068
#, no-c-format
msgid "<refentrytitle>scheduleFile</refentrytitle>"
msgstr "<refentrytitle>scheduleFile</refentrytitle>"

