"                  int <replaceable>opomnikMins</replaceable>,\n"
"                  const QString&amp; <replaceable>ponovitev</replaceable>,\n"
"                  int <replaceable>podIntervalPonovitve</replaceable>, \n"
"                  int <replaceable>podŠteviloPonovitev</replaceable>)"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: index.docbook:4077
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool scheduleFile(const QString&amp; <replaceable>name</replaceable>,\n"
"                  const QString&amp; <replaceable>URL</replaceable>,\n"
