"                  const QString&amp; <replaceable>URL</replaceable>,\n"
"                  const QString&amp; <replaceable>začetekDatumČas</"
"replaceable>,\n"
"                  int <replaceable>pozenZaključek</replaceable>,\n"
"                  unsigned <replaceable>zastavice</replaceable>,\n"
"                  const QString&amp; <replaceable>bgBarva</replaceable>,\n"
"                  const QString&amp; <replaceable>audioURL</replaceable>,\n"
"                  int <replaceable>opomnikMins</replaceable>,\n"
"                  int <replaceable>vrstaPonovitve</replaceable>,\n"
"                  int <replaceable>intervalPonovitve</replaceable>,\n"
"                  int <replaceable>številoPonovitev</replaceable>)"

#. Tag: parameter
#: index.docbook:4091
#, no-c-format
msgid "<parameter>URL</parameter>"
msgstr "<parameter>URL</parameter>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4093
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specifies the text or image file whose contents are to be displayed in the "
"message to be scheduled."
msgstr "<parameter>URL</parameter>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4134
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specifies the logical OR of the desired alarm flags. The flag bits are those "
"defined in class <classname>KAlarmIface</classname> in <filename>kalarmiface."
"h</filename>. Note that not all flag bits are applicable to file alarms."
msgstr ""
"Določa logično ALI želenih alarmnih zastavic. Biti zastavic so tisti, ki so "
"opredeljeni v razredu <classname>KAlarmIface</classname> v "
"<filename>kalarmiface.h</filename>. Upoštevajte, da za datotečne alarme ne "
"veljajo vsi biti zastavic."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4144
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specifies the background color for displaying the file. The string may be in "
"the format <quote>#RRGGBB</quote> (as returned by <methodname>QColor::"
"name()</methodname>) where RR, GG and BB are two-digit hexadecimal values "
"for red, green and blue. Alternatively the string may be in any of the other "
"formats accepted by <methodname>QColor::setNamedColor()</methodname>, such "
"as a name from the X color database (&eg; <quote>red</quote> or "
"<quote>steelblue</quote>). Set the string to null to specify the current "
"default background color."
msgstr ""
"Določa barvo ozadja za prikaz datoteke. Niz je lahko v obliki "
"<quote>#RRGGBB</quote> (kot ga vrne <methodname>QColor::name()</"
"methodname>), kjer so RR, GG in BB dvomestne šestnajstmestne vrednosti za "
"rdečo, zeleno in modro. Alternativno je lahko niz v kateri koli drugi "
"obliki, ki jo sprejme <methodname>QColor::setNamedColor()</methodname>, na "
"primer name iz baze barv X (&eg; <quote>rdeča</quote> ali <quote>modra</"
"quote>). Nastavite niz na nič, da določite trenutno privzeto barvo ozadja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4254
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<function>scheduleFile()</function> is a &DBus; call to schedule the "
"specified text or image file for display at the specified date and time. "
"Apart from specifying a file path or &URL; and omitting the foreground color "
"and font, its usage is identical to <link linkend=\"scheduleMessage-descrip"
"\"><function>scheduleMessage</function></link> - see the description of that "
"function for further details."
msgstr ""
"<function>scheduleFile()</function> je klic &DBus; za načrtovanje prikaza "
"določene besedilne ali slikovne datoteke ob določenem datumu in času. Razen "
"navedbe poti do datoteke ali &URL; ter opustitve barve in pisave v ospredju "
"je njena uporaba enaka uporabi <link linkend=\"scheduleMessage-descrip"
"\"><function>scheduleMessage</function></link> - za več podrobnosti glej "
"opis te funkcije."

#. Tag: refentrytitle
#: index.docbook:4266
#, no-c-format
msgid "<refentrytitle>scheduleCommand</refentrytitle>"
msgstr "<refentrytitle>scheduleCommand</refentrytitle>"

