"replaceable>,\n"
"                     const QString&amp; <replaceable>začetekDatumČas</"
"replaceable>,\n"
"                     int <replaceable>pozenZaključek</replaceable>,\n"
"                     unsigned <replaceable>zastavice</replaceable>,\n"
"                     int <replaceable>vrstaPonovitve</replaceable>,\n"
"                     int <replaceable>intervalPonovitve</replaceable>,\n"
"                     int <replaceable>številoPonovitev</replaceable>)"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: index.docbook:4276
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool scheduleCommand(const QString&amp; <replaceable>name</replaceable>,\n"
"                     const QString&amp; <replaceable>commandLine</"
"replaceable>,\n"
"                     const QString&amp; <replaceable>startDateTime</"
"replaceable>,\n"
"                     int <replaceable>lateCancel</replaceable>,\n"
"                     unsigned <replaceable>flags</replaceable>,\n"
"                     int <replaceable>recurType</replaceable>,\n"
"                     int <replaceable>recurInterval</replaceable>,\n"
"                     const QString&amp; <replaceable>endDateTime</"
"replaceable>)"
msgstr ""
"bool scheduleCommand(const QString&amp; <replaceable>ime</replaceable>,\n"
"                     const QString&amp; <replaceable>ukaznaVrstica</"
"replaceable>,\n"
"                     const QString&amp; <replaceable>začetekDatumČas</"
"replaceable>,\n"
"                     int <replaceable>pozenZaključek</replaceable>,\n"
"                     unsigned <replaceable>zastavice</replaceable>,\n"
"                     int <replaceable>vrstaPonovitve</replaceable>,\n"
"                     int <replaceable>intervalPonovitve</replaceable>,\n"
"                     const QString&amp; <replaceable>konecDatumČas</"
"replaceable>)"

#. Tag: parameter
#: index.docbook:4289
#, no-c-format
msgid "commandLine"
msgstr "ukaznaVrstica"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4291
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specifies the command whose execution is to be scheduled. The "
"<parameter>flags</parameter> parameter indicates whether this parameter "
"contains a shell command line or a command script."
msgstr ""
"Določa ukaz, katerega izvajanje je treba načrtovati. Parameter "
"<parameter>flags</parameter> označuje, ali ta parameter vsebuje ukazno "
"vrstico lupine ali ukazno skripto."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4333 index.docbook:4700
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specifies the logical OR of the desired alarm flags. The flag bits are those "
"defined in class <classname>KAlarmIface</classname> in <filename>kalarmiface."
"h</filename>. Note that not all flag bits are applicable to command alarms."
msgstr ""
"Določa logično ALI želenih alarmnih zastavic. Biti zastavic so tisti, ki so "
"opredeljeni v razredu <classname>KAlarmIface</classname> v "
"<filename>kalarmiface.h</filename>. Upoštevajte, da se za alarmne ukaze ne "
"uporabljajo vsi biti zastavic."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4419
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<function>scheduleCommand()</function> is a &DBus; call to schedule the "
"specified shell command line, or command script, for execution at the "
"specified date and time. Apart from specifying a command and omitting the "
"message color, font and audio file parameters, its usage is identical to "
"<link linkend=\"scheduleMessage-descrip\"><function>scheduleMessage</"
"function></link> - see the description of that function for further details."
msgstr ""
"<function>scheduleCommand()</function> je klic &DBus; za načrtovanje "
"izvajanja določene ukazne vrstice lupine ali ukazne skripte ob določenem "
"datumu in času. Razen določitve ukaza in izpustitve parametrov barve "
"sporočila, pisave in zvočne datoteke je njegova uporaba enaka kot pri <link "
"linkend=\"scheduleMessage-descrip\"><function>scheduleMessage</function></"
"link> - za več podrobnosti glej opis te funkcije."

